Usebenzela ekhaya noma cha, asikho isizathu sokuba ungazivocavoci. Nazi izizathu Okubalulekile okufanele ukwazi Izifo ezingathathelaniyo (amaNon-communicable diseases (ama-NCD)), okuhlanganisa izifo zenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi, umdlavuza, izifo zokuphefumula, nesifo sikashukela, ziyimbangela ehamba phambili yokushona emhlabeni wonke futhi zinobungozi kwezempilo emhlabeni jikelele. Kodwa-ke, ukuzivocavoca njalo kungenza ngcono impilo yenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi, amandla emisipha, kanye nokuguquguquka kube futhi kunciphisa nobungozi bokukhuluphala ngokweqile, isifo sikashukela, nezinye izifo ezingalapheki. Kusukela kuzisetshenziswa zokuphilisa umzimba namawashi obuchwepheshe kuya kuzinsiza zokuphilisa umzimba ezitholakala ku-inthanethi nasemphakathini, ubuchwepheshe benza amaklasi okuzivocavoca atholakale kalula, ukwazi ukuzibandakanya, kanti futhi kusebenza kakhulu kunakuqala. Izifo ezingathathelaniyo (amaNCD), okuhlanganisa izifo zenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi, umdlavuza, isifo sokuphefumula, nesifo sikashukela, ziyimbangela ehamba phambili yokushona emhlabeni wonke futhi zinobungozi kwezempilo emhlabeni jikelele. Ngo-2010, iNhlangano yezeMpilo eMhlabeni (iWorld Health Organization (iWHO)) yabikezela ukuthi i-Afrika izobona ukukhula kakhulu kwezinga lokufa kwezifo ezingathathelaniyo eminyakeni eyishumi ezayo. Ngokusho kwephepha lemininingwane leWHO lango-2022, abantu abayizigidi eziyi-17 babulawa iNCD ngaphambi kokuba babe neminyaka engama-70 minyaka yonke. Lokhu kufa ngaphambi kwesikhathi kubala u-86% wokufa kwabantu emazweni anengeniso lemali ephansi nephakathi kanti ama-77% wabantu abafayo ngokuhlobene ne-NCD kwenzeka lapho.
Ngeshwa, ngo-2030, izifo ezingathelelaniyo zizobikwa njengezifo ezihamba phambili ezibanga ukufa kuzwekazi lase-Afrika eliyi-sub-Saharan, zidlule izifo ezithathelanayo, zabesifazane, zezingane ezisanda kuzalwa, kanye neziphathelene nokudla okunomsoco (icommunicable, maternal, neonatal, and nutritional (iCMNN)). Izisetsenziswa zikamakhalekhukhwini, ama-EHR, kanye namanye amathuluzi obuchwepheshe alekelela ama-Afrika ekulawuleni nasekuvikeleleni izifo Kungani kunokwenyuka kwamaNCD e-Afrika? Kuningana okuyimbangela, okuhlanganisa inani labantu asebekhulile, ingqalasizinda yokunakekelwa kwezempilo enganele, kanye nokungakwazi ukubona inkinga kusenesikhathi, ukuvimbela, nokwelashwa, kube nomthelela ekwenyukeni kwamaNCD ezwenikazi. Ngaphandle kwalokho, ubumpofu nokungalingani e-Afrika kuvame ukuba yimbangela yokungakwazi ukukhetha ukudla okunempilo, izindawo zokuzivocavoca eziphephile, kanye nezinsiza zokunakekelwa kwezempilo ezisezingeni eliphezulu, okwenza kube yinselele ukuvimba nokuphathwa kweNCD. Ukufudukela emadolobheni ngokushesha e-Afrika kuyimbangela yokushintsha kwendlela yokuphila nokudla, njengoba abantu abaningi bedla ukudla okulondolozwe kakhulu okunosawoti omningi, ushukela namafutha angenampilo. Ukuthuthuka kwezobuchwepheshe nakho kuholele ekwenyukeni kwempilo yokuhlala ndawonye kanye nokwehla kwamazinga okunyakazisa umzimba. Kodwa-ke, ukuzivocavoca njalo kungenza ngcono impilo yenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi, amandla emisipha, kanye nokuguquguquka kube futhi kunciphisa nobungozi bokukhuluphala ngokweqile, isifo sikashukela, nezinye izifo ezingalapheki. Kodwa ngaphambi kokuba siqhubeke, kumele siqonde umehluko phakathi kokunyakazisa umzimba nokuzivocavoca. Yini umehluko phakathi kokunyakazisa umzimba nokuzivocavoca?
NgokweWHO, ukunyakazisa umzimba kuhlanganisa konke ukunyakaza kwezicubu zamathambo okudinga amandla, okuhlanganisa nalokho okwenzeka uma usebenza, udlala, wenza imisebenzi yasekhaya, usohambweni, kanye nokuba yingxenye yemidlalo yokuzijabulisa. Lokhu kuchaza ukuba ngungani impilo yokuhlala ungenzi lutho inciphisa ukunyakaza komzimba, okwandisa ubungozi bokuba neNCD. Isibonelo, phakathi nesonto, ngivame ukuchitha amahora ayisishiyagalombili esikrinini sekhompyutha yami futhi ngivuka embhedeni noma ngisuk etafuleni lami uma ngithathe ikhefu lokudla nom lasendlini yangasese. Ubungozi kwezempilo obungagwemeki obubangwa yintuthuko kwezobuchwepheshe ephazamisayo Ngenxa yokuthi ngichitha okungenani amahora ayisithupha nsuku zonke ngihlezi noma ngilele phansi ngaphandle kokunyakazisa umzimba, ngiphila impilo yokuhlale ngingenzi lutho. Uvame ukuchitha isikhathi esingakanani usebenza ehhovisi lakho uma ungasebenzeli ekhaya? Ukuhlala emotweni noma ebhasini akubalwa njengokusebenzisa umzimba. Ngaphandle uma uhamba ngezinyawo noma ugibela ibhayisikili uma uya emsebenzini, udinga ukunyakazisa umzimba kaningana. Njalo ngeviki, iWHO itusa ukuba abantu abaneminyaka ephakathi kweyi-18 nengama-64 banyakazise umzimba okungenani imizuzu eyi-150 ngamandla asezingeni elimaphakathi, banyakazise umzimba okungenani imizuzu engama-75 ngamandla amakhulu, noma ngokulinganayo kulokhu okubili. Abantu abadala kufanele banyakazise umzimba ngamandla asezingeni elimaphakathi imizuzu engama-300 ngesonto, noma okulinganayo, ukuze bazuze kwezempilo.,.
Bangakwazi futhi ukunikela izinsuku ezimbili noma ngaphezulu ngesonto bevocavoca izingxenye zomzimba eziqondene nemisipha. Ngakho-ke, noma ngabe usebenzela ekhaya noma uneshejuli engu-9–5, kungasiza uma uhlanganisa ukunyakazisa umzimba osukwini lwakho lomsebenzi. "Ukunyakazisa umzimba" kanye "nokuzivocavoca" akufanele kusetshenziswe ngokushintshana ngoba ukuzivocavoca noma ukujima ngokuvamile kusho indlela ehlelekile, ehleliwe, nephindaphindayo yokunyakazisa umzimba ngenhloso yokuthola umphumela othile, njengokukhulisa amandla emisipha, ukuphilisa inhliziyo nemithambo yegazi, noma ukuncipha. Kungani ukuzivocavoca kubalulekile? Ucwaningo luye lwabonisa ukuthi ukuzivocavoca njalo kwandisa impilo. Ucwaningo lwaseHarvard University luveze ukuthi abantu abanyakazisa umzimba ngenani elincane elishiwo banciphisa ingozi yokufa ngaphambi kwesikhathi ngama-21%. Ngocwaningo oluhlukile, ukuzivocavoca njalo kungandisa impilo yomuntu ngeminyaka emithathu kuya kwemihlanu. Ukujima njalo kungaqinisa isimiso senhliziyo nemithambo yegazi, kwandise amathambo nemisipha, kwandise ukuguquguquka, futhi kunciphise ingozi yokuba nezifo ezingelapheki. Isibonelo, ukugijima noma ukushova ibhayisikili kungasiza ukuqinisa inhliziyo namaphaphu, kwehlise ingozi yesifo senhliziyo nezinye izimo zenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi. Ukuzivocavoca okwandisa ithambo nemisipha, njengokuphakamisa izinsimbi noma ukudonsa intambo enwebekayo, kunganciphisa ingozi yesifo samathambo i-ostiyophorosisi.
Wake wajima wase uzizwa ukhululekile futhi ungenagcindezi? Sengike ngakwenza, futhi ukujima kuyayithuthukisa impilo yengqondo ngokunciphisa ingcindezi, ukhwantalala, ixhala, kanye nezimpawu zokhwantalala. Kusiza futhi ukwenzangcono isimokuzizwa futhi kuthuthukise nenqubokucabanga. Isibonelo, ukuhlanganisa i-yoga noma ukuzindla kwengqondo nokuzivocavoca kungasiza ukwehlisa ingcindezi nexhala. Ukuzivocavoca njalo kunganciphisa ingozi yokukhuluphala ngokukusiza ukuthi ushise amakholori bese wandisa imisipha yakho. Ukuzivocavoca nge-erobikhi njengokugijima noma ukubhukuda kungakusiza ushise amakholori ngenkathi usiza ukwakha imisipha, eshisa amakhalori amaningi ngisho noma uphumule. Ngenxa yokuthi balala kangcono futhi balale isikhathi eside, abantu abazivocavoca njalo bazizwa bephumule futhi benamandla. Ngokwesibonelo, ukuzivocavoca okulula, njengeyoga noma ukuhambahamba, kungenzangcono indlela olala ngayo, besekuthi lokhu okunamandla, okuhlanganisa ukuphakamisa izinsimbi noma ukugijima, kungakwandisa. Ngaphezu kwalokhu okuzuzayo, abantu abaningi bayehluleka ukuzivocavoca ngenxa yokuthi bamatasa kakhulu ngokuphathelene nemindeni yabo, imisebenzi, kanye neminye imisebenzi nokunye. Nakuba abanye abantu benganazo izindlela zokuzivocavoca, abanye abakwazi ukufinyelela ezikhungweni zemidlalo, izindawo zokuzivocavoca, noma ezinye izinsiza ezingabalekelela.
Futhi, kungase kubenzima kwabanye ukuhlala bekhuthazekile, ikakhulukazi uma bengakujabuleli noma bengayiboni imiphumela esheshayo. Abanye kungenzeka ukuba abakwazi ukuzivocavoca kahle noma abaqondi abangakuzuza ngokuzivocavoca. Ubuhlungu obungapheli kanye nezinkinga zokuhamba zombili lezi zimo zingenza ukuzivocavoca kube nzima noma ungakhululeki. Ngaphandle kwalokho, abanye bangase babe nexhala noma ukuzinyeza uma bezivocavoca phambi kwabanye noma esidlangalaleni, okungabavimba ukuba baqale noma bagcine isimokwenza. Ubuchwepheshe buyasiza ekutheni umuntu abhekane nezingqinamba zokuzivocavoca nokukhuthaza ukuphila kahle. Futhi manje, asikho isizathu sokungazivocavoci Eminyakeni yamuva nje, ubuchwepheshe bushintshe kakhulu izingxenye zempilo yethu, okuhlanganisa nendlela esinyakazisa ngayo umzimba nokuqina komzimba. Ukwengeza, kunyukile ukuthakasela ukuzivocavoca nokuqinisa umzimba e-Afrika njengoba abantu abaningi sebebona abangakuzuza ngokuzivivinya njalo ukuze baphile emzimbeni nasengqondweni. Futhi, ubuchwepheshe buthuthuke ngokushesha, okube nomthelela omkhulu kwezokuqinisa umzimba e-Afrika. Sekube neqhaza elikhulu ekuguquleni indlela abantu abazivocavoca ngayo nokuhlala bephila. Ngabe kwenzeka kanjani?
Izinhlelo zokujima eziqondene nawe Abantu bangafinyelela ezinhlelweni zokujima ezenzelwe ukuhlangabezana nezidingo nemigomo yabo ehlukile. Izisetshenziswa zokujima namawashi obuchwepheshe zikwazi ukulandelela amamethrikhi ezempilo ambalwa, njengezinga lokushaya kwenhliziyo, amaphethini okulala, nezinyathelo ezithathiwe, futhi zisebenzise leyo imininingo ukuze udale izinhlelo zokujima eziqondene nawe. Amanye amasimathifoni, okuhlanganisa iSamsung, enza lokhu. Awudingi ukulanda ezinye izisetshenziswa ezengeziwe. Ungangena ku"Samsung Health" ukuze uqale ukuqapha amamethrikhi akho ezempilo. Futhi, i-Apple Fitness+ iyatholakala kusisetshenziswa sokujima uma une-iPhone, i-iPad, noma i-Apple TV. Amadivayisi alandelela ukujima kwakho njengamabhendi okujima namawashi obuchwepheshe aya ngokuya atholakala kalula e-Afrika. Iwashi laka-Apple lingelinye lalezo zibonelo. Ungakwazi ukulanda ezinye izisetshenziswa, njengeGoogle Fit uma isimathifono sakho singakabi nazo.
Ungasebenzisa lokhu ukuhlala ukhuthazekile, ulandelele amazinga akho okujima, futhi uhlele ukujima okusebenzayo. Ungafaka izinhlelo zokujima eziqondene nezidingo zakho ngokusebenzisa izinhlelo ezisuselwe kuzinhlaka eziningi, okuhlanganisa amazinga okujima, iminyaka, nempilo. Izinhlelo zokujima eziqondene nawe zingakusiza uzuze imiphumela engcono futhi uqinisekise ukujima okuphephile nokusebenza kahle. Amakilasi aku-inthanethi nolwazi Ubhebhane lweCOVID-19, olwaphoqa okwesikhashana ukuvalwa kwezindawo eziningi zokuzivocavoca nezokujima, lwabanomthelela ekwandiseni amakilasi okujima ku-inthanethi kanye nezinsiza ezwenikazi. I-Afrika manje isiyakwazi ukufinyelela kumakilasi okujima afundiswa abafundisi emhlabeni wonke ngenxa yezinkundla eziku-inthanethi nezisetshenziswa zamavidiyo. Ngenxa yokuthi abantu abaningi manje sebengakwazi ukuba yingxenye yamakilasi okujima angaphandle kwezindawo zabo, abantu abaningi sebeyakwazi ukuthola ulwazi ngokujima, okwenza singabikhona isidingo somqeqeshi wokujima, okungase kubize. Abantu base-Afrika bangakwazi ukuthola izindlela zokujima, amavidiyo okuzivocavoca, nezeluleko ngokujima kuzitshenziswa zokujima eziningi, amawebhusayithi, nezinkundla zokuxhumana, okubavumela bafunde ngokudla okunempilo, izindlela zokuzivocavoca ezahlukene, kanye nangezempilo nokuphila kahle jikelele. Ngenxa yokusetshenziswa kwamasimathifoni kanye ne-inthanethi ezwenikazi, lolu lwazi lubanika amandla okwenza izinqumo ezinolwazi mayelana nemigomo namasu abo okujima. Ngakho-ke, akudingeki ukuthi uye ejimini ukuze uzivocavoce.
IYouTube inolwazi oluningi, okuhlanganisa namavidiyo okuzivocavoca alo lonke uhlobo lokuzivocavoca. Ungakwenza lokhu ngaphambi kokuya emsebenzini noma uma ubuya khona. Kufanele akukhuthaze amamethrikhi akho ezempilo. Ukwengeza, ungabheka izinsiza ngokucinga amagama afana nokuthi "ukuzivocavoca," "ama-aerobics," kanye "nokujima" kunoma iyiphi inkundla yezokuxhumana. Imiphakathi eku-inthanethi Ubuchwepheshe bube negalelo ekukhuleni kwemiphakathi yokujima ku-inthanethi e-Afrika. Abathanda ukujima sebengakwazi ukuxhumana, babelane ngamasu, futhi basekane ohambweni lwabo lokujima ezinkundleni zokuxhumana, emiphakathini eku-inthanethi, nesezinkundleni zokujima. Le miphakathi eku-inthanethi iyagqugquzelelana, iyakhuthazana, futhi iyakubophezela, okuyizinto ezibalulekile ukugcina isimiso sokujima esingaguquki. Imiphakathi yokujima eku-inthanethi iphinde ikwenze uzizwe uyingxenye yomphakathi ngokufaka umoya omuhle lapho abantu bengasekelana khona, baphumelele ndawonye, futhi basebenzisane nakuba kunezithiyo. Imishini yokuzivocavoca yasekhaya
Ubuchwepheshe sebenze kwaba lula kwabaningi ukwenza amajimu abo asekhaya ngokusebenzisa imishini yokuzivocavoca eshibhile nesebenzayo. Sekukuningi abantu abangakhetha kukho ukuze bazivocavoce ngokunethezeka emakhaya abo, kusukela kumabhande kuya emishinini yokuzivocavoca ephathekayo. Kusiza labo abangenawo amajimu noma izikhungo zokuzivocavoca lapho behlala khona. Miningi imishini yokuzivocavoca okungakhethwa kuyo eklanyelwe izidingo nezabelomali zabantu base-Afrika, kusukela kwijimu yasekhaya enngabizi kuya kuzimpahla zokujima ezenziwe endaweni. Ngokubheka uhlobo lwakho lokuzivocavoca, ijimu yakho yasekhaya ingaba ne-yoga noma umata wokuzivocavoca, amabhande okujima ahlukahlukene, ibhola lokujima, ibhentshi noma ibhokisi lokunyathela, isondo lesisu, idiski, noma intambo yokugxuma. Uma uqaphela futhi ungazi ukuthi ungaqala kanjani, ungabuka izinsiza eziku-inthanethi ngenkathi usebenzisa imishini yokujima. Ungaluhlela kanjani uhlelo lokuzivocavoca Ukuhlela uhlelo lokuzivocavoca ongakwazi ukulimela kungaba nzima, kodwa uma unohlelo olufanele, kungenzeka. Nakhu okokukucebisa. Hlola izinga lamandla omzimba
Ukuhlonza izinga lamandla omzimba wakho kuyisinyathelo sokuqala esibalulekile ekwakheniuhlelo lokujima ukuze uhlangabezane nezidingo nemigomo yakho. Unganquma izinga lamandla omzimba ngezindlela ezilandelayo: Ukuqapha izinga lokushaya kwenhliziyo yakho ngenkathi uzivocavoca kungenye yezindlela zokuhlola ukubekezela kwenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi. Ukugqoka okuqaphela ukushaya kwenhliziyo noma ukusebenzisa okulandelela amandla omzimba kuzokwenza wazi ukushaya kwenhliziyo yakho. Futhi ungagijima imizuzu eyi-12 njengengxenye yokuhlola ukushaya kwenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi. Ungakwazi ukukala izinga lakho lamandla emisipha ngokuzivocavoca njengokuphakamisa umzimba ngokusebenzisa izandla, ukuphakamisa umhlane uhlezi phansi, noma uqoshame bese ubala ukuthi ungakuphinda kangakhi lokhu. Ukuze uhlole ukuthi imisipha yakho ingakubekezelela kangakanani lokhu, ukwazi ukuzivocavoca, njengamaplanki, ukuncika ngodonga, noma amalanjisi, bese ukala isikhathi. Ukuze ukwazi ukulinganisa ukuguquguquka, hlala phansi ulule imilenze yakho iqonde phambi kwakho bese ulula izandla zakho ziye phambili ukuze izandla zakho zifinyelele ezinyaweni uhlezi phansi. Sebenzisa amathuluzi afana nama-skinfold callipers ukubala amaphesenti amafutha omzimba wakho ukuze wazi ukwakheka komzimba wakho. Ungakwazi futhi nokuhlola impilo yakho jikelele kanye nobungozi bezifo ezingelapheki usebenzisa izilinganiso ezifana nomjikelezo wokhalo noma inkomba yesisindo somzimba (ibody mass index (iBMI)).
Ungakwazi ukuzivocavoca njengokuma ngomlenze owodwa uvale amehlo akho noma uhambe ucokama ukuze uhlole ibhalansi yakho nokuxhumanisa. Zibekele imigomo engafezeka Ukuzibekela imigomo engakwazi ukufezeka kuza ngemva kokuhlola ileveli yamandla omzimba. Izinjongo zakho kufanele zibe yinselele kodwa zikwazi ukwenzeka ngesikhathi esifanele. Yakha isimiso esizinzile futhi uqale kancane Kubalulekile ukukhetha izinhlelo zokuzivocavoca ezisebenza ngohlelo lwakho, ngakho hlela ukuzivocavoca futhi ukuhlanganise nohlelo lwakho lwansuku zonke noma lwamasonto onke. Khetha isikhathi esikulungele. Kubalulekile ukuthi uqale kancane futhi ukhuphukele ezingeni eliphezulu ngokuhamba kwesikhathi. Kuzokwenza kube lula ukuhlala ohlelweni lwakho lokujima futhi ungalimali. Hlanganisa ukujima kwakho bese uhlola inqubekela phambili yakho.
Kubalulekile ukushintsha ukujima kwakho ukuze ugweme isithukuthezi kanye nokumelandawonye. Zama izinhlelo zokuzivocavoca ezintsha, khulisa umfutho, noma unyakazise umzimba ngendlela enstha. Ungaqapha ukuthuthuka kwakho ngokugcina irekhodi lokujima kwakho futhi ugade izinga lakho lamandla omzimba. Ukwenza lokhu kuzokwenza ugqozi lwakho luhlale phezulu.
ITECNO Isintshe Ubuciko Kumasimathifoni ngoMklomo omuhle weCAMON 20 Doodle! Ngokwakhela phezu kwempumelelo yohlelo lweCAMON 19 Mondrian, iTECNO isiphinde yethula enye isimathifoni enobuciko nentsha, iCAMON 20 Doodle Edition ene-Android. manje, isimbozo sangemuva sigqame imidwebo emangalisayo, njengoba imidwebo inezithunzi ezidansayo nezishiya umkhondo ohlekisayo nongaqondakali la ohamba khona. Idizayini ehlukile ehlelelwe ukuchaza kabusha ukuthi sibubona kanjani ubuciko kumasimathifoni. Ukwethulwa kweCAMON 20 Doodle Edition ku-Android, kwenza imidwebo ibe ngaphezu nje kohlobo lokuziveza; kuba yinto ejulile ehlanganisa ubuciko nobuchwepheshe. Isimbozo sangemuva esihlotshiswe ngobuciko bemidwebo obukhazimulayo zizojabulisa futhi zihehe, zenze kube nezingxoxo futhi zijikise amakhanda. Umdwebo ngamunye ugcwele ubuhlakani nokuqamba izinto ezintsha, okwenza iCAMON 20 Doodle Edition ingabi nje idivayisi kodwa ikhanvasi yamathuba angapheli. Kodwa lomlingo awugcini lapho. Ngale kobuchule bayo bobuciko, iTECNO CAMON 20 Doodle Edition lunikeza oyisebenzisayo ulwazi olushelelayo nolunamandla. Inikwa amandla yi-Android 13 yeGoogle, iTECNO CAMON 20 Doodle Edition lunebhethri elihlala isikhathi eside elingu-5000mAh, elinikeza amandla osuku lonke, kanye neshaji engu-33W ukuze igcwalise amandla ayo ngokushesha.
