IDuke ne-ICANBOI babambe umhlangano weSME ukuze babe nomthelela kosomabhizinisi abangaphezu kuka-100+ ILagos, inhloko-dolobha yezomnotho yaseNigeria iyisizinda samabhizinisi amancane naphakathi (ismall and medium enterprises (ama-SME)) eNigeria futhi iyindawo egcwele izinguquko, umthethonqubo omningi futhi izikhathi eziningi alukho ulwazi olwanele lobuchwepheshe ukuze bakwazi ukumelana nezithiyo. ISME Bootcamp 1.0 Initiative ihlose ukulungisa imithwalo ephathelene nokuba nebhizinisi elisha noma elikade livele likhona eLagos eNigeria ngokuhlomisa abanikazi bamabhizinisi abasha nabakade bevele bekhona ngezinsiza ezifanele namathuba okuhlala besebenza endaweni yemakethe ehlale iqhudelana. IDuke Sell, ngokubambisana ne-ICANBOI, iLagos State Employment Trust Fund (iLSETF), i-Institute of Chartered Accountants of Nigeria (i-ICAN) kanye neBank of Industry (iBOI), iJobtech Alliance, kanye neSalad Africa bazohlanganisa isizukulwane esisha sama-SME ukuhlomisa osomabhizinisi nabanikazi bamabhizinisi ngolwazi, ukuqeqeshwa, namathuba okukhulisa amabhizinisi abo. Ibootcamp inesihloko esithi “Umhlahlandlela wamaSME Wokuqala Nokukhulisa Ibhizinisi Lakho” izobanjelwa e-ICANBOI Innovation Hub etholakala phakathi neYaba, eLagos. IBootcamp inikeza ababambiqhaza, abanikazi bamabhizinisi abasha nabakhona ithuba lokuthola uqeqesho, izinsiza namathuba adingekayo ukuze kuncishiswe izithiyo zokuqala nokukhulisa ibhizinisi njengosomabhizinisi eLagos. Usuku: uNcwaba 26, 2023 (ngoMgqibelo) Isikhathi: 10am Indawo: ICANBOI Innovation Hub 5th Floor, 82 Murtala Mohammed Way, Ebute-Metta, Lagos KUNGANI KUFANELE UBEKHONA?
Ukuthola uqeqesho namathuba okuthuthuka Ukuthola uxhaso olungase lube khona nezinsiza Ukufinyelela kubantu nezinhlangano ezinamandla Ibootcamp IMAHHALA!, Vakashela ku-bit.ly/SMEBizClinic ukuze uthole isikhala. Ukubhalisa kuyisibopho. Mayelana Nathi IDukesell IDuke yingosi yokuthengisa kabusha eyenza noma ubani akwazi ukuqala ibhizinisi eliku-inthanethi ngaphandle kwemali noma uhlu. Lokhu sikwenza ngokuhlinzeka ngengqalasizinda, uhlu, kanye nolwazi, ngaleyo ndlela sinciphisa okungavimba ukuba uqale ibhizinisi namuhla. I-ICAN-BOI Innovation Hub
I-ICAN-BOI iyingosi yokugxila ekukhuleni kwezobuchwepheshe kanye nokutholwa kwamakhono ngokunikwa amandla kwezamabhizinisi. Isemkhankasweni wokuba isixhumanisi sethalente lezobuchwepheshe kanye nokuqamba izinto ezintsha, okuhlanganisa abafundi, izifundiswa, abasunguli, abatshalizimali, kanye nongoti bokuthuthukiswa komnotho. ILagos State Employment Trust Fund (iLSETF) ILagos State Employment Trust Fund (iLSETF) yasungulwa yiLagos State Employment Trust Fund Law ngo-2016 ukuze inikeze usizo lwezezimali kubahlali baseSifundazweni SaseLagos, ukuze kubhekwane nokuntuleka kwemisebenzi ngokwakha imisebenzi nengcebo. I-Institute of Chartered Accountants yaseNigeria (i-ICAN) I-Institute of Chartered Accountants yaseNigeria iyinhlangano yamabhuku ezimali eNigeria. Ingenye yezinhlangano ezimbili zobungcweti zokubalwa kwezimali neziphathimandla ezilawulayo eNigeria, Ngolwazi lwayo lwezobuchwepheshe, amakhono, kanye nobungcweti, ihlinzeka ngokuqondisisa kanye nobuholi kumkhakha wezokubalwa kwezimali emhlabeni wonke kanye nomsebenzi wezezimali. IBank of Industry (iBOI) Ibhange iBank of Industry liyisikhungo sezezimali eNigeria (idevelopment financial institution (iDFI)) esinegunya lokuguqula umkhakha wezimboni waseNigeria ngokuhlinzeka ngosizo lwezezimali ukuze kusungulwe amabhizinisi amakhulu, aphakathi nendawo, namancane; kanye nokugqugquzela ukwanda, ukuhlukahluka, kanye nokwenza kube yisimanjemanje.
Igunya elihloselwe ukusekela amaphrojekthi anamandla okuthuthuka. IJobtech Alliance IJobtech Alliance iwuhlelo lokwakha i-ecosystem emisebenzini ebandakanyayo e-Afrika enentshisekelo yokuxhumanisa abantu namathuba omsebenzi ngokwenza izindawo ezivumela osomabhizinisi bakwazi ukwakha izingosi eziphilisa abantu ngendlela eseqophelweni eliphezulu. ISalad Africa ISaladi iletha izixazululo zokuguqula abasebenzi base-Afrika ngokufaka isandla emphakathini wabantu abanezimali abaphila izimpilo ezingcono. ISalad Afrika ibambisana nabaqashi ukuze banikeze abasebenzi babo bathole ingxenye yemiholo yabo ngaphambi kosuku lomholo ukuze bakwazi ukubhekana nezidingo eziphuthumayo kalula okuyisinyathelo sokuqala ohambweni oluya ekuphileni kahle kwezezimali nenkululeko.
Osaziwayo Bemithombo Yezindaba "iDo2dtun" ijoyina i-AltSchool Africa njengoMqondisi we Creator Relations I-AltSchool Africa, inkampani ehamba phambili yobuchwepheshe bezemfundo egxile ezisombululweni ezintsha zokufunda namathuba emisebenzi, imemezele ukuqokwa komunye wabezindaba abadume kakhulu e-Afrika, u-Oladotun Ojuolape Kayode, owaziwa nangokuthi iDo2dtun, njengoMqondisi Wezobudlelwano. Esitatimendeni esikhishwe yinkampani, u-Do2dtun uzobamba iqhaza elibalulekile ekuqiniseni ubudlelwano nabasunguli bokuqukethwe, othisha, kanye nabagqugquzeli ukuze kuthuthukiswe umgomo we-AltSchool Africa wokuguqula ukufunda ngenthanethi kulo lonke izwekazi. Ngomsebenzi ophumelelayo othathe iminyaka engaphezu kwamashumi amabili embonini yezindaba nezokuzijabulisa, u-Do2dtun uletha ingcebo yesipiliyoni, ubuciko, kanye nenethiwekhi enkulu esikhundleni sakhe esisha e-AltSchool Africa. Njengomethuli womsakazo ovelele, umphathi womcimbi, kanye nomgqugquzeli, u-Do2dtun ubelokhu ekhombisa uthando lwakhe lokuba nomthelela omuhle kwisiko lentsha kanye nemboni yezokuzijabulisa iyonke. "Siyajabula ukwamukela u-Do2dtun ethimbeni lethu njengoMqondisi Wezabasunguli," kusho [uRachael Onoja], Inhloko Yezokusebenza, i-AltSchool Africa. "UDotun udlala indima ebalulekile ekusizeni i-AltSchool Africa ukuthi igcwalise isithembiso sayo sokwenza ukufunda kube mnandi, kube nokuhlangenwe nakho, futhi kube nenzuzo. Ngokuvala igebe phakathi kwe-AltSchool Africa kanye nongoti bezimboni, manje sesingakwazi ukuletha iminyaka yolwazi olungakasetshenziswa, olubalulekile kanye nokuqonda kubantu base-Afrika abafisa ukuphishekela imisebenzi emabhizinisini nasezimbonini zobuciko." Ukuqokwa kukaDo2dtun kufika ngesikhathi esibalulekile ku-AltSchool Africa njengoba iqhubeka nokwandisa ukufinyelela nomthelela wayo endaweni ye-edtech. Ngobuntu bakhe obuguquguqukayo kanye nesizinda sakhe sobungcweti kwezokuXhumana Kwabantu abaningi, uDo2dtun umiselwe ukuhola imizamo yokukhuthaza ukusebenzisana okunenjongo nobudlelwano nabafundisi, amaciko, kanye nabagqugquzeli ukuze kuthuthukiswe iminikelo ye-AltSchool Africa nokudala indawo yokufunda eheha abafundi.
"Ngijabule kakhulu ukujoyina i-AltSchool Africa futhi ngifake isandla endleleni yabo entsha yokufunda," kusho u-Oladotun Ojuolape. "Imfundo iyithuluzi elinamandla lenguquko, futhi ngizibophezele ekusebenziseni ulwazi lwami ukuze ngivale igebe phakathi kokudalwa kokuqukethwe kanye nolwazi lokufunda oluzuzisayo. Ngokubambisana, sizogqugquzela isizukulwane esilandelayo sabafundi." Mayelana ne-AltSchool Africa: I-AltSchool Africa yinkampani yomhlaba wonke yezobuchwepheshe bethalente elizibophezele ekulungiseni kabusha isimo sokufunda ngobuchwepheshe obusha, ulwazi lokufunda oluqondene nawe, kanye nobudlelwano obunenjongo. Ngokuhlanganisa ubuchwepheshe obusezingeni eliphezulu nokuqukethwe okuklanywe ngobungcweti, i-AltSchool Africa ihlose ukuhlinzeka abafundi ngamathuluzi nezinsiza abazidingayo ukuze baphumelele emhlabeni ohlale uvela. Imininingwane ngo-Oladotun "Do2dtun" Ojuolape: U-Oladotun Ojuolape ungumuntu waseNigeria osemoyeni, ijockey yevidiyo, ihypeman, umlingisi, kanye nosomabhizinisi wezindaba onolwazi olungaphezu kweminyaka engamashumi amabili embonini yezindaba nezokudala.
IPATRICIA Technologies Limited Ithola Ukutshalwa Kwezimali Okubalulekile Ukuze Kuthuthukiswe Ukusebenza IPatricia Technologies Limited ithole ukutshalwa kwezimali okubalulekile okuvela ku-Oluwaseun Dania, iSikhulu Esiphezulu seTradefada, okungenye yokuhwebelana kwecrypto ehamba phambili yaseNigeria. Lokhu kutshalwa kwezimali kuyinkomba evotini lokuzethemba abatshalizimali abanalo embonweni oqinile wePATRICIA kanye nesinqumo sokuvula indlela yokuthuthuka kwezezimali e-Afrika. Ihlonishwa njengenye yezindawo ezihamba phambili zokuhwebelana nge-crypto e-Afrika, iPATRICIA iqinisa indima yayo ehamba phambili ezindaweni zebhukunyazi yase-Afrika ehlala ishintsha ngokusebenzisana okunamandla, ubudlelwano, kanye nokutshalwa kwezimali okuvela kubalingani emhlabeni jikelele. U-Oluwaseun Dania ungumtshalizimali owaziwayo we-serial, onentshisekelo yokusekela amabhizinisi amasha kuzo zonke izimboni ezahlukahlukene. Ukhuthaza abantu ngabanye kanye nontanga basezimbonini ukuthi bamjoyine ekusekeleni ukuvela kabusha kwe-Patricia Technologies njengoba inkampani iqhubeka nokumela i-Afrika emhlabeni jikelele wezindawo zebhukunyazi. Encwadini yakamuva ku-inthanethi, uMnu Oluwaseun uthe, “Utshalomali lwami alukona nje umnyakazo wezezimali; ivoti elikhulu lokulethemba eqenjini eliholwa uHanu Fejiro Agbodje elihlale likhombisa ukukhalipha nokuqamba izinto ezintsha futhi elimele kahle iNigeria ne-Afrika emhlabeni jikelele”. “Ukuvela kabusha kwePATRICIA kuzoqinisa imboni yethu futhi kujulise ukwethenjwa kwabasebenzisi bethu. Kuwukuwina kwethu sonke,” ephetha. Ephawula ngokutshalwa kwezimali okubalulekile kukaMnu. Dania kuPatricia, uHanu Fejiro, Umsunguli kanye Nomphathi Omkhulu, ugcizelele ukuzibophezela kwakhe ekuqinisekiseni ifa elihlala njalo lebhizinisi ngenkathi egqamisa amathuba amakhulu asazayo.
“Lokhu kutshalwa kwezimali okuvela kuMnu. Oluwaseun Dania uthembisa ukushayela i-Patricia Technologies ukuthi iqhube imingcele futhi iqinise isikhundla sayo njengamandla ahamba phambili endaweni yebhukunyazi yase-Afrika eguqukayo njalo”, esho. Ngokusekelwa okungapheli okuvela kubatshalizimali kanye namakhasimende ngokufanayo, uPatricia uqhubekisela phambili indawo yebhukuyazi yase-Afrika. Hlanganyela nathi kulolu hambo namuhla futhi ube yingxenye yesitimela esihambayo. IPatricia enye yezinkampani eziphathelene nezokukhokha ongayisebenzisa esebenzisa amandla obuchwepheshe beBlockchain ukuze kube lula ukusetshenziswa kwezimali zebhukunyazi okwenziwa nsuku zonke. Ngokuzibophezela okuqinile embonini yezamabhukunyazi, siye saletha ngokungaguquki izixazululo ezintsha ezihlangabezana nezidingo zamakhasimende ethu futhi zidlule lokho abekulindele.
Ngemuva kokusokola ukuthola imali eyengeziwe kubatshalizimali, ukuqalwa kwezokuthengiselana ngobuchwepheshe i-ecommrce eKenya, iMarketForce, iqoqa isigidi esisodwa samadola kwingosi yokuqoqa izimali kubantu ababhlukene phecelezi icrowdsourcing, iCapitalize Emuva konyonyaka owodwa wokumemezela ukuvalwa kweSeries A yayo eyizigidi ezingama-$40, iMarketForce imemezele ukuthi iqoqa isigidi esisodwa samadola ngo-WeFunder. "Ngesikhathi siqala lolu hambo, sazibophezela ekwakheni inkampani yase-Afrika eyingqayizivele enikeza amandla abantu base-Afrika, imiphakathi kanye nezomnotho, futhi lo mjikelezo womphakathi ungenye yezindlela zokuhlanganisa okuhle. "Lokhu sikwenza ngoba sikholelwa ukuthi inkampani efana neMarketForce inikeza ithuba lokukhiqiza imali, hhayi kuphela kubathengisi nozakwethu esibasebenzelayo, kodwa nakubantu abaqondayo nabakholelwayo ukuthi esikwakhayo kubalulekile kuzwikazi," ingxenye yesimemezelo. Ibhizinisi elisaqala lamukela ukutshalwa kwezimali kusuka kokulinganiselwe ku-$1,000 ngemibandela efanayo esetshenziselwa i-Series A. Kodwa-ke, ithi akubona bonke abatshalizimali abazothola inani labo abalifunayo lokutshala imali. Yasungulwa ngo-2018 nguTesh Mbaabu kanye noMesongo Sibuti, iMarketForce iyindawo yemakethe yeB2B ehlinzeka ngezinsizakalo zokusabalalisa kanye nezezimali kubathengisi. Kusukela eKenya, ukuqaliswa selokhu kwanda emazweni aseduze, okuhlanganisa iTanzania, iRwanda, ne-Uganda. Iphinde isebenze naseNigeria. Isiqalo esisekelwe iY Combinator sisebenzela abathengisi abangaphezu kuka-200,000 kulawa mazwe amahlanu futhi sibone imali engenayo ikhula isuka ku-$140,000 ngo-2021 yaya kwizigidi ezingu-$2.5 ngo-2022, ngokohlu lwayo lweCapitaize.
Ihlela futhi ukwelula izinsizakalo zayo emazweni amane ngaphezulu. Ngenkathi iMarketForce iphakamisa uchungechunge A lwayo ngo-2022, yayinethemba lokuqhuba inani labathengisi kuhlelo lwayo lokusebenza olukhulu lomthengisi, iRejaReja, lifinyelele esigidini ekupheleni kuka-2022. Kodwa-ke, lezo zinhlelo zathinteka ngemuva kokuthi abatshalizimali abathile behlulekile ukuthumela ingxenye yomhlomulo wotshalomali phecelezi i-equity investment eyayithenjiswe ekuqaleni. Ngenxa yalokho, yadiliza abasebenzi abangama-250 futhi yahlela kabusha ibhizinisi layo ukuze lenze inzuzo. Engxoxweni abe nayo neTechCrunch kuNhlaba wezi-2023, iMbaabu, iCEO sale nkampani, iveze ukuthi inciphise isibalo semizila ebihamba kuyo isuka ku-700 yaya ku-400 ukuze iqhubekisele phambili ukusebenza kahle, wengeza ngokuthi inkampani izoqopha imali yayo ephezulu kakhulu.
Umsunguli weKobo360, u-Obi Ozor, ujoyina iKhabhinethi Yesifunda sase-Enugu njengoKhomishana Wezokuthutha U-Obi Ozor, umsunguli weKobo360, uqokwe njengoKhomishana Wezokuthutha e-Enugu State. U-Ozor, owasungula iKobo360 no-Ife Oyedele ngowezi-2017, wafungiswa kanye nabanye okhomishana abangu-19 ngumbusi we-Enugu State, uBarr. Peter Mbah, ngoLwesine, ziyi-10 kuNcwaba wezi-2023. Emcimbini wokufungiswa, umbusi waveza ukuthi amakhomishana akhethwe ngokwesipiliyoni, umlando kanye nemvelaphi yawo. Uphinde wezwakalisa ukuthi unethemba lokuthi izakhamuzi zakulesi sifundazwe zizoqala ukubona imiphumela kokhomishana abasanda kuqashwa ezinsukwini eziyi-100 zokuqala ehhovisi. “Sizwakalise umbono omkhulu ozosibona sikhulisa umnotho wethu. Siphinde sathembisa abantu bakithi ukuthi bazoqeda ububha futhi sifuna ukwenza i-Enugu State indawo ephambili yokutshalwa kwezimali. Leyo yimibono encomekayo nephakeme. Kodwa ngesikhathi senza lezo zithembiso, sasidinga ithimba elizodlulisela abantu bakithi kusukela lapho esikhona namuhla libayise kuleya ndawo esifuna ukubayisa kuyo. Ngalesi sizathu, inqubo eholele ekukhethweni kwakho ibiqinile futhi inemininingwane,” kusho yena.
U-Ozor uyilungu lakamuva le-ecosystem yaseNigeria oqokwe esikhundleni sezepolitiki ngemuva kokuthi uBosun Tijani efakwe ohlwini lwabaqokwe njengongqongqoshe oluthunyelwe umongameli waseNigeria, uBola Ahmed Tinubu. Akukacaci ukuthi u-Ozor uzohoxa yini esikhundleni sakhe sokuba iCEO ye-Kobo360, njengoba kungekho mfuneko ecacile yokuthi abaqokwe ezinkampanini ezizimele bashiye umsebenzi wabo wangaphambilini.
Ingosi yentengiselwano yomphakathi edla ubhedu yeVendorstack Idlula iNigeria, Yenza kubelula Ukuthengisa Kwi-inthanethi Imakethe yezentengiselwano yezenhlalo ikhula ngokushesha njengoba abathengi baya ngokuya bethenga phakathi kwezinkundla zokuxhumana. Ngokocwaningo lwakamuva, imakethe yezentengiselwano yomhlaba wonke kulindeleke ukuthi ifinyelele ku-$604.5 wezigidigidi ngo-2027, isuka ku-$492.2 wezigidigidi ngo-2021. Lokhu kumele iCAGR ye-3.7% emuva kwesikhathi sokubikezela. Ezentengiselwano zokuxhumana zithola umfutho eNigeria ngokukhula okusheshayo kokusetshenziswa kwezinkundla zokuxhumana. INigeria inabasebenzisi bezinkundla zokuxhumana abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-33, iningi labo lizebenzasa uFacebook, Instagram, Twitter kanye neWhatsApp. Lokhu kuveza ithuba elikhulu lokuthenga ebantwini. Imakethe yezentengiselwano ngobuchwepheshe yaseNigeria kulindeleke ukuthi ifinyelele ku-$75 wezigidigidi ngo-2025, isuka ku-$12 wezigidigidi ngo-2018. Imakethe iqhutshwa ukwanda kokungena kwe-inthanethi, ukwamukelwa kwamasimathifoni, kanye nenani labantu abasha abanolwazi lwezobuchwepheshe. Ngokwalo mbiko, izigidi ezingama-357 zeNaira kubikwa ukuthi kunomkhonyovu wokuntshontshela kubantu abathenga izinto kubathengisi baku-Instagram, izigidi ezingama-84 zeNaira kuthiwa zidalwe ukuthengiselana okungagculiseki ngenkathi amaNaira ayizigidi ezingama-273 zibalwa nemikhonyovu phakathi kowezi-2020 - 2021, iningi labantu baseNigeria labhekana nalokhu ngenkathi bethenga kubathengisi bakwezokuxhumana.
