Sethula iRoqqu: ezokunza uthole iBhukunyazi eGhana Siyajabula ukumemezela ukwethulwa kweRoqqu, ingosi yoguquko eletha imali yebhukunyazi kubantu baseGhana. IRoqqu ingaphezu nje ngokushintshana ngemali yebhukunyazi; iyisixazululo sakho sokuthenga ngokushesha, ukuthengisa, nokuphatha izimpahla zedijithali. Ukunika amandla Abashisekeli bebhukunyazi baseGhana Ngokukhula kwentshisekelo yezebhukunyazi emhlabeni, uRoqqu uyasibona isidingo sengosi ethembekile nesebenziseka kalula eklanyelwe imakethe yaseGhana. Umgomo wethu uwukunikeza amandla abantu baseGhana ukuthi babambe iqhaza emhlabeni othokozisayo wezezimali zebhukunyazi sibe sinikeza ingosi yokuthengiselana evikelekile nephumelelayo. Mayelana neRoqqu: IRoqqu ingosi yezezimali zebhukunyazi ehamba phambili enikeza abasebenzisi bayo indlela elula nevikelekile yokuthenga, ukuthengisa, nokuphatha izimali zebhukunyazi. Ngomgomo wokushayela ukwamukelwa kwezezimali zebhukunyazi ezimakethe ezisafufusa, i-Roqqu inikeza isikhombimsebenzisi esisebenziseka kalula, izimali zebhukunyazi ezahlukahlukene, nezici zokuphepha eziqinile. Landa uhlelo lokusebenza lweRoqqu lapha Isitolo Sohlelo Lokusebenza neSitolo sikaGoogle Play. Kungani kufanele ukhethe iRoqqu?
