Izindaba Ezijabulisayo Zomphakathi Womkhiqizo e-Afrika: Qguqguzela Abalingani base-Afrika ngeProductDive! Siyajabula ukwabelana ngezindaba ezinhle ezingase zikhulise ulwazi lwakho lokufunda nokuxhumana nabantu. Ukusebenzisana phakathi kwemicimbi emibili eguquguqukayo kulungiselwe ukuchaza kabusha indawo yamathuba ekuphathweni komkhiqizo. Siyajabula ukumemezela ubudlelwano obuyisisekelo phakathi kwe-ProductDive kanye nengqungquthela i-Inspire Africa, ehlelwe yithimba leSilicon Valley Product. Ukuhlangana kwalezi zinkundla ezimbili ezinamandla kusho ukuthi bonke abahambele umcimbi abanethikithi lokuya ku-DIVE sebemenyiwe ukuthi babe yingxenye yengqungquthela i-Inspire Africa – MAHHALA! Yebo, uzwe kahle. Njengengxenye yalokhu kuhlanganyela okusha, sivula iminyango yomhlaba wokuqonda, ukuxhumana, nokukhula. Njengoba kuhlangene kokubili iDIVE nengqungquthela i-Inspire Africa, akusadingeki ukhethe phakathi kwemicimbi emibili ehlukile. Konke kufinyeleleka kuwe! Lokhu kubambisana kuwukuzibophezela kwethu ekukhuthazeni umphakathi womkhiqizo ochumayo eNigeria nakwamanye amazwe.
Kumayelana nokususa imigoqo, ukwandisa amathuba, nokusungula ulwazi oluphelele olukunika amandla okuphumelela njengabaholi bemikhiqizo. Futhi ukuze ujabule, iProductDive ikunikeza ngomusa isaphulelo sika-15% sokuthenga ithikithi lakho engqungqutheleni yabo ezoba ngoMgqibelo, ziyi-12 kuNcwaba. Sicela ucofe isixhumanisi ukuze uthenge ithikithi lakho. Sebenzisa Ikhodi Yokuthengisa iDIVESVPG15 Maka amakhalenda akho, ulungele ukungena kwezokuphathwa komkhiqizo kwakusasa, futhi wamukele leli thuba eliyingqayizivele Lokukhuthaza i-Afrika ngobungcweti bomkhiqizo wakho.
I-OAU, CU ikhiqize inani eliphakeme kakhulu labasunguli bokuqala 'abangosozigidi' baseNtshonalanga ne-Afrika kule minyaka eyishumi edlule. NgoMsombuluko, zi-5 kuMfumfu wezi-2020, iTechpoint Africa yethule umbiko wayo weWest Africa Startup Decade. Lo mbiko ugxile kumisebenzi yokuxhasa ngemali yokuqala ibhizinisi kwezobuchwepheshe phakathi kuka-2010 no-2019. Iqukethe ukuhlukaniswa kwemisebenzi yoxhaso ngezimboni eziqalayo, umsuka wabatshalizimali, nokugqama kwemboni, phakathi kokunye. Kubalulekile ukusho ukuthi yi-Millionaire West African Startups (iMWAS) kuphela -- ababhizinisi asafufusa esifundeni saseNtshonalanga ne- Afrika aqoqe isigidi esisodwa samadola ngokunqwabelana -- ngesikhathi sokubuyekeza esicutshungulwe kulo mbiko. Ukugxila kwezemfundo zabasunguli bamabhizinisi asaqala kuveze ukuthi i-Obafemi Awolowo University (OAU) kanye neCovenant University (CU) bakhiqize abafundi abayi-12 nabayi-6, ngokulandelana, ukuze bathole indawo yokuqala neyesibili ekuqhekekeni kwesikhungo ngeziqu zokuqala. okumangalisayo, ukuthi okuvamile ukuthi abasunguli beMWAS besikhungo esisodwa semfundo ephakeme basungula izinkampani ndawonye. IKudi, uma senza umzekelo, inabasunguli abambalwa beMWAS abavela eNyuvesi yase-Obafemi Awolowo; amanye amabhizinisi asaqala anabasunguli abavela e-OAU yiTeamApt, Terragon, Farmcrowdy, 54gene, SlimTrader, kanye nePropertyPro. ICovenant University iphinde yakhiqiza abasunguli abaqalayo -- i-PiggyVest, iMDAAS, neKora Network -- evezwe embikweni. Kungase kubonakale sengathi lezi zikhungo zinekhono lokukhiqiza ama-alumni aqalayo aphumelele noma lawa ma-alumni aqhubeke nokuxoxisana, ngemva kokuthweswa iziqu, okubavumela ukuthi bahlangane baqale lezi zinkampani.
Noma ngabe yisiphi isizathu, lezi zikhungo zinikeze abasunguli beMWAS abaningi kule minyaka eyishumi edlule. Ukuze uthole okwengeziwe, thola Umbiko Weminyaka Eyishumi Yokuqala kwamabhizinisi YaseNtshonalanga. Isithombe esifakwe nguNick Fewings ku-Unsplash
I-OPay yaseNigeria ihamba phambili kuFintech landscape, ihola iCNBC kanye neStatista ezingeni lomhlaba njengebhizinisi elidijithali okuyilona kuphela eNigeria Elisesigabeni Sokukhokha ngobuchwepheshe. Ngempumelelo emangalisayo, i-OPay isifinyelele phambili endaweni ye-fintech yaseNigeria, yathola isikhundla esihlonishwayo njengengxenye yokukhokha edijithali yaseNigeria okuwukuphela kwayo kuCNBC kanye nezinga elihlonishwayo leStatista. Kusuka emhlabeni wonke, okuhlanganisa izinhlobonhlobo zezicelo zezezimali, iCNBC; inethiwekhi kamabonakude edijithali yomhlaba wonke nehloniphekile yamahora angu-24 enikeza bukhoma, ulwazi lwemakethe yezezimali yomhlaba wonke kanye nezinhlelo, kanye nefemu eyaziwayo ezimele yocwaningo lwemakethe iStatista ibambisene ukuze iqondise uhlu olubanzi lwezinkampani ezihamba phambili ekusunguleni imikhiqizo namisebenzi yezezimali afakwe ubuchwepheshe obusha. Umzamo wabo wokubambisana ukhiqize inhlanganisela yezinkampani eziphezulu ezingu-200 ze-fintech, zisebenzisa indlela echazwe ngokucophelela yokuhlola ukusebenza kwezinkampani kuzo zonke izinkomba ezibalulekile, okuhlanganisa umthamo wabasebenzisi, amanani okwenziwayo, kanye nemali engenayo. Izinkampani ezifakiwe zihlukaniswe ngokucophelela zaba izingxenye eziyisishiyagalolunye ezihlukene: i-neo-banking, izinkokhelo zedijithali, izimpahla zedijithali, ukuhlelwa kwezimali kwedijithali, ukuphathwa kwengcebo yedijithali, enye indlela yokuxhaswa ngemali, enye indela yokuboleka, izixazululo zebhange ledijithali, nezixazululo zebhizinisi ledijithali. Uhlu lubonise ukuthandwa kwePaypal, iRevolut, iWISE, nezinye izinkampani ezinkulu esikhaleni sefintech emhlabeni jikelele. I-OPay ivele phakathi kwesigaba sokukhokha ngobuchwepheshe salolu hlelo oludumile. Isidingo esikhulayo sezixazululo zokukhokha kwedijithali ezingenamthungo eNigeria sikhanyise umkhondo we-OPay, siyibeka njengenkundla eshesha kakhulu, evikelekile, nethembekile yazo zonke izinhlobo zemisebenzi yezezimali. Lokhu kuqashelwa komhlaba wonke kuqinisekisa ukuzibophezela kwethu ekuguquleni isimo sokukhokha kwedijithali eNigeria nangale kwalokho,” kuphawula u-Adekunle Adeyemi, INhloko Yezokumaketha kwa-OPay. "Kukhombisa lokho ebesizimisele ukukwenza njengenkampani, nalokho amathimba ethu abesebenza ngokuzikhandla ukukufeza.
Siyaziqhenya ngempela ngokuba yizibani ezikhanyisayo ekusunguleni nasekusebenzeni kube lula embonini ye-fintech yaseNigeria, futhi le mpumelelo iqinisa ukuzinikela kwethu, kanye nokuqina kwendlela yethu engapheli yokugxilisa amakhasimende," engeza. Esikhathini sezinxushunxushu ezinkulu emkhakheni we-fintech, ukushoda kwezimali, kanye nokwanda kwezindlela zokunciphisa izindleko, i-OPay iqondise imizamo yayo ekwakheni imikhiqizo nemisebenzi ajwayelekile ukuze isekele futhi inikeze amakhasimende amandla kuyilapho inikeza ulwazi lwamakhasimende oluhlukile.
IBankly Ichaza Kabusha Ukonga Kwabantu Kwansuku Zonke Uyazi ukuthi bathi abantu abangafani bayathandana? Hhayi-ke, leyo yindlela ephelele yokuchaza ubungane phakathi kwami ​​​​noSusan, unguzakwethu obalulekile empilweni yami yonke. Mina noSusan sihlukene kakhulu, futhi lokho kuhluka bekulokhu kungashintshi phakathi nobungane bethu obucishe bube yiminyaka eyishumi. Nakuba ngivame ukwamukela isimo sengqondo sokungakhathali nesizenzakalelayo, uSusan uyisibonelo somuntu ozolile, ocophelelayo. Uneso elimangalisayo lemininingwane kanye nomuzwa wokuhleleka adalwe nawo. Naphezu kwezimo zethu ezihlukene, mina noSusan sinothando olufanayo lokonga imali. Sivame ukuxoxa ngezindlela ezihlukahlukene zokuphatha izimali zethu, futhi inselele yethu yakamuva ibibaluleke kakhulu – ukuhlela nokongela umgubho ozayo wosuku lokuzalwa lukanina lweminyaka engama-50. Umndeni wawunqume ukubeka lokhu njengengqophamlando umcimbi okhethekile. Nokho, nakuba izingane zakubo zazimagange ukunikela kulo mcimbi, wayenejoko lokuphatha le minikelo ngendlela efanele.
Ucabange ukuphinde avakashele i-"Ajo", isiko leminyaka elidala lokonga umphakathi. Le ndlela yokonga ibambe indlela elula yokuhlanganisa imali yomgubho. Nokho, wayazi ngokuhlangenwe nakho kwakhe ukuthi le ndlela yayinamaphutha, futhi ukukhwabanisa kwakuvamile. Ukwethula izingane zakubo eqenjini elithi “Ajo” kwakuyingozi. Uma othile ehamba neminikelo yakhe, kungase kubangele ukungqubuzana phakathi kwakhe nezingane zakubo. Kwakumele athole enye indlela. Ukufuna kukaSusan isixazululo kwamholela e-Bankly Microfinance Bank. Banikeze iGroup Savings kuhlelo lokusebenza lweBankly elenza i-"Ajo" yendabuko ibe eyesimanjemanje. Kwakufana nebhuloho elixhumanisa umoya womphakathi wokonga nokusebenziseka kalula kwamathuluzi edijithali. Ngalesi sici, uSusan wayekwazi ukuhlanganisa izingane zakubo ngokuzethemba ukuze zongele umcimbi womndeni ozayo.
Isici seBankly's Group Savings siyindlela entsha yokonga edala ukubonakala obala nokuziphendulela. Ihlanganisa ukufinyeleleka, isixhumi esibonakalayo esisebenziseka kalula, kanye nokugcizelela obala ukuze kunikeze abantu abafana noSusan indlela yokuphuma lapho bedinga ukulondolozela izidingo ezibalulekile. Isici seGroup Savings siphinde sinikeze isilinganiso senzalo saminyaka yonke esingu-15% esinqwabelene nsuku zonke, sinikeza ithuba lokukhula okuzinzile, okuqhubekayo ngokuhamba kwesikhathi. Akugcini lapho. Abasebenzisi bangasetha amashejuli okonga, amanani aqondiwe, namadethi okuvuthwa ohlelo lwabo lokonga lweqembu, okukhuthaza umuzwa wobunye bezezimali kanye nomthwalo wemfanelo okwabelwana ngawo. Ukudala obala nakakhulu, isici seGroup Savings sihlonyiselwe ukunikeza amalungu izaziso ezisheshayo zamadiphozithi nokuhoxiswa kwemali, ukuqinisekisa ukuthi wonke umuntu uhlala enolwazi, okusiza ukunikeza induduzo kwabanikelayo nokwakha ukwethembana phakathi kweqembu. Ngokuvumelana nomgomo wayo, iBankly Microfinance Bank izinikele ekulungiseni kabusha isimo sezezimali futhi inikeze amandla abantu abafana noSusan ngokusebenzisa izici zomkhiqizo ezibhekana nezinselele zezimali zansuku zonke. Baguqula umbono wokonga usuka emsebenzini, ube indlela yokuphila esiza abantu ukuthi bathole ukukhula komuntu siqu, umndeni, kanye nebhizinisi. Ukuze uthole ulwazi olwengeziwe mayelana Nesici Sokulondoloza Iqembu Le-Bankly, sicela uchofe lapha ukuze ubuke ividiyo yedemo, noma vakashela ku-bankly.ng.
ILagos State Senior Model College iBadore Iwina Umncintiswano weProjekthi iCommunity STEAM Ehlelelwe Izikole Zomphakathi e-Lagos IChevron Nigeria Limited (iCNL) ngokubambisana neNigerian National Petroleum Limited (iNNPCL) ngokubambisana neSTEAM Fun Fest bahlele uMqhudelwano weProject iCommunity STEAM. Abafundi abangu-500 abavela ezikoleni zomphakathi ngaphansi kweSifunda Semfundo Sesifunda Sesithathu saseLagos muva nje babambe iqhaza emqhudelwaneni okhuthazayo weSTEAM okuhloswe ngawo ukuthuthukisa amakhono okucabanga ngokujulile nokuxazulula izinkinga phakathi kwabafundi abasebasha. IProject iCommunity ehlelwe yiSTEAM Fun Fest ngokubambisana neLagos State Education District III, iSTEAM UP Lagos iqale ngeseshini yokuqeqesha othisha abangu-20 kanye namasonto amane (4) okuqeqeshwa kokuklama ukucabanga kwabafundi ezikoleni eziyi-10 kuso sonke isifunda. Isigaba sokugcina somncintiswano senzeka ngoMgqibelo, ziyi-8 kuNtulikazi wezi-2023, lapho izikole ezikhethiwe zethula amaphrojekthi azo esibonelo kuphaneli yamajaji avelele, ochwepheshe bezemfundo, nezinhlangano ezixhasayo. ILagos State Senior Model College, iBadore iwine umncintiswano weSTEAM ngephrojekthi yabo eyingqayizivele yebhodlela Lamanzi Ashisayo Ebhethri-Powered, ithole umklomelo omkhulu we-1,000,000 naira. IKuramo Senior College High School, eVictoria Island ithole isikhundla sesibili ngephrojekthi yekhamera yeWireless CCTV ehlaba umxhwele, yawina umklomelo we-500,000 naira. IKing Ado Senior High School ithole umklomelo wendawo yesi-3 we-250,000 naira ngephrojekthi yabo yeWooden Walking Way, kuyilapho iGirls Senior Academy Lagos Island, ne-Educational Learning App, kanye ne-Government Senior College Ikoyi ngephrojekthi yayo yeSolar Powered Electric Bulbs zombili ziwine i-100,000 naira, ngokulandelana njengabawine indawo yesi-4 neyesi-5. Wonke amaphrojekthi ayi-10 abonise ubuhlakani nokuzibophezela ekubhekaneni nezinselele ezibucayi. NgokukaJadesola Adedeji omunye wabahleli beSTEAM Fun Fest, "Siyaziqhenya kakhulu ngempumelelo ekhonjiswe yibo bonke ababambiqhaza.
Emqhudelwaneni walo nyaka we-STEAM, inhloso yethu eyinhloko bekuwukuvusa intshiseko ejulile yokufunda, ukuxazulula izinkinga, nokusungula izinto ezintsha phakathi kwemiqondo yabancane yaseLagos. Ugqozi esiluthole entshisekweni yabafundi lusishukumisele ukuba silwele okwengeziwe, ngethemba lokwandisa lolu hlelo ezikoleni hhayi kuphela eLagos kodwa kulo lonke elaseNigeria." Ubonge iChevron Nigeria Limited, iNigerian National Petroleum Limited (iNNPCL), kanye neTexaco Nigeria Outer Shelf Limited (iTNOS), ngokumeseka noxhaso lwabo, oluqinisekise impumelelo yomncintiswano weSTEAM. "Ukuzinikela kwabo ekukhuliseni amathalente abafundi abasebasha kanye nokuthuthukisa imfundo eLagos kwaziswa kakhulu," engeza. ISTEAM Fun Fest iwubambiswano lwezinkampani ezine (4) ezihamba phambili ze-Edtech - i-9ijakids, iSTEM-METS, i-Edufun Technik, neSabiteach.
Ukunika amandla ama-SME akwa-Kwara: ITrade Lenda SME Fair Partners neKwara State Government And DTO Foundation For Lasting Impact ITrade Lenda SME Fair iyaziqhenya ukumemezela ukuthi ibambisene noHulumeni Wesifunda Sakwara kanye ne-Dr. Toba Oloyede (iDTO) Foundation ukusekela ukukhula nokuthuthukiswa Kwamabhizinisi Amancane Naphakathi (amaSME) esifundazweni ngokuxhaswa kwe-7 ethembisayo. osomabhizinisi, abazobe bebambe iqhaza kwiTrade Lenda SME Fair ehlonishwayo eSifundazweni SaseLagos. Ihlelelwe ukuthi ibe ziyi-19 kuNcwaba, iTrade Lenda SME Fair ingumbuthano omkhulukazi waseNigeria wamaSME, abaholi bezimboni, nabamele uhulumeni. Lolu xhaso lubonisa ukuzinikela kweKwara State kanye neDTO Foundation ekunikezeni amandla amabhizinisi endawo kanye nokugqugquzela inqubekelaphambili yezomnotho esifundeni. Yomibili le nhlangano iyalibona iqhaza elibalulekile elibanjwe ama-SME ekuqhubekiseni ukukhula komnotho nokudala amathuba emisebenzi. Ngokuxhasa labo somabhizinisi abayi-7 abakhethekile ukuze babambe iqhaza kuTrade Lenda SME Fair, Kwara State kanye neDTO Foundation ihlose ukubahlinzeka ngenkundla ebalulekile yokukhombisa imikhiqizo yabo emisha namasevisi. ITrade Lenda SME Fair inikeza ithuba eliyingqayizivele kosomabhizinisi ukuthi baxhumane nochwepheshe bemboni, abangaba ozakwethu, kanye nezilaleli ezihlukahlukene zamakhasimende angaba khona. Ngokubamba iqhaza kuTrade Lenda SME Fair, osomabhizinisi abaxhasiwe bazothola imininingwane ebalulekile, basungule ubudlelwano obubalulekile bebhizinisi, futhi bandise amanethiwekhi abo. Abahambele umcimbi bangalindela ukubona ama-SME ahlukahlukene anemikhiqizo emisha, kanye nezaphulelo ezikhethekile kule mikhiqizo. Ukubhalisela iTrade Lenda Fair 2023 kusaqhubeka, futhi sikhuthaza abantu ukuthi bathenge amathikithi abo manje.
Thola amathikithi akho lapha: https://tix.africa/discover/tradelenda Mayelana neTrade Lenda ITrade Lenda yibhange ledijithali elihamba phambili elizinikele ekunikezeni amandla amabhizinisi amancane naphakathi nendawo (amaSME) eNigeria. Ngokusebenzisa uchungechunge olubanzi lwezinsizakalo zezezimali, okuhlanganisa ukubolekwa kwemali, ukonga kanye nomshwalense, iTrade Lenda ihlose ukuthuthukisa ukukhula komnotho, ukuzimela ngokwezimali nokudala uhlelo lwezemvelo oluchumayo olusekela impumelelo yamaSME.
Ukwakha Ikusasa: Isikole Sebhizinisi saseLagos sisingathe iNgqungquthela Yaso Yokuqala Ye-Tech Founders Isikole esihlonishwayo saseLagos Business School (LBS) sizosingatha ababambiqhaza be-ecosystem yezobuchwepheshe baseNigeria eNgqungqutheleni yabasunguli beTech yokuqala e-Campus Auditorium e-Ajah, eLagos, ngoLwesine, ziyi-17 kuNcaba wezi-2023. Le ngqungquthela enendikimba ethi “Ukwakha Ikusasa: Ubuchwepheshe, Ukuqamba Okusha, kanye Nosomabhizinisi” ihlose ukuhlanganisa abasunguli bezobuchwepheshe, abatshalizimali, abaholi bezimboni kanye nongoti, abenzi bezinqubomgomo, osolwazi, kanye nabathandi bezobuchwepheshe ndawonye ukuze bahlele ikusasa lesikhala sobuchwepheshe saseNigeria. Ekhuluma ne-Techpoint yase-Africa ngokuthi kungani i-LBS ihlela le ngqungquthela, u-Segun Thomas, iNhloko, Ukuthuthukiswa Komkhiqizo kanye Ne-Innovation e-LBS, uthe, "Sibonile ukuthi abantu abaningi bangena endaweni yokuqala yobuchwepheshe, kodwa okuyisisekelo sisashoda. Abanye abasunguli bangabasebenza ngobuchwepheshe, kodwa ukuqonda ukuhlobana phakathi kokuphathwa kwebhizinisi nobuchwepheshe kusenzima kwabanye. Umgomo we-LBS walo mcimbi ukwenza sikwazi ukuqhamuka nezixazululo ezihambisana nezidingo zalezi ziqalo ngoba zinenqwaba yezinselelo. Ukuze i-LBS iqhamuke nemikhiqizo nezixazululo mayelana nalokhu, kudingeka siqale siqonde izinkinga ababhekana nazo, futhi sidinga ukuletha ukuhlangana phakathi kwabo bonke abasebenza ohlelweni. " Ubuye wengeza ngokuthi bazama ukwakha indawo lapho izidingo zabatshalizimali, abasunguli, kanye nabantu abazolawula indawo, bese bekwazi uthola amaphuzu abalulekile angabaphethe kahle abasebenza kwezobuchwepheshe. Ongakulindela Engqungqutheleni YeTech Founders' Amathuba okuxhumana asezingeni eliphezulu: Le ngqungquthela ihlinzeka ngenkundla yabahambele lo mcimbi ukuthi baxhumane nabathatha izinqumo nabasunguli.
Ukubavumela ukuthi bakhe ubudlelwano nabanye osomabhizinisi. Imininingwane evela kubaholi bezimboni: Ababambiqhaza kufanele futhi balindele ukuzwa kubatshalizimali, abasunguli, abenzi benqubomgomo, nabanye abaholi bezimboni, phakathi kwabanye. Kufanele balindele izingxoxo eziphathelene nezigaba zokuthuthuka , kusukela ekukhuphuleni imali kuye ekutholeni ulwazi ngokuthi abatshalizimali bafunani, indlela yokuphatha elindelekile, okubaluleke kakhulu nokusimama embonini yabo. Igalelo engxoxweni: Abahlanganyeli bazothola ithuba lokuzibandakanya ezingxoxweni futhi babambe iqhaza ekuthuthukisweni kwe-ecosystem yezobuchwepheshe e-Nigeria. Izixazululo eziphelele ezivela ku-LBS: Abahleli, i-Lagos Business School, bahlela ukuthuthukisa izixazululo eziholwa ochwepheshe ngokusekelwe ekuqondeni nasekuxoxweni phakathi nengqungquthela. Okulindeleke ukuba bakhulume engqungqutheleni yilaba abaholi bemboni abalandelayo: U-Olugbenga Agboola, umsunguli kanye ne-CEO, uFlutterwave; UDkt Ola Brown, Umsunguli kanye noMphathi Omkhulu, i-HealthCap Africa; UDkt Bosun Tijani, umsunguli kanye ne-CEO, i-CcHub; u-Oswald Guobadia, owayenguMsizi Omkhulu Okhethekile KaMongameli mayelana Nokuguqulwa Kwedijithali; Goke Olubisi, Umsunguli kanye noMphathi Omkhulu, iHelium Health; USolwazi u-Olayinka David West, uMdidiyeli Ohlangene, iSikole Sebhizinisi saseLagos, phakathi kwamanye amaflaya aphezulu aphawulekayo. Ukuze bathamele Ingqungquthela Yabasunguli Bezobuchwepheshe, abantu abanentshisekelo bangabhalisa besebenzisa isixhumanisi esinikeziwe: https://bit.ly/tech-founders-summit. Amathuba oxhaso nawemibukiso ayatholakala kumabhizinisi anentshisekelo yokubonisa izisombululo zawo engqungqutheleni. Ezinye zezinzuzo ezivulekele amabhizinisi ukuchayeka okuphambili, ukwanda kwamathuba okuxhumana, nokukhiqiza okuphambili, phakathi kokunye.
I-Raven Bank Inika Abafundi Abangu-400,000 Amandla Nge-Cutting-Edge ‘Feather Internet’ - I-WiFi yamahhala ekhempasini Ngohlelo lwe-Feather Internet Initiative, iRaven Bank isiqalile ukufaka isandla emkhakheni wezemfundo ngokuhlinzeka nge-WIFI yamahhala kuwo wonke amakhempasi aseNigeria. Umklomelo we-BAFI, 2022 Neo Bank of the Year, wethule Uhlelo NgoLwesihlanu ngesikhathi kwethulwa okokuqala kwe-Raven Feather Internet e-Ignatius Ajuru University, eRumolumeli, ePort Harcourt, e-Rivers State. Ebungaza lo msebenzi oncomekayo, u-Uchenna Nnodim, oyiSikhulu Esiphezulu se-Raven Bank, uveze ukuthi lesi yisinyathelo sokuqala esibheke emgomweni waleli bhange wokunikeza amandla abafundi abangaphezu kwama-400,000 kuwo wonke amanyuvesi kahulumeni ezweni ngokuthola mahhala i-inthanethi ye-broadband esheshayo ukuze kuthuthukiswe ezemfundo. Udalule ukuthi lesi sinyathelo siqhamuke njengekhambi lesu lokubhekana nokuhlukana okukhona kwedijithali okubangelwa ukufinyelela okulinganiselwe kwe-inthanethi, okuyisithiyo abafundi abaningi baseNigeria ababhekana nakho. Ethathela ohambweni lwakhe lwezemfundo, ubalule ngezithiyo ayebhekana nazo ukuze athole ulwazi ku-inthanethi. Lokhu, kuhambisana nokuzibophezela kukaRaven ekuthuthukiseni ulwazi lwezezimali phakathi kwe-Gen Z kanye nezinkulungwane zeminyaka, kukhuthaze ukubaluleka kwalolu hlelo lombono. Uthe, “Sibone ukuthi cishe amaphesenti angama-70 abafundi baseNigeria abanayo i-inthanethi. Lena inombolo enkulu. Sazi kakhulu futhi ukuthi ezikhathini zanamuhla umthamo wemininingo nolwazi olukhona ku-inthanethi ngeke kugcizelelwe ngokweqile.”
"Ungakwazi ukufinyelela kunoma yiluphi ulwazi noma imininingo nge-inthanethi, ngakho ukufinyelela ku-inthanethi kubaluleke kakhulu ukuze uphumelele kwezemfundo futhi uphase izifundo kahle." UNnodim uphinde waphawula ukuthi ukwethulwa kokuqala kwe-IAUE kwakuyisinyathelo sokuqala salolu hlelo. “Ukwethulwa kwethu namuhla (ngoLwesihlanu) bekuyindawo yethu yokuqala, kodwa sinezinhlelo ezinkulu ngalo msebenzi. Sengike ngasho ukuthi sifuna ukufinyelela okungenani kubafundi abangama-400,000, futhi sesivele senza imephu yezinye izindawo ezingu-26 esizihlolayo ukuze sizikhulise.” “Sixoxisana nabaphathi balezi ezinye izindawo, ingxoxo ihamba kahle. Uhlelo lwethu wukwenza kulezi zindawo ngekota yesibili yowezi-2024,” engeza. Ukwethulwa ngokusemthethweni kwe-Raven Feather Internet kuqale ngomhlangano wokucobelelana ngolwazi othathe ihora lonke, ophethwe ngu-Raven CFO Chidinma Maduwesi, ohlanganisa izingxoxo ezithinta izihloko mayelana nokonga, ukutshalwa kwezimali, ezohwebo, nokunye. Iphaneli yomhlangano wokucobelelana ngolwazi ihlanganisa u-Uchenna Nnodim, i-CEO ye-Raven, i-Raven POS aggregator Benjamin Idisi, kanye no-Kelechi Godfrey, Uthisha Wezezimali wase-The Boardroom. Futhi abafundi bakhangwe engxenyeni yakamuva yomcimbi ngamaciko akhethiwe. Omunye obekhona emcimbini wokwethulwa nguSolwazi Okey Okechukwu, iPhini likaShansela we-Ignatius Ajuru University of Education.
Enkulumeni yakhe, utuse abaphathi beRaven ngomsebenzi wabo oyimpumelelo ekuqalisweni nasekusebenziseni uhlelo lwe-Feather Internet ekhempasini. siphinde sincoma ibhange ngokukhetha isikhungo sephrojekthi yokuhlola. Uphinde wakhuthaza abafundi ukuthi basebenzise i-internet yamahhala esikhungweni, wengeza ngokuthi i-inthanethi ayigcini nje ngokucebisa ezifundweni kodwa iphinde yenze bafundi bathole izinhlobonhlobo zamakhono empilo, ibanike amandla kulo lonke uhambo lwabo lokufunda nangale kwalokho. Eqinisekisa umthelela omkhulu we-Feather Internet, uNnodim uzwakalise ukuthi, “Lolu hlelo luqondiswe ngqo ukuba nomthelela osezingeni eliphezulu ezimpilweni zabafundi baseNigeria.” “Kuhloswe ngayo ukunikeza abafundi baseNigeria abangama-400,000 ukuba bathole i-inthanethi yamahhala nsuku zonke; lokhu ukwethulwa kwezintombi futhi endaweni eyodwa nje; sihlose ukuwenabela nakwamanye amaNyuvesi. Okubalulekile wukuqinisekisa ukuthi abafundi bayayithola i-inthanethi ukuze benze izifundo zabo, benze ucwaningo futhi bakwazi ukufinyelela kunoma yiluphi ulwazi abaluthandayo.” Ekhuluma ngombono waleli gama, waveza ukuthi izimpaphe zegwababa elikhulu, okuyisilwane esimele inkampani, zaqamba leli gama. Ligqugquzelwa ukushesha kwamaphiko alo, ithimba laqamba inethiwekhi eyeqa imingcele, lichaza kabusha ukusebenzisana kwedijithali ngezimpaphe zayo. Ukuze uthole okwengeziwe ngohlelo lwe-inthanethi lwe-Raven Bank oluguqulayo futhi ube yingxenye yalolu hambo oluyingqophamlando, landela i-Raven Bank ku-@theravenbank kuzo zonke izinkundla. Mayelana ne-Raven Bank: I-Raven Bank “iRaven” noma “i-RMFB” iyibhange ledijithali elihlinzeka ngezinsizakalo zezezimali ezisheshayo, ezivikelekile nezithembekile kubantu base-Afrika kusukela eNigeria.
I-“People’s Bank of Africa” - Ibhange iRaven lihamba phambili ekusunguleni izinto ezintsha, lizibophezele ekuchazeni kabusha ukuxhumana nemfundo ngohlelo lwayo lwe-Feather Internet olunombono. Ngokuzinikezela okungaguquki ekunikezeni abafundi amandla kanye nokuvala ukuhlukana kwedijithali, iRaven Bank ibona umhlaba lapho ubuchwepheshe bucebisa khona izimpilo futhi buqhubekisela phambili amaphupho. Landa uhlelo lokusebenza lwe-Raven Bank.
