I-Glovo yehlula i-Jumia Food, i-Bolt Food, abanye ukuba ngomunye wabalingani be-Chicken Republic eNigeria I-Glovo namuhla imemezele ubudlelwano obuzokwenza ukuthi ibe ngomunye wabalingani bokulethwa kwe-Chicken Republic eNigeria. Ubambiswano, oluqale ngoNcwaba, luzobona i-Chicken Republic isebenza ne-=Glovo, iqeda ubudlelwano ne-Jumia Food kanye ne-Bolt Food. Ngaphezu kwalokho, ubudlelwano bungasatshalaliswa eGhana, lapho zombili izinkampani sezivele zisebenza khona. ENigeria, i-Glovo njengamanje isebenza eLagos, Ibadan, nase-Abuja, lapho isebenza khona nezitolo ezingama-58 ze-Chicken Republic. Ngakolunye uhlangothi, iChicken Republic isebenza ngezitolo ezingaphezu kwama-300 kulo lonke elaseNigeria, futhi umuntu uyazibuza ukuthi ingabe lobu budlelwano buyisandulela sokwanda kwe-Glovo yonkana eNigeria. Kodwa-ke, abaphathi be-Glovo bebelokhu beqinisa isifiso sabo sokugxila eLagos, e-Ibadan nase-Abuja. U-Kofi Abunu, oyi-CEO ye-Food Concepts, uzwakalise ukuthi unethemba lokuthi ukubambisana kuzothuthukisa ulwazi lwamakhasimende abo futhi kuthuthukise ukudiliva, kuyilapho u-Lamide Akinola, iMenenja-Jikelele esanda kuqokwa ye-Glovo Nigeria, naye ezwakalise ukujabula ngokubambisana. “Kusukela ekusebenzisaneni kwethu okokuqala ne-Chicken Republic kuNhlaba wezi-2022, sikhombise amandla okuhlinzeka ngomsebenzi osheshayo nosezingeni eliphezulu kumakhasimende abo. Ngakho-ke, siyaziqhenya kakhulu ngokuthi iChicken Republic, i-QSR ehamba phambili eNigeria, ibubonile ubuchwepheshe bethu futhi yasikhetha, ”kusho u-Akinola.
Selokhu yangena emakethe yaseNigeria ngo-2021, i-Glovo ibilokhu izama ukunweba, namabhodi ezikhangiso kuwo wonke amadolobha asebenzayo. Ngesikhathi sokuvakasha ngoNhlaba wezi-2023, i-CEO ye-Glovo, u-Oscar Pierre wachaza ukuthi inhloso yenkampani ukuba ngumdlali ovelele emkhakheni wezohwebo osheshayo waseNigeria. Kakade, i-Glovo Nigeria iqashe abathumeli bezincwadi abangaphezu kuka-1,000 kanye nezisebenzi ezingaba ngu-50 ezweni. Ukwengeza, uPierre udalule ukuthi ukuqalisa kusebenzise imali engaphezu kwezigidi ezintathu zamaRandi eNigeria, njengoba achaza ukuthi inhloso eyinhloko yenkampani ukukhulisa isisekelo samakhasimende nokuthuthukisa izinsizakalo zayo. Umphathi wezwe lase-Glovo Nigeria ulindele ukuthi isidingo sokulethwa okudingekayo siqhubeke naphezu kokukhuphuka kwezindleko zokusebenza
U-X (owayekade engu-Twitter) ufuna ukukhoka izimali zakho zezomthetho Ngesikhathi kuvela izindaba zokuqokwa kuka-Bosun Tijani njengongqongqoshe, i-tech ecosystem yaseNigeria yajabula kakhulu. I-CcHub ka-Tijani, isikhungo sezobuchwepheshe esikhulu kunazo zonke e-Nigeria, sibambe iqhaza elikhulu ekukhiqizeni izinkampani ezinkulu zezwe kusukela ekuqaleni kwayo eYaba, eLagos. Ukuba nomuntu onjengoTijani omele i-ecosystem ezingeni longqongqoshe kunomqondo ophusile njengoba eqonda usizi lwababambe iqhaza kulomkhakha. Nokho ukuqokwa kwakhe sekuke kwaba nezinsolo ngabamthatha njengomuntu ongathandi izwe ngenxa yemibhalo ayibhale ngeNigeria ku-X (owayeyiTwitter). Kuyinkinga ukuba igama lakho libandakanyeke "ne-Nigeria" . Khohla ukuthanda izwe umzuzwana - lokubandakanyeka kuwukumosha amandla nje. Iphasipothi yesibili yangaphandle ayanele ukususa "isono." Uxolisile ngesikhathi ehlolwa njengongqongqoshe wachaza nezimo eziholele ekutheni abhale ezikhundleni zokuxhumana. Mina nozakwethu sike saxabana.
"Bekungamele axolise ngoba akonanga lutho." "Kungcono abeke umsebenzi wakhe ngaphezu kokuzicabangela yena." Wawungenzenjani ukube ubunguTijani? Qala uMsombuluko wakho ngalezi zindaba: Uhlelo luka-X lokumboza izikweletu zakho zezomthetho I-Wema + Nigeria izokwethula izindawo zobuchwepheshe Ukudilizwa emsebenzini kwe-Big Cabal Media U-X uzokhokhela izindleko zakho zezomthetho uma uxoshwa emsebenzini wakho NgeSonto, zi-6 kuNcwaba wezi 2023, uMphathi we-X (owayekade engu-Twitter), u-Elon Musk, wabhala, "Uma umqashi wakho eye wakuphatha ngokungafanele ngenxa yokuthumela noma ukuthanda okuthile kule nkundla, sizokuxhasa ngokukhokhela isikweletu sakho sezomthetho. Akunamkhawulo. Ngicela usazise."
Ingabe u-X akekho enkingeni yezikweletu? Ukusabela kwami ​​kokuqala kule-tweet, ngisho, okuthunyelwe, bekuwukuthi, "Lol" nayi imbangela. U-X okwamanje ukweleta u-$136,250 werenti engakhokhelwanga kuma-HQ ayo e-San Francisco, e-USA. Umbiko ovela ku-New York Times uze ubonise ukuthi u-X ubengakhokhi irenti kuwo wonke amahhovisi awo omhlaba njengendlela yokunciphisa izindleko zabo. Akugcini lapho: U-X noMusk njengamanje babhekene namacala okumangalela ama-dollar ayizigidi eziyi-14 ngezikweletu ezingakhokhiwe. Abasebenzi abaxoshwe ngaphandle kokunikezwa izimali zabo nabo babavulela icala lezigidi ezingama- $500. Hlehla: Uma ubheka emuva kwezinye zezinto uMusk azenzile, akubhalile kumveza njengomuntu ongenalo iqiniso. NgoLwezi wezi-2022, waxosha unjiniyela we-X owamlungisa ngephutha alenza mayelana no-X. Abasebenzi abaningana nabo babhala ngokuxoshwa kwabo ngokudalula izitatimende ezingalungile zikaMusk ngo-X. Linda: Ngaphambi kokuba ubhale okungase kukuxoshise, khumbula ukuthi ubani u-Musk nokuthi unokusho into ngolunye usuku bese eshintsha umqondo wakhe ngokulandelayo.
I-Big Cabal Media yehlisa abasebenzi ngo-19% IBig Cabal Media, okuyinkampani yeTechCabal, i-Zikoko ne-Citizen, ikhiphe u-19% wabasebenzi bayo ngenxa "yezimo ezibucayi zemakethe." Kumemo yangaphakathi eya kubasebenzi, iCEO yeBig Cabal Media, uTomiwa Aladekomo, uthe, “Isinqumo sanamuhla asimnandi, kodwa labo abasishiyayo bangaziqhenya ngomsebenzi wabo kanye nomthelela ababe nawo. Kuthina esisele, yazini ukuthi sizibophezele njengakuqala ekwakheni elinye lamabhizinisi abaluleke kakhulu kwezezindaba ezwenikazi. Lo msebenzi usaqhubeka, futhi ungaziqhenya ngokufaka isandla kuwo.” I-Citizen, ushicilelo olusha lwenkampani olugxile kwezokuphatha nepolitiki luzothinteka kakhulu ngokudilizwa. Le nkampani ithe, "Ezindaweni ezihlukile zebhizinisi, besihlose ukuthi izakhamizi zibe nezinyanga eziyi-12-18 ukuze zithole imithombo eqhubekayo yemali engenayo." Nakuba iqophe ukukhula kwemali engenayo ngonyaka ngo-180% ekupheleni kwe-H1, amaqiniso ezomnotho afana nokwehla kwezimali kanye nokwehla komnotho, kunomthelela emalini engenayo. I-Big Cabal Media manje isizogxila ku-TechCabal ne-TechCabal Insights kanye ne-Zikoko. I-Nigeria ibambisene ne-Wema Bank ukwethula izindawo zedijithali
Uhulumeni wobumbano waseNigeria ubambisene ne-Wema Bank ukwethula izindawo zedijithali ezifundazweni eziyisikhombisa. Ngokwesitatimende sika-Olusola Abiola, onguMqondisi Wolwazi wePhini likaMengameli waseNigeria, uKashim Shettima, lezi zikhungo zizohlomisa intsha eyisigidi kuleli ngamakhono edijithali. Udalule ukuthi abamele ibhange iWema kanye nephini likamengameli baqhamuke nalolu hlelo ngemuva komhlangano wakamuva obuse-Abuja. Iqala ngeLagos ne-Borno States: Uhlu lokuqala lezindawo izokwethulwa eLagos nase-Borno States kanti ezinye izifundazwe, okubandakanya i-Oyo ne-Cross River, zizothola ezazo kamuva. Ibizwa ngokuthi i-FGN/ALAT Digital kanye ne-SkillNnovation Hub, izosekela "intsha enolwazi ngezobuchwepheshe nenentshisekelo ejulile futhi efisa ukuletha intuthuko yezobuchwepheshe, ngokubanikeza izixazululo zezimali, ukuqeqeshwa kanye nobambiswano lwamasu."
I-FG Partners Wema Bank izosungula izindawo ezidijithali nezithuthukisa amakhono Kuwo wonke amazwe I-Wema Bank, ibhange elihamba phambili e-Nigeria, ibambisene noHulumeni Wombuso waseNigeria ukuze kusungulwe izindawo ezidijithali futhi zokuthuthukisa amakhono kuzo zonke izifundazwe ezweni, ngenhloso yokuthuthukisa intsha eyisigidi ngamakhono edijithali namanye afanelekile. Lolu hlelo, olwaziwa nge-FGN/ALAT Digital kanye ne-SkillNovation Hub, kwavunyelwana ngalo ngesikhathi somhlangano phakathi kwabamele ibhange kanye nePhini likaMongameli u-Kashim Shettima e-Abuja, okuhambisana nokuzibophezela kukaMongameli u-Bola Tinubu ekwakheni amathuba emisebenzi eminingi yedijithali kubantu abasha baseNigeria. Eminyakeni edlule, i-Wema Bank ibe yingqalabutho ekuguquleni idijithali embonini yamabhange, izibophezele ekukhuthazeni isiko lokusungula izinto ezintsha, ukufunda nokuthuthukiswa kwamakhono. OnguMdidiyeli kanye neSikhulu Esiphezulu sebhange iWema, uMoruf Oseni, uthi lolu hlelo olusha lwenzelwe ukuguqula indlela osomabhizinisi abasebasha nabasebenzi abasebenzisana ngayo nobuchwepheshe, amabhizinisi kanye nokuthuthukiswa kwamakhono. "I-Digital & SkillNovation Hub ibonisa ukuzinikela kwethu ekukhuthazeni i-ecosystem ephumelelayo enikeza amandla Osomabhizinisi Abasebasha bakwa-Tech-Savvy, Osomabhizinisi Abasebasha ngokweminyaka, kanye Nabasebenzi Abasebasha, abathuthukisa umnotho nenqubekelaphambili esimeme ezweni lonke. Le nkundla emaphakathi izohlanganisa amathuluzi edijithali aphambili, ubuchwepheshe, kanye nezinsiza ukuze kuqondiswe imisebenzi yedijithali, ukubambisana, kanye nokwabelana ngolwazi," kwengeza u-Oseni. Ngokwesitatimende esivela ehhovisi lePhini Likamongameli, i-Digital & SkillNovation Hub izoqale ivulwe e-Lagos nase-Borno States, bese kulandela i-Katsina, i-Cross River, i-Anambra, i-Oyo, ne-Kano. Lolu hlelo luhlose ukuhlinzeka ngezixazululo zezezimali, ukuqeqeshwa, kanye nokufinyelela ekubambisaneni kwamasu, ukunika amandla abasebenzi abasebasha ukuthi babe ingxenye ebalulekile yabasebenzi baseNigeria, ikakhulukazi labo abalethwe nge-NYSC. Isitatimende sengeza ngokuthi ongoti bazoluleka ama-SME angu-500,000 kulo lonke elaseNigeria, okuyilapho abaqeqeshi bezohlinzeka ngoqeqesho futhi bathuthukise amakhono okukhula kwezamabhizinisi.
Ngaphansi kwalolu hlelo, izibonelelo zizonikezwa ngohlelo lokusebenzisana phakathi kukaHulumeni Wombuso kanye ne-WEMA Bank, kwabelwa izigidi ezingu-N500 ezizonikezwa ama-SME namaTechpreneurs. Izindawo ze-FGN/ALAT Digital SkillNovation zizogxila ekuqeqesheni abantu abasha abayizigidi eziyinkulungwane kwezobunjiniyela bezinhlelo zekhompyutha, ukuphathwa kwemikhiqizo, ukuhlaziya ibhizinisi, ukusebenzisa ikhompyutha emkhathini, nokuklama umkhiqizo, kusetshenziswa izinsiza ezikhethekile.
I-ISACA Isebenzisana ne-Onitsha Business School ukuze Ithuthukise Abafundi Ngamakhono Nemininingwane Edingeka Emhlabeni Wonke Inhlangano yezobuchwepheshe yomhlaba wonke i-ISACA kanye ne-Onitsha Business School, eseSifundazweni sase-Anambra eNigeria bamemezele ukubambisana kwezemfundo ukuze kunikezwe abafundi ithuba lokuthuthukisa ulwazi lwabo lokufunda ngohlelo oluyingqayizivele olunikeza amakhono adingekayo kanye nemininingwane ukuze baqale umsebenzi wokucwaninga nge-IT, Ezokuphepha ngotwamkhathi , ubuchwepheshe obusafufusa, ukubusa kanye nobumfihlo. I-ISACA ithuthukise Uhlelo Lobambiswano Lwezemfundo ukuze inikeze amathuba okufunda okuthuthukisiwe ngokusebenzisa amakhono adingekayo ukuze kuqalwe umsebenzi we-IT, ukuhlolwa kwe-IT, ubungozi, ukuphepha, imininingo, ukuvikeleka ku-inthanethi, ukubusa, noma ubumfihlo. Izenzo zethu zihambisana nokuzibophezela okujulile kwe-ISACA kokutshala izimali ezinhlelweni zomhlaba wonke kanye nobambiswano olunikeza izinzuzo eziphezulu zezenhlalakahle, ukuhlanganiswa, nokulingana, kobubili ngaphakathi kwemboni nangale kwayo. Njengengxenye yalokhu kubambisana, i-ISACA izohlinzeka ngobulungu kanye nezitifiketi zayo zezamabhizinisi kanye nezitifiketi zezobuchwepheshe obusafufusa okuhlanganisa Umcwaningimabhuku Oqinisekisiwe Wezinhlelo Zolwazi (CISA), Ugunyazwe Ku-Risk and Information Systems Control (CRISC), Umphathi Wokuphepha Kolwazi Oluqinisekisiwe (CISM), Ubumfihlo Beimininingo Eqinisekisiwe. I-Solutions Engineer (CDPSE), Certified in Emerging Technology (CET), Information Technology Certified Associate (ITCA) nokunye okwengeziwe ngentengo enesaphulelo kubafundi base-Onitsha Business School. "Njengenhlangano yokufunda yomhlaba wonke, i-ISACA ikholelwa emandleni okwakha ukuxhumana kanye nomphakathi ukwandisa umthelela weminikelo yethu yemfundo kubafundi nongoti esisebenzela bona," kusho uJeff Angle, uMqondisi Omkhulu we-ISACA, Ukuthuthukiswa Kwezemfundo Nokusebenza Kwabasebenzi. “Sijabulile ngokubambisana kwethu ne-Onitsha Business School kanye nezinyathelo esingazithatha ndawonye ukuze sivule izindlela ezintsha zokufunda nezindlela zomsebenzi zabafundi futhi sizibandakanye ezingxoxweni ezinengqondo mayelana nokwethembeka kwedijithali.” “I-Onitsha Business School (OBS) iwuhlelo olwenzelwe ukusebenzisa izinsiza zezemfundo ezifanele ukuthuthukisa nokuqeqesha inqwaba yamathalente ezentengiselwano, ezezimboni kanye nezamabhizinisi edolobheni eliseduze nelase-Onitsha eSifundazweni sase-Anambra, eNigeria. Eminyakeni engaphezu kwengama-50, i-ISACA isithuthukise amathalente ahamba phambili, ongoti abaziwayo nokufunda kwezobuchwepheshe, ezemfundo, kanye nomphakathi ukuze bathuthuke emisebenzini yabo futhi baguqule izinhlangano zabo. Sijabule ngalobu budlelwano ne-ISACA kanye nomthelela woguquko oluzoba nawo kongoti bezokwethembeka kwedijithali esifundeni esiseNingizimu neMpumalanga eNigeria, "kusho uSolwazi Olusegun 'Dapo Sogbesan, uMqondisi Jikelele, e-Onitsha Business School.
Ukwengeza kulokhu, njengengxenye yalokhu kubambisana, umnyango kanye namalungu e-Onitsha Business School kanye ne-ISACA Abuja Chapter bazohlanganyela ndawonye kumihlangano yokucobelelana ngolwazi, izinkomfa neminye imicimbi ukukhuthaza ukwabelana ngemibono, ulwazi kanye nemikhuba emihle yokusebenza. “Njengengxenye yohlelo lwesu lesahluko se-Abuja, ithimba lethu labaxhumanisi nobudlelwano bezemfundo liye lathuthukisa indlela ebukeka ngayo i-ISACA njengomholi wezobuchwepheshe kwezamabhizinisi phakathi komphakathi wezemfundo eNtshonalanga ne-Afrika futhi lakhulisa ukuqwashisana nokusebenzisana phakathi kwezemfundo nabasebenzi. Sijabule kakhulu ukugubha ubudlelwano kwezemfundo bokuqala kobuningi obuke babakhona e-sub-saharan Africa,” kusho u-Emmanuel Omoke, uMongameli we-ISACA Abuja Chapter. Mayelana ne-ISACA I-ISACA® (www.isaca.org) umphakathi womhlaba wonke othuthukisa abantu nezinhlangano ekutheni bathole idijithali ethembekile. Sekuyiminyaka engaphezu kwengama-50, i-ISACA ihlomise abantu namabhizinisi ngolwazi, iziqinisekiso, ezemfundo, ukuqeqeshwa kanye nomphakathi ukuze bathuthuke emisebenzini yabo, baguqule izinhlangano zabo, bakhe izwe ledijithali elithembekile nelinokuziphatha okuhle. I-ISACA iyinhlangano yabasebenzi nenhlangano yokufunda yomhlaba wonke esebenzisa ubuchwepheshe bamalungu ayo angaphezu kuka-170,000 asebenza emikhakheni yezokwethembeka kwedijithali efana nokuvikeleka kolwazi, ukubusa, isiqiniseko, ubungozi, ubumfihlo kanye nekhwalithi. Itholakala emazweni ayi-188, kufaka phakathi izahluko ezingama-225 emhlabeni jikelele. Ngesisekelo sayo i-One In Tech, i-ISACA isekela imfundo ye-IT kanye nezindlela zemisebenzi kubantu abangenazo izinsiza ezidingekayo nabangamelwe muntu. Mayelana ne-Onitsha Business School
I-Onitsha Business School (OBS) iwuhlelo oluklanyelwe ukusebenzisa izinsiza zezemfundo ezifanele ukuthuthukisa nokuqeqesha iqoqo elikhulu lamathalenta ezentengiselwano, ezezimboni kanye nezamabhizinisi edolobheni eliseduze nelase-Onitsha. Nakuba yasungulwa ngenxa yezidingo ezingavamile neziqondile zedolobha kanye nesifunda sase-Anambra, eNigeria ikakhulukazi, ukugxila kwayo kanye nomgomo wayo wokuba yiSikhungo esihlonishwa umhlaba wonke sokwenza kahle kwezemfundo esiletha uhla lobuholi obuklanywe ngamasu obuholi, umsebenzi wezandla kanye nezamabhizinisi. , izinhlelo zobungcweti, nezisekelwe kumakhono esigabeni esikhethiwe sabafundi abangaba abafundi. Lesi sikole sifundisa abafundi okungaphezu kokwenziwa ekilasini ukuze baqonde amaqiniso ngomhlaba wezamabhizinisi. Amakhono abaphathi nabaholi ayathuthukiswa ukuze kubhekwane nezinselele. Abantu balekelelwa ukuba bakwazi ukucabanga futhi ngalokho baqinisekisa ukuthi amasu abanawo ngamabhizinisi ayaphumelela.
Ama-Hacktivists amemezela impi yotwamkhathi eNigeria I-Apple izokwethula eyayo i-AI chatbot, futhi izobizwa nge-Apple GPT. I-Apple inendlela yokujoyina izitayela zobuchwepheshe futhi benze abayisebenzisayo bakholwe ukuthi ubuchwepheshe abuzange bubekhona ngaphambilini. Ngifuna ngempela ukubona ukuthi izoyikhipha kanjani i-Apple GPT. Okudabukisayo ukuthi angeke ifiki maduzene. Njengezinto eziningi, i-Apple ithatha isikhathi sayo futhi ngeke ibe nengcindezi yokukhipha ubuchwepheshe noma isici esingaphelele. Nakuba umbiko we-Bloomberg usitshele ngoNtulikazi ukuthi i-Apple GPT ingase ifike ngo-2024, umhlaziyi we-Apple, uMing-Chi Kuo uthe kusasele iminyaka eminingi. Noma ingaphuma nini, ngiyazi ukuthi abalandeli be-Apple bazothola indlela yokwenza i-Apple GPT ibonakale sengathi i-AI chatbots ayizange ibe khona kuze kube kwethulwa ayakwa-Apple. Ngenkathi sisalinde i-Apple ukuthi ibe yingxenye yalomphakathi we-AI, nakhu engikuphathele kona namuhla: IWorldcoin ayililahli ithemba ngeKenya
Izigebengu ziza eNigeria I-Worldcoin ihlela ukuqhubeka nokuskena isiyingi samehlo eKenya NgoLwesithathu, zi-2 kuNcwaba wezi-2023, iziphathimandla zaseKenya zamisa imisebenzi ye-Worldcoin, iphrojekthi yebhukunyazi/blockchain efuna ukwakha isizindalwazi sabo bonke abantu emhlabeni ngokuskena isiyingi samehlo abo. Nakuba imisiwe, iWorldcoin ayihlehli. Ima, yini iWorldcoin? Uma namanje udidekile ngokuthi imayelana nani yonke iphrojekthi ye-Worldcoin, ungabheka incazelo emfushane lapha. Noma kunjalo, i-Worldcoin, itshele i-TechCrunch ukuthi isebenzisa lokhu "kumiswa kwesikhashana" "ukuze iqhamuke nezinqubo ezingcono zokugibela kanye nezindlela zokulawula isixuku. Lokhu kungaphezu "kokusebenza nezikhulu zendawo ukuze kwandiswe ukuqonda kwezinyathelo zobumfihlo nezibopho ezisetshenziswa yi-Worldcoin." Ixhaswe ngokubambisana ne-OpenAI CEO, uSam Altman, iWorldcoin ibhalise abantu baseKenya abangaphezu kwama-350,000. Izixuku ezinkulu zabantu zibonakale ziklelisa ukuzohlola isiyingi samehlo abo ukuthola ibhonasi yokubhalisa engu-$50.
Yimali eningi leyo: Yebo, ikhona. Futhi ngenkathi i-Worldcoin yethulwa ngokusemthethweni emasontweni ambalwa edlule, ithole uxhaso lwezigidi ezingu-500 zamaRandi. Hlehlisa: Isitatimende se-Worldcoin asikufaki ukuvuma ukuthi imisebenzi yayo imisiwe eKenya. Ngokomongo, ithe, "Ngenxa yokuqapha okukhulu nangomzamo wokunciphisa umthamo wesixuku, izinsizakalo zokuqinisekisa ziye zamiswa okwesikhashana." Kuyathakazelisa ukuthi ungqongqoshe we-ICT waseKenya, u-Eliud Owalo, usevele wathi imisebenzi ye-Worldcoin isemthethweni, kungani sekushintshwa inkulumo ngokushesha? Abagqekezi bahlose ingqalasizinda ebalulekile yaseNigeria Iqembu labagqekezi elibizwa nge-Anonymous Sudan lihlela ukuhlasela i-inthanethi okubeka engcupheni ingqalasizinda yedijithali eNigeria. I-National Information Technology Development Agency (i-NITDA), esitatimendeni sabezindaba ithe ithole okwenziwa yizigebengu ezigqekezayo futhi yatshela umphakathi ukuthi uzilungiselele ngokuhlaselwa kotamkhathi okuzobe kusuka kuleli qembu. Kungani bebhekise eNigeria? Ngangena esiteshini saleliqembu ku-Telegram, futhi bathi bahlanyiswa iNigeria ngoba inqume "ukweseka nabacindezeli baseFrance futhi ilwe neNiger."
Bazichaza njengabagqekezi base-Afrika abalwa nempi ye-inthanethi egameni lamaSulumane acindezelwe emhlabeni wonke. Kufanele ukhathazeke kangakanani? I-Sudan Anonymous ayivamisile ukugeja uma ifika. Bahlasele iKenya muva nje futhi bakwazi ukugebenga ingosi ye-eCitizen, lapho izakhamizi zaseKenya zingakwazi ukuthola izinsiza ezifana nokuvuselelwa kwelayisensi yokushayela kanye nokuvuselelwa kwe-visa. Sebevele bayihlasele i-MTN: NgoLwesithathu ekuseni, zi-2 kuNcwaba wezi-2022, "Nigeria zilungiselele namuhla" kuthunyelwe esiteshini sabo seTelegram. Ntambama, leli qembu lamemezela ukuthi selihlasele "inethiwekhi yezokuxhumana ye-MTN eNigeria. Kuzobonakala ukunqamuka kwengxenye kanye nokusalela okukhulu." INigeria yenzani ngalokhu? Ithimba le-NITDA elilungiselela izimo eziphuthumayo kanye nezimpendulo zekhompiyutha liye leluleka izinhlangano zikahulumeni ngokuthi zingakuvimbela kanjani ukuhlasela okuvela kwi-Sudan Anonymous, kodwa yisikhathi kuphela esizosho ukuthi lezi zinyathelo zizosebenza yini.
Kufundiswa Abasunguli base-Afrika Abasebasha: I-STEAM Fun Fest 2023 yenza Amarekhodi Amasha Kwezemfundo ze-STEAM! Uhlelo lwesithathu lwe-STEAM Fun Fest, ebelubanjwe zingama-22 kuNtulukazi wezi-2023, lube yimpumelelo emangalisayo, luthathe izinhliziyo nezingqondo zezinkulungwane zabasunguli abasha, abaxazululi bezinkinga, nabaholi. Lo mcimbi ongajwayelekile, obuhlelwe ukubambisana okunombono ka-Titi Adewusi (9ijakids), Jadesola Adedeji (STEM METS), Uchenna Onwuamaegbu-Ugwu (Edufun Technik), Wale Ogunjobi (Sabiteach), Kunmi Adenipebi (Gamr), kanye no-Bukola Akingbade (Kucheza) , ngempela iphile ngokuvumelana nesithunzi sayo njengefestiveli ye-STEAM enkulu kunazo zonke ezwenikazi, ivunguza uthando lweSayensi, Ubuchwepheshe, Ubunjiniyela, Ubuciko, Nezibalo (STEAM) entsheni. Inhloso ebaluleke kakhulu ye-STEAM Fun Fest ukunikeza isizukulwane esilandelayo amakhono abalulekile nolwazi oludingekayo ukuze baphumelele emisebenzini yesikhathini esizayo kanye nasenkathini edijithali. ngesikhathi somcimbi, abahambele umcimbi abangaphezu kwama-4000 babe nethuba lokusebenza ezintweni ezihlukahlukene ze-STEAM, kusukela kwezerobhothi, isakhiwo somudlalo, okwenzeka ngobuchwepheshe, imodeli ye-3D yopopayi, izakhiwo zezithombe, nokuhlolwa kwesayensi. Inhloso yomkhosi bekuwukuthuthukisa ukucabanga okujulile, ukuxazulula izinkinga, namandla okubambisana, ukugqugquzela uthando lwemfundo ye-STEAM phakathi kwezingane ezineminyaka eyi-7-15. Umcimbi uqale ngenkulumo yosuku ka-Iyin Aboyeji (u-CEO, e-Future Africa) othe inhloso yemfundo ye-STEAM wukuba izingqondo ezisencane ezinolwazi lwe-STEAM emikhakheni yazo zihlanganyele ukuze zinikeze isisombululo ezinkingeni zomphakathi ezithinta abantu kunokuthi bagcine ulwazi/amakhono kubona. Kube nezinye izikhathi zezikhulumi ezivela kochwepheshe bemboni ababehlanganisa uMalik Afegbua oyi-CEO ye-Slick City, i-Bode Abifarin CEO ye-Flutterwave, uMsunguli we-Oreoluwa Lesi i-WTEC, u-Lanre Bamisebi, u-ED, i-Access Corporation no-Jola Aderemi-Makinde, u-Google phakathi kwabanye. Umcimbi wakulonyaka uhlanganise okusha ohlelweni okufana ne-STEAM Competition Pitch kanye ne-Tech Career Corner lapho izingane zibe nezingxoxo mayelana nemisebenzi yezobuchwepheshe nochwepheshe obuvela ezinkampanini zobuchwepheshe eziphezulu njenge-Interswitch, MainOne, Jumia, Utiva, Flutterwave, ne-AltSchool. Ku-STEAM Competition Pitch, abafinyelele kowamanqamu abayisithupha abakhiwe izingane ezineminyaka engu-9 -15 baphonsele iphaneli yamajaji izixazululo zokubhekana nezinkinga eziphathelene Nokwenza Kabusha, Imvelo, Ukusimama, kanye Namandla Avuselelekayo.
U-Kamdilichukwu Chukwuneta, umfana oneminyaka eyi-9 wase-Grace Saint School, e-Ikorodu, unqobe umncintiswano we-STEAM, egoduka nesibekwamathangeni esisha kanye nomklomelo wemali ongu-N400,000. Usuku lonke, indawo ibigcwele imisebenzi ethokozisayo - amalebhu e-STEAM, indawo ye-Esport, ibhola likanobhutshuzwayo elingakhokhelwa, kanye nababukisi be-STEAM abangaphezu kuka-30. I-STEAM Labs yethule ikhodingi, Ezobunjiniyela, Ezamarobhothi, Ukuhlolwa kwezesayensi, Izithobe zopopayi, idizayini ye-UI/UX, Amathuluzi e-AI, kanye Nokuthuthukiswa Kwegeyimu ezinganeni. Abahleli badlulisa ukubonga okusuka enhliziyweni kubaxhasi: i-Access Bank, i-Argentil Capital, i-Lotus Bank, i-Flutterwave, i-Kibo, i-Flour Mills, i-The Place Restaurant, i-Hyde Energy, i-A.G Leventis, i-Nigeria Communication Commission (NCC), ne-MTN. I-STEAM Funfest 2023 ibe yimpumelelo ngenxa yokusekwa yinina. Njengoba iphela i-STEAM Fun Fest 2023, umthelela wayo mukhulu udlulela ngale kosuku lomcimbi. Intshisekelo yemfundo ye-STEAM efakwe ezinhliziyweni zabancane, kuhlanganiswe nokungapheli amandla kusungulwa izinto ezintsha nokufunda, iqinisekisa ukuthi ikusasa laseNigeria lizoba eliqhakazile, libe nabanesibindi, futhi ligcwale amathuba angapheli. Masiqhubeke sigubhe futhi sisekele izinhlelo ezifana ne-STEAM Fun Fest, njengoba zikhuthaza futhi zihlomisa abasunguli abasha base-Afrika ukuze balolonge ikusasa lezizukulwane ezizayo.
U-Bosun Tijani we-CcHUB ukuqokwe njengongqongqoshe kwikhabhinethi kaMongameli Tinubu UMongameli u-Bola Tinubu ufake u-Bosun Tijani, umsunguli kanye noMphathi Omkhulu wesikhungo esikhulu sezobuchwepheshe saseNigeria, i-Co-Creation Hub (CcHUB), eqenjini lesibili lohlu lwakhe longqongqoshe. Lokhu kuqokwa kusho ukushiya ohlwini olugcwele osopolitiki, ababusi besikhathi esidlule, nezigele. Wazalwa zingamna-20 kuNtulikazi we-1977, uhambo lukaTijani lwezobuchwepheshe lwaqala ngediploma yeSayensi yezeKhompiyutha kanye neBachelor yeSayensi yezoMnotho yaseNyuvesi yaseJos. Ukulandela kwakhe imfundo kwamuholela ekutheni athole iziqu ze-Mastazi kwezoBuchwepheshe bezoKwazisa nokuPhatha azithola e-Warwick Business School kanye ne-PhD yezoKusha nokuThuthukiswa koMnotho e-University of Leicester. Isipiliyoni sikaTijani sobungoti naso sihlaba umxhwele. Kusukela eyiMenenja Yokuthuthukiswa Kwezamabhizinisi ne-DeliveryKing kuya ekusebenzeni njenge-Deployment Lead (i-Africa) ne-Hewlett Packard (i-HP) Global Micro-enterprises Acceleration Programme (i-GMEAP), umnikelo wakhe endaweni yezobuchwepheshe ujule kakhulu. Uphathe izikhungo zokufunda e-Afrika yonkana futhi waqala amaphrojekthi abalulekile, okuhlanganisa ukuvakasha kokuqala kuka-Mark Zuckerberg eNigeria nase-sub-Saharan Africa kanye nokuhlangana noBill Gates, uMsunguli we-Microsoft. Ngaphansi kobuholi bukaTijani, i-CcHUB ikhule kusukela ekuqaleni kwayo e-Yaba yafinyelela ekutholeni izindawo ezinkulu e-Afrika yonkana, okuyenza ibe incubator yobuchwepheshe base-Afrika, inika abantu abasha amandla ngamathuluzi, imiphakathi, kanye nemali abayidingayo ukuze baqalise amabhizinisi anomthelela omuhle. Ngokukhula kwesikwama se-naira esingamabhiliyoni, i-CcHub itshala imali kubasunguli abasaqala ukwakha imikhiqizo emisha ezinhlelweni zemfundo nokunakekelwa kwezempilo zase-Afrika.
U-Bosun Tijani njengoNgqongqoshe Wezokuxhumana kanye Nomnotho Wedijithali? Ukuqokwa kukaTijani kubika ukuthi kunemicabango yokumfaka esikhundleni sokuba nguNgqongqoshe Wezokuxhumana kanye Nomnotho Wedijithali. Lesi sinyathelo sihambisana nokugxila kukaMongameli uTinubu ku-tech ecosystem yaseNigeria ngesikhathi somkhankaso wakhe, kodwa akukona lokho kuphela okukhona. Ulwazi oluningi luka-Tijani kanye nengqondo yakhe ecabanga izinto ezintsha nakho kungamenza abe yimbangi enkulu yezinye izikhundla zobungqongqoshe. Isizinda sakhe kwezomnotho, sihambisana nobuchule bakhe kwezobuchwepheshe, kumbeka njengomuntu ongase angamele izikhundla zobungqongqoshe eziphathelene nokuthuthukiswa komnotho noma ezemfundo. Kodwa-ke, kumongo womsebenzi wobungqongqoshe ohlongozwayo, iphrofayili kaBosun Tijani akuyona kuphela inketho phakathi kohlu lwabaqokelwe ukuba ungqongqoshe. Iphrofayili ka-Olubunmi Tunji-Ojo nayo ibonakala njengembangi enamandla esikhundleni sikangqongqoshe we-ICT. Njengoba enemvelaphi ebanzi kwezobunjiniyela be-elekthronikhi nokuxhumana, ukuphumelela emsebenzini njenge-CEO ye-Matrix IT Solutions Limited, nolwazi lwezombangazwe njengelungu leNdlu yabaMeli, iziqu zika-Tunji-Ojo zihambisana kahle nendima. Ukuqokwa kwabaholi bezobuchwepheshe abafana noTijani kungaba wushintsho oluthembisayo esimweni sezepolitiki saseNigeria. Akugcini nje ngokuvuma ukubaluleka kwemboni yezobuchwepheshe kodwa futhi kuvula indlela yokubusa okusha nokucabanga okuya phambili.
Njengoba iSigele siqhubeka nenqubo yokuhlola, umphakathi wezobuchwepheshe kanye nesizwe ngokubanzi silindele ngokulangazela isinqumo sokugcina, sinethemba ngekusasa lapho ubuchwepheshe nokusungula kuzothatha indawo ebaluleke kakhulu ekuthuthukisweni kweNigeria.
I-CcHub manje inezitezi ezi-5 ehhovisi le-Yaba nendawo entsha ye-American Spaces I-United States Consul General u-F. John Bray umemezele ekuqaleni kwanamuhla ukuthi i-Co-creation Hub izoba ngumlingani wabo osemthethweni ekumiseni i-American Spaces eYaba, eLagos. Ngezikhala ezingaphezu kuka-700 emazweni angu-152 emhlabeni jikelele, i-American Spaces inikeza izindawo lapho izivakashi zingaxhuma futhi zifunde mayelana ne-United States. #CGBray: Sibona umklomelo oyingqayizivele ku-@Cc_HUB njengozakwethu wokusetha nokusebenzisa i-Priority entsha #AmericanSpace ku-Co-Creation Hub e-Lagos— U.S. Mission Nigeria (@USinNigeria) zingama-28 kuMfumfu wezi-2026 Ihhovisi Lezikhala ZaseMelika lithuthukisa futhi lisekele izinkundla zesimanjemanje, ezisebenzayo zokuxoxisana komphakathi nezithameli eziqondiswe kwamanye amazwe ekusekeleni izinjongo zenqubomgomo yezangaphandle yase-United States. Ukuhlanganisa ubuchwepheshe nobuhle, i-Spaces inikeza izindawo ezibonakalayo eziguqukayo ezinokubukeka nomuzwa waseMelika. Ngokombiko wonyaka we-American Spaces 2015, kukhona ukulungiswa okuthile okuzokwenziwa ku-Spaces kulo nyaka. Okubili kwalolo shintsho ukuthuthukiswa kwe-inthanethi kokusebenzelana kwedijithali nobuchwepheshe obuvumela ukuhlela okubonakalayo. Kanti esinye isitezi sengezwe endaweni yethu e-#Yaba okwenza izitezi ezi-5 sezizonke. Ukuwina okukhulu kwe-#Yaba & #Tech e-#Nigeria.
Okokuqala okubalulekile #AmericanSpace in #WestAfrica. Lokhu kuzokwenza lula ukusebenzisana nokufinyelela! Ngobambiswano olusha neNxusa Lase-United States, i-CcHub manje isinesamba sezitezi ezinhlanu endaweni yaseYaba, eLagos. U-Bosun Tijani kanye nethimba le-CcHub bayisinyathelo esisodwa sokusondela ekutholeni sonke isakhiwo esisekelwe ngamasu asendaweni yezobuchwepheshe.
Inkampani yaseNingizimu Afrika yezohwebo inyusa imali engaphezu kwezigidi eziyishumi zamaRandi ukuze kuxhaswe isikhwama se-proptech Inkampani yaseNingizimu Afrika, i-REdimension Capital, iqoqe imali engaphezu kwezigidi eziyishumi zamaRandi esikhwameni sayo sokuqala, i-REdimension Real Estate Technology and Sustainability Fund I. Lesi wukuvalwa kokuqala kwalesi sikhwama, esibala i-Rand Merchant Bank, i-Investec Property Fund, kanye ne-Growthpoint Properties njengabalingani abalinganiselwe. Abanye abatshalizimali bahlanganisa i-Liberty Two Degrees, i-Liberty Group, ne-Sphere Holdings. Le nkampani inethemba lokuthi izoqeda ukuvalwa kokugcina kwesikhwama ngoMasingana wezi- 2025. Isungulwe ngo-2021 ngu-Peter Clark no-Matt Marshall, i-REdimension Real Estate Technology and Sustainability Fund ngizotshala kumabhizinisi asaqala akha izixazululo zokwenza umkhakha wezindawo ezithengiswayo ube yidijithali. Ngeso lokuthuthukisa ukusimama, inkampani iphinde ihlele ukubuyisela emuva amabhizinisi asaqala akhuthaza ukusebenza kahle kwamandla, kanye nezinyathelo zekhabhoni ephansi. Umkhakha we-proptech wase-Afrika uyakhula, kodwa ubone ukukhula kancane eminyakeni emithathu edlule. Ngo-2022, iziqalo eziyi-15 ze-proptech zakhuphula u-$16.6 wezigidi, kodwa ngaphezu kuka-50% wemali etshalwe kumamabhizinini asaqala. Isamba semali esiqoqiwe siphinde saphakama ngo-13% kunonyaka odlule, okubonisa ukukhula kwenzalo yabatshalizimali.
I-Egypt kanye neNigeria nabo babenesibopho sezivumelwano eziningi ezidaluliwe ze-proptech.
Grey, I-Fintech ibhizinisi elisaqala laseNigeria, iHosts Clique, Isidlo Sakusihlwa Esikhethekile Sokunika Abasunguli Bamabhizinisi asaqala Amandla Ngemininingwane Ebalulekile evela kubaholi Bemboni IGrey, inkampani ehamba phambili ye-fintech, isanda kusingatha u-Clique, umcimbi wesidlo sakusihlwa okhethekile endaweni yokudlela edumile, i-Ile-Eros, eLagos, eNigeria, ehlanganisa abasunguli bokuqalisa abanamandla abayi-16 abavela emikhakheni eyahlukene. Inhloso yalo mbuthano osondelene kwakuwukugqugquzela ukuxhumana, ukwabelana ngemininingwane ebalulekile, kanye nokunika amandla isizukulwane esilandelayo sabasunguli bokuqalisa ngolwazi olubalulekile ekwakheni iziqalo eziphumelelayo. Okuhlangenwe nakho kwama-Epikhuru e-Ile-Eros kwakungeyona into encane njengokungavamile, njengoba izihambeli zanikezwa ukudla oku-4, okuhambisana nama-cocktail aklanywe ngokucophelela namawayini amahle. Ukwengeza kwimpatho, umdlali wevayolini onethalente wadlala izingoma ezishisa izikhotha ukuze kujabule izihambeli, okwenxa kwaba ubusuku obungeke babukhohlwa. Okugqame kakhulu kulo mcimbi wukuba khona kwabasunguli beGrey, u-Idee Obong no-Femi Aghedo, indaba ekhuthazayo yempumelelo emhlabeni wokuqala wase-Afrika. Abasunguli Abahlanganyeli bahehe izethameli ngohambo lwabo olumangalisayo, banikeza imininingwane ebalulekile nezifundo wonke umsunguli okudingeka akwazi mayelana nokwakha ibhizinisi elisaqala. U-Idee, wabelane ngamasu abalulekile abawasebenzisile ukuze bathole izimali ngempumelelo, ekhanyisela uhambo lukaGrey lokuba yingxenye ye-Y Combinator, enye yamabhizinisi asaqala akhule ngokushesha edume kakhulu emhlabeni. Ukwengeza, u-Femi ugcizelele ukubaluleka kokusebenza kahle kanye nezinyathelo zokonga izindleko, ikakhulukazi kumabhizinisi asaqala. Wagqamisa ngentshiseko amandla obambiswano lwamasu ekuqhubekiseleni phambili isiqalo esibheke ekukhuleni nasekuphumeleleni okusimeme.
Ukwengeza ekuhehekeni kwakusihlwa, u-Dapo Awobokun, uzakwethu wokuqala e-Paystack, uphathe umcimbi njengesivakashi esikhethekile. Ulwazi oluningi luka-Dapo nobungcweti embonini ye-fintech bunikeze abasunguli imininingwane ebalulekile ngendawo eguqukayo kanye namathuba avelayo okuqalisa. Ngaphezu kwalokho, uDapo wakhuluma nabasunguli, egcizelela ukubaluleka okukhulu kweSiko kwibhizinisi elisaqala. "Isiko nguwe. Yeqa imithetho nemithethonqubo nje ethunyelwe endaweni yakho yokwamukela izivakashi. Njengabasunguli, kufanele nihlanganise isiko lenkampani yenu futhi niwamukele ngenhliziyo yonke umsebenzi wayo,” kusho yena. Umbuthano wesidlo sakusihlwa usebenze njengenkundla eyingqayizivele yabasunguli bamabhizinisi asaqala ukuxhumana nontanga abanomqondo ofanayo abavela emikhakheni eyahlukene, ukukhuthaza ukusebenzisana kwezimboni ezihlukahlukene kanye nokushintshisana ngemibono emisha. Umkhathi wawugcwele ugqozi kanye nokuzibophezela okwabiwe ekubumbeni ikusasa eliqhakazile ngosomabhizinisi. "UGrey ukholelwa ngokuqinile ekunikezeni amandla abaqalayo ukuze bafinyelele kumamakhono abo aphelele," kusho u-Idee Obong, umsunguli we-Grey. “Lo mcimbi wesidlo sakusihlwa okhethekile usinikeze ithuba elihle lokwabelana ngolwazi nolwazi lokwakha isiqalo esiyimpumelelo.
Sizibophezele ekuthuthukiseni uhlelonhlaliswano lokuphilayo nokungaphili kwezamabhizinisi kanye nokweseka abasafufusa abasunguli njengoba beqala uhambo lwabo oluletha uguquko." Umcimbi ushiye umbono ongenakucimeka emphakathini yamabhizinisi asaqala, uhlanganisa abasunguli abasafufusa nabaholi bezimboni ekuphishekeleni okwabiwe kokwenza kahle nokusungula izinto ezintsha. Mayelana noGrey UGrey wenza lula ukuthumela nokwamukela izinkokhelo zangaphandle zabazisebenzayo, abasebenzela emakhaya namabhizinisi. Yasungulwa maphakathi no-2020 ngu-Idorenyin Obong kanye no-Femi Aghedo, iGrey iyindlela elula yokuthumela nokwamukela izinkokhelo zamazwe ngamazwe ngaphandle kwemingcele. Ngelayisensi Yebhizinisi Lomsebenzi Wemali evela kwa-FITRAC eCanada & FinCEN e-USA, uGrey wenze kwalula ukuba abantu bathumele imali kwamanye amazwe ngokushesha.
I-Prembly Iqinisa Ukuthobelana Nengqalasizinda Yezokuphepha Ngokuthola Umhubhe, Ukwandisa Amakhono Emininingo Yezezimali kuzo wonke Amamakethe Ezisafufusa Ngaphambilini, ohamba phambili ekuthobeleni nasekuvikeleni ingqalasizinda yamamakethe asafufusa umemezele ukutholwa kwayo kwe-Tunnel, inkampani esungulwe eqhuba ukwabiwa kweimininingo okusemthethweni kuwo wonke amabhizinisi. Lokhu kuhlanganiswa kuthuthukisa ukuphepha kwePrembly futhi kwandise nezinsizakalo zezezimali, okuvumela ukuqinisekiswa kobunikazi obuqinile ngokuhlanganiswa kwemininingo yezezimali ngokuphelele. Ingqalasizinda yemininingo nenkampani yezibalo, i-Tunnel, izimise njengozakwethu othembekile embonini yezikweletu nezomazisi ngokuxhuma ababolekisi kumininingo yangempela esezingeni eliphezulu kanye nobuchwepheshe obuzinzile. Umkhiqizo wayo ohamba phambili we-fintech, i-PhoneCash, futhi usiza amakhasimende ukuthi athumele imali ngokushesha okukhulu. Ukuhlanganiswa kwezinsizakalo zeTunnel kunikeza amabhizinisi ithuluzi elinamandla lokukala, okwenza kufinyeleleke olwazini lwesikhathi sangempela lwekhasimende kusuka emithonjeni eminingi nge-API eyodwa. Iqaphela ukubaluleka kwemininingo yezezimali njengengxenye ebalulekile yokuqinisekisa ubuwena, i-Prembly ikhethe ngobuchule ukuhlanganisa i-Tunnel nezixazululo zayo ezikhona zokuqinisekisa ubunikazi. “Siyaziqonda izinselelo eziyingqayizivele ezibhekene nazo zonke izimakethe futhi sijabule kakhulu ukumemezela ukutholwa kweTunnel. Lokhu kuhambisana nomgomo oyinhloko ka-Prembly wokuvikela nokwenza amabhizinisi athuthuke ngokuhlinzeka ngengqalasizinda eqinile yokuthobela imithetho nezokuphepha.”, kusho uLanre Ogungbe, oyi-CEO u-Prembly. I-Tunnel yasungulwa ngenhloso yokuqondisa ukufinyelela kwemininingo okulawulwayo, ukusetshenziswa, nokwabelana phakathi kwabahlinzeki, okuhlinzeka amakhasimende ngezindlela eziningo zokwenza imali.
U-Tobi Okedeji, umsunguli kanye no-CEO we-Tunnel, uzwakalise ukuziqhenya kwakhe ngokujoyina i-Prembly, egcizelela ukuhlanganiswa kwezixazululo zabo kunethiwekhi ebanzi yokuthobela nokuvikeleka. Lokhu kutholwa kwamasu kuthuthukisa ukuhlomisa amabhizinisi, ukuletha ulwazi lwamakhasimende olusebenzisekayo kanye nemininingwane ebalulekile. Lokhu kwenza umehluko omkhulu ekusebenzeni kwe-Prembly, kubanga uhlelonhlaliswano yokuphilayo nokungaphili elungele ukuthuthukisa ukwabelana ngeimininingo nokunciphisa ubungozi ngokuqinisekiswa kwamakhasimende. Imele ingqophamlando ekukhuleni kwenkampani futhi iqinisa ukuzinikela okuqinile ekukhuthazeni ukusebenzisana kwamasu nokubambisana ukuze kwandiswe iminikelo yomsebenzi. Mayelana ne-Prembly: I-Prembly yinkampani yengqalasizinda yokuthobela nokuvikeleka, esungula ingqalasizinda ebalulekile edingekayo ukuze kuthuthukiswe ukuhlanganiswa kwedijithali kuyo yonke i-Afrika. Ehamba phambili ekuqinisekisweni kobunikazi, ekuvimbeleni/ukutholwa kokukhwabanisa, kanye nokuhlolwa kwemvelaphi, i-Prembly yenza amabhizinisi emazweni angaphezu kuka-40 ase-Afrika akwazi ukusebenzisana ngokuthembana nezinkampani ezifuna ukungena ezimakethe zase-Afrika ukuze zenze kanjalo ngokuphepha. Mayelana neTunnel: I-Tunnel (i-Usetunnel Limited) yasungulwa nguTobi Okedeji, u-Yusuf Badmos, kanye noLanre Ibraheem. Kuyinkampani yokuhlaziya imininingo kanye nengqalasizinda egxile ekunikeni amandla ukwabelana ngemininingo okusemthethweni kuwo wonke amabhizinisi.
Ngobuchwepheshe bayo bokuxhumanisa izinsiza eziningi zokuboleka imininingo kanye nokunika amandla imininingo yezezimali, i-Tunnel isibe uzakwethu othembekile embonini yemisebenzi yezezimali.
Izingcingo ezengeziwe zokusebenzisana nababambiqhaza njengoba isikhungo soguquko lwedijithali sisingatha inkhulumomphendvulwano yenqubomgomo ngoMthetho Wamabhizinisi Asaqala WaseNigeria owaziwa nge-Nigerian Startup Act. I-GIZ/Digital Transformation Centre (i-DTC), ngokubambisana ne-European Union kanye ne-National Information Technology Development Agency (i-NITDA), bahlele iseshini yengxoxo yenqubomgomo yedijithali lapho kugxilwe khona kumthetho wezamabhizinisi asaqala owaziwa nge-Nigerian Startup Act (i-NSA). I-DTC yase-Nigeria ihlose ukugqugquzela izingxoxo ezibandakanya wonke umuntu futhi iqoqe imininingwane ebalulekile evela kubabambiqhaza ukuze kwakhe uhlaka olusebenzayo olukhuthaza ukuqamba okusha, amabhizinisi, kanye nokukhula komnotho okusimeme ngaphakathi kwe-ecosystem yokuqala yaseNigeria kanye nomnotho wedijithali. Iseshini ekhiqizayo, ebibanjelwe e-Lagos ngoLwesine, zingama-27 kuNtulikazi wezi- 2023, yahlanganisa ababambiqhaza abavela emikhakheni kahulumeni nezizimele ndawonye egumbini elilodwa ukuze kudingidwe izindlela zokugqugquzela ukwamukelwa koMthetho Wokuqala waseNigeria ezweni lonke. Owayekhona engxoxweni yenqubomgomo bekunguDkt. Thuweba Diwani, iNhloko, ye-GIZ/Digital Transformation Centre (DTC) Nigeria, owenze inkulumo yokwamukela. Uthe amabhizinisi asaqala aseNigeria ngeke nje akhe indawo eyenza kusebenzeke kodwa kuzokwandisa nokwakhiwa kwamakhono futhi kusheshise intuthuko. Yingakho kubalulekile ukuthi ababambiqhaza basebenzisane ukuze kuqinisekiswe impumelelo yoMthetho Wamabhizinisi asaqala. Iseshini iphinde yaba namakheli avela ku-Markus Wauschkuhn, umxhumanisi we-Sustainable Economic Development Cluster (SEDEC), e-GIZ Nigeria, kanye no-Inga Stefanowicz, iNhloko Yesigaba sehhovisi, e-Green and Digital Economy, Izithunywa ze-EU eNigeria kanye ne-ECOWAS. UDkt. Aminu Lawal Muhammad, Umeluleki Okhethekile Womqondisi Jikelele we-NITDA mayelana nokuguqulwa kwedijithali, ukhulume kakhulu ngoMthetho Wamabhizinisi asaqala waseNigeria kanye nemiphumela yawo ekuguqulweni kwedijithali eNigeria. Uxoxe ngomsebenzi osuwenziwe, wengeza ngokuthi umsebenzi oqhubekayo nokwesekwa kuzoqhubeka kuvela kwa-NITDA.
U-Tracy Okoro-Isaac, Ohola I-State Adoption for the Nigeria Startup Act, uthathe izethameli ohambweni oluholele kuMthetho Wokuqala waseNigeria, kusukela ekubizweni kwamavolontiya ukuya ekusebenzeni kanzima kanye nokufezwa kwezinyathelo ezibalulekile eziholela ekusayineni umthetho. Ufingqa ezinye zezinhlinzeko zalo mthetho, wengeza ngokuthi uklanyelwe ukuzuzisa kakhulu amabhizinisi asaqala nokuthi uhulumeni uyabeseka njengoba lo mthetho ubeka zonke izinhlaka ezithintekayo. Iseshini yephaneli eyenganyelwe ngu-Justina Oha, Umsunguli kanye ne-CEO, we-Digital Equity Africa, enamaphaneli u-Amina Lawal, Unjiniyela we-DevOps, I-Hostspace; u-Ized Uanikhehi, Umsunguli, we-Zedi Afrika; Unjiniyela u-Yakubu Musa, Ibamba Lomxhumanisi Kazwelonke, ONDI NITDA; U-Amal Hassan, Isekela likasihlalo wekomidi elisetshenziswayo; UCharles Emembolu, umsunguli kanye nomqondisi, we-Roar Nigeria Hub; kanye no-Amina Lawal, Unjiniyela we-DevOps kanye nomsunguli, we-Hostspace, bangene ngokujulile kumthelela we-Nigeria Startup Act emnothweni oqhutshwa izinto ezintsha. U-Amal uxoxe ngezinye zezinzuzo zalesi senzo uma kubhekwa ukuthi sivikela abasunguli abasaqala amabhizinisi futhi sibanikeze uhlobo lokusekelwa amabhizinisi amadala abengathanda ukuba nalo lapho eqala, esebenzisa ibhizinisi lakhe lokuqala njengesibonelo. U-Amina wakwazi ukuveza isidingo sokuqeqeshwa okuqhubekayo kanye nokuhlinzekwa kwemisebenzi kubantu abaqeqeshiwe. Uphinde wacela isidingo sokwakha indawo evumayo kanye nokuhlinzeka ngengqalasizinda edingekayo ukuze amabhizinisi anikwe amandla ezobuchwepheshe athuthuke. UMusa, ekhuluma esikhundleni se-NITDA, uthe basebenzisana nohulumeni wezifundazwe ukuze bathole ukuthi basebenzise uMthetho Wokuqala amabhizinisi waseNigeria ezinhlelweni zabo zokuguqula idijithali. Uthe basebenzela ukuthi izifundazwe ziqale owabo umththo wokuqala amabhizinisi, zisebenzisa umthetho wokuqala amabhizinisi kazwelonke njengohlelo. U-Ized unxuse ukuthi kukhuliswe ukubamba iqhaza emiphakathini yendawo lapho bonke ababambiqhaza bekhona futhi nohulumeni andisa ukuxoxisana futhi eqhubeka nokwakha ukwethembana. Abakwiphaneli nezethameli bavumelene ngokuthi bonke abathintekayo kulo mthetho kumele bahlangane ngokugcwele ngoba isakhamuzi ngasinye sinesandla kulo mthetho, sathi uhulumeni akakwazi ukukwenza yedwa.
Ngakho impumelelo yesenzo izoncika ekubambisaneni okuqhubekayo kwabo bonke ababambiqhaza. U-Charles ucele ukutshalwa kwezimali okwengeziwe kwendawo nokwakha kwendawo eyenza kusebenzeke ukuze kugqugquzelwe abatshalizimali bendawo ukuthi batshale izimali kumabhizinisi asaqala asekhaya. U-Ized uphinde wacela uhulumeni ukuthi aqinisekise ukuthi amabhizinisi asaqala ayavikeleka kuzinqubomgomo ezintsha ezingase zingqubuzane noMthetho Wokuqala amabhizinisi waseNigeria. U-Oswald Guobadia, Umholi weKomidi Lokuqala Lokuqala amabhizinisi ENigeria, uphawulile engxoxweni, wathi umthwalo usuku-NITDA ukukhulisa ukwamukelwa koMthetho Wokuqala mamabhizinisi njengoba kungumthwalo wabo ngokuvumelana nezinhlinzeko zezomthetho. Njengoba umcimbi usuya ngasemaphethelweni, kwaba nengxoxo yeqembu. Ababambiqhaza bahlukaniswa baba ngamaqembu amane ngenhloso yokuqoqa imininingwane yokwakhiwa kohlaka lokusetshenziswa kwenqubomgomo yokubamba iqhaza. Iqembu ngalinye ligxile kuzinqubo zentuthuko, ababambiqhaza, ukwakhiwa kwamakhono, ukuqaliswa kwenqubomgomo, ubuchwepheshe njengokwenza amandla, nokuqapha nokuhlola ukuqalwa kwamabhizinisi, ngokulandelana. Iqembu ngalinye lethule izixazululo zalo, okwaxoxwa ngazo ngesikhathi sengxoxo, i-NITDA yayibhala izimpendulo. Inkhulumomphendvulwano ifike esiphethweni ngezingcingo ezengeziwe zokwakhiwa kwamakhono, izindlela ezisebenzayo zokuphendula, ukuxoxisana okwengeziwe phakathi kwababambiqhaza bemboni yomphakathi nezimele, nokwanda kokuqwashisa nokufundisa ngezinhlinzeko zoMthetho Wokuqala WaseNigeria. Mayelana ne-GIZ/DTC Nigeria:
I-GIZ/Digital Transformation Centre (i-DTC) yase-Nigeria ixhaswe ngemali ngokuhlanganyela ne-European Union kanye Nomnyango Wesifunda WaseJalimane Wokubambisana Kwezomnotho Nentuthuko (i-BMZ), futhi isetshenziswa yi-Deutsche Gesellschaft fuer Internationale Zusammenarbeit (GIZ) GmbH. I-DTC Nigeria ihlose ukuthuthukisa amandla ohlelonhlaliswano yedijithali ukuqaliswa kwenqubomgomo, ukusebenza kwezinhlangano, namanethiwekhi njengabahlinzeki bezinsizakalo zomnotho wedijithali, enikeza izixazululo nekhono ledijithali elikhulayo—ukuze kukhule i-ecosystem yokusungulwa kwedijithali. Le phrojekthi isebenzisana kakhulu nabalingisi baseNigeria kuhlelonhlaliswano yokuphilayo nokungaphili okusha, njenge-National Information and Technology Development Agency (i-NITDA), izikhungo zocwaningo, izindawo zokusungula izinto ezintsha, amanethiwekhi omphakathi, amabhizinisi asaqala, ama-MSME nabesifazane.
Ukubheka Emuva Ezindabeni Ze-Quidax Njengoba Igubha Iminyaka eyi-5 I-Quidax, i-African cryptocurrency exchange, ifinyelele kwingqophamlando njengoba inkampani iqeda unyaka wayo wesihlanu isebenza ngokusemthethweni. Ukuze igubhe impumelelo, i-Quidax inikezela ngokufaka idiphozithi mahhala i-Naira kanye nokuhoxa kumakhasimende ayo kusukela ngomhlaka zi-1 zi-7 kuNcwaba. Phakathi kwalesi sikhathi, wonke amakhasimende - kungakhathaliseki ukuthi amadala noma amasha - azokwazi ukufaka idiphozithi futhi akhiphe i-Naira mahhala kuzo zonke iziteshi zenkampani. Ukuphumelela akuyona into encane. Imininingwane esemthethweni evela e-U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics ikhombisa ukuthi amabhizinisi angama-65% ayahluleka eminyakeni emihlanu yokuqala. Futhi, i-Quidax ikwazile ukulwa nezinselelo zayo ezimbalwa eminyakeni embalwa edlule. Ake sihambe ngezinye zezikhathi eziphawuleka kakhulu zenkampani. Ukwethulwa Ngokusemthethweni I-Quidax yethulwa ngo-2018 nguBuchi Okoro (Co-Founder/CEO), u-Uzo Awili (Co-Founder/CTO), kanye noMorris Ebieroma (Co-Founder/CIO).
U-Okoro, owayengumfundi wase-Covenant University, u-Ota, wachaza ukuthi uthuthukise umbono we-Quidax kulandela isipiliyoni sakhe esidabukisayo ayenaso ngenkathi ehweba ngezezimali zebhikunyazi. “Ngangiqale ukuhweba ngemali yebhukunyazi ngisesikoleni, futhi ngaqolwa ngokuthengiselana okuthile. Nakuba ngalinyazwa isipiliyoni, ngaphinde ngabona ukuthi izinkulungwane zabantu ziba yisisulu sokukhwabanisa endaweni yezebhukunyazi. Umgomo wami ne-Quidax bekuwukwakha inkundla lapho abantu bengahweba khona futhi bahwebe ngokusebenzisa i-bhukunyazi ngokuphepha. " Ndawonye u-Awili no-Ebieroma - nabafundi base-Covenant University - u-Okoro baqala ukwakha i-Quidax. Futhi, ngemuva kokuthola imali yokuqala nokungena kuhlelo lwe-Techstars Accelerator ngo-2018, inkampani yehla phansi. Ukwandiswa Kokuqala Iminyaka emibili yokuqala ye-Quidax yanda kakhulu. Ngaleso sikhathi, imakethe yebhukunyazi ibilokhu ibhekana nesinye sezikhathi zayo ezimbi kakhulu, lapho amanani entengo ehla ngemva kokukhuphuka okukhulu ngo-2016 nango-2017. Noma kunjalo, lesi sikhathi siphinde sabona abantu abaningi befunda ngezezimali zebhukunyazi- ikakhulukazi e-Afrika.
Futhi, leli lukuluku libabone behileleka kakhulu kulo mkhakha. Ngokushesha ngokwanele, i-Quidax yayisizuze isisekelo samakhasimende esinomona futhi yayikhula kakhulu. Ukuzulazula ku-CBN Ban Le nkampani ekhulayo ihlangabezane nenselelo yokuqala enkulu ngoNhlolanja wezi- 2021 njengoba iBhange Elikhulu laseNigeria (i-CBN) limemezele ukuvinjelwa kobudlelwane bebhukunyazi namabhange. Ngaleso sikhathi, i-apex bank yabeka umkhawulo kumabhange anezihlangano nezimali zebhukunyazi anoma yiluphi uhlobo. Lokhu kwakusho ukuthi izinkampani zebhukunyazi, abahwebi, namabhizinisi amukela izimali zebhukunyazi avalwa ngokushesha ama-akhawunti abo asebhange. Uma kucatshangelwa ukuthi ibhukunyazi isewumkhakha okhulayo, lesi sinqumo sasiphathelene namakhasimende amaningi e-Quidax. Noma kunjalo, i-Quidax yakwazi ukuthola indlela kulokhu. Inkampani yethule umsebenzi wontanga, eyenza kubelula ukuba amakhasimende afake futhi akhiphe izimali ngokuphepha. Isevisi, ebizwa ngokuthi i-Qdirect, ihlinzeka ngenzuzo eyengeziwe yokwethenjwa - esikhundleni sokusebenzelana nomuntu ongaziwa, wenza ukuthengiselana ngokuqondile ne-Quidax.
Ngale ndlela, amakhasimende aqinisekiswa ngomsebenzi obushelelezi, ovikelekile. Ukwethulwa kwethokheni ye-QDX NgoNhlaba wezi-2021, i-Quidax nayo yashaya ingqophamlando ngemuva kokuthi inkampani yethule ithokheni yayo yebhukunyazi yangaphakathi, i-QDX. Le mpahla emakiwe eyokuqala emkhakheni wezebhukunyazi yase-Afrika, inikela ngezinzuzo ezifana nemivuzo nokubamba iqhaza kumakhasimende okushintshana. Naphezu kokuhamba kancane kwemakethe, ukwethulwa kwe-QDX kuhlangatshezwane nesasasa elikhulu, futhi i-Quidax inyuse amaRandi ayizigidi ezi-3 emalini eyengeziwe kusukela kulokho kwethulwa ngosuku olulodwa. Ukwethulwa kwethokheni kuphinde kwahambisana nokwethulwa kwenkonzo ye-QDX Vault - Quidax. Nge-QDX Vault, abasebenzisi be-Quidax bangakwazi ukufaka i-QDX yabo futhi bathole imiklomelo evela kuma-airdrops neminye imikhankaso yokuphromotha evela kwezohwebo. U-Don Jazzy Wembula kanye Nomkhankaso we-BBN Ukukhula okuqhubekayo kwe-Quidax kwangena ngo-2022, inkampani yaqala izinhlelo ezimbalwa zokumaketha ezihlaba umxhwele ukuthuthukisa ukufinyelela kwayo kanye nomthelela womkhiqizo. Ingxenye yalokho kwaba ukwembulwa kukaMichael Collins - odume ngelikaDon Jazzy - njengenxusa lomkhiqizo walo osemthethweni.
U-Jazzy, ongomunye wabakhiqizi bomculo abaphambili baseNigeria nabaphathi bemboni, usize ekuqhubekiseni imizamo yokuthengisa umkhiqizo we-Quidax, ebambe iqhaza emikhankasweni eminingi njengoba inkampani ikhula iba ngelinye lamagama athenjwayo kwezebhukunyazi. U-Quidax uphinde waba nguzakwethu osemthethweni wohlelo lwango-2022 lwe-Big Brother Naija - umdlalo wabukhoma owaziwa kakhulu e-Afrika. I-Dollar Savings Pivot Enye ingqophamlando ye-Quidax kube ukwethulwa kwethuluzi layo le-Dollar Savings. Umenyezelwe ngoMandulo wezi-2022, umkhiqizo ohlinzeka ngendlela kumakhasimende ukuthi aguqule imali yawo ibe amaDola ase-U.S., ayilondoloze, futhi azuze inzalo efika ku-10% ngonyaka. Ithuluzi belingeke liqalise ngesikhathi esingcono. I-Naira yaseNigeria ilahlekelwe ngaphezu kuka-20% yenani layo uma liqhathaniswa neDola ngo-2022, futhi isendleleni yokulahlekelwa nakakhulu kulo nyaka. Njengoba ukwehla kwamandla emali nakho kufinyelela phezulu, ithuluzi le-Quidax’s Dollar Savings linikeza indlela efanelekile yokuthi noma ubani avikele imali yakhe - futhi azuze izinzuzo ezikhangayo ngenkathi elapho. Ngokunjalo, ihlinzeka ngendlela yokuthi i-Quidax ibhekelele amakhasimende ayo okungenzeka ayixwaye kancane imakethe yezebhukunyazi. Njengoba imboni isebenza ukuze ilulame kwenye imakethe ye-bearish, amakhasimende amaningi angase afune ukulinda kuze kuphele isiphepho kodwa asafuna indlela yokuzuza abe nethuba eliphelele ngethuluzi Lokulondoloza Idola.
Kulo nyaka, inkampani ithuthuke nakakhulu kule sevisi, okwenza amakhasimende akwazi ukukhipha imali ezinhlelweni zawo Zokonga I-Dola kanye namawalethi e-USD aye kuma-akhawunti awo e-Domiciliary. Okufezwe yi-Quidax njengoba inkampani ihlanganisa iminyaka emihlanu kube kuhle kakhulu, ukusho okungenani. Futhi, njengoba imakethe yebhukunyazi ibukeka ilungele ukululama, inkampani izibonakalise iyindawo ethembekile, ephephile kunoma ngubani ofuna ukungena kulomkhakha.
okufundwe ku-Dayari yomqalibhizinisi yentengiselwano ngobuchwepheshe wase-Nigerian "zama nsuku zonke futhi uzame ukubangcono. Ungazehluleli." Umzuzu nomzuzu uyisifundo kithina njengosomabhizinisi, futhi ezweni labasaqalayo lapho izinto zihamba ngokushesha okungaka, kungaba yinto edabukisayo ukusala ngemuva. Mina nethimba lami saba nesikhathi esinzima kakhulu sokusuka kumzila wezindiza wezentengiselwano ngobuchwepheshe, ikakhulukazi ukuba imakethe ye-inthanethi yezinto zokwakha. Kuze kube manje kuhle kakhulu, kodwa sisaphokophele kokungcono kakhulu. Nazi ezinye zezifundo engizifundile ekusebenziseni imakethe yezentengiselwano ngobuchwepheshe. Khetha umkhakha wakho Ngaso sonke isikhathi uma ngitshela abantu ukuthi i-Cribpark iyinkundla yentengiselwano ngobuchwepheshe, bangibuka ngeso elithi, “futhi? Enye inkundla yentingiselwano ngobuchwepheshe ?"
Kepha uma ngengeza ukuthi siyindawo yemakethe yentengiselwano ngobuchwepheshe yezinto zokwakha, bathi, “hh, kuhle lokho. I-twist entsha kwintengiselwano ngobuchwepheshe". Njengoba i-Jumia ne-Konga sebekhulise cishe amakhulu ezigidi zamadola phakathi kwabo, kungcono ukhethe indawo noma uzoba i-Konga.com yomuntu ompofu. Uma ukhetha umkhakha wakho, khetha owodwa owuqonda kahle futhi wenzengcono kakhulu kuwo. Ngisho ne-Amazon yaqala njengesitolo sezincwadi esiku-inthanethi. Lapho siqala njengentengiselwano ngobuchwepheshe yezinto zokwakha saqaphela ukuthi iningi lamakhasimende ethu akuqala kwakungabantu ababeqala ukwakha. Babazi okuncane ngokwakha futhi bengafuni ukuboshwa ngezeluleko zikasonkontileka wabo. Njengoba ithimba lethu ligcwele onjiniyela bezakhiwo, kube lula ngathi ukubanikeza ulwazi ngezinto ababezithenga ababengazi abahlinzeki babo nosonkontileka. Babengagcini ngokukhokhela umkhiqizo, babethola nolwazi olubalulekile lwamahhala. Ukukhetha umkhakha owuthandayo kukusiza ukuthi ugxile emzamweni wakho omuhle kakhulu, futhi awufuni ngempela ukusabalalisa mncane kakhulu.
Khumbula lezo zinsuku lapho ukuthenga kuqala futhi kwaphela emakethe yeYaba; uma ubuthenga nje amajini, bekungenzeka ukuthi uthenge kumuntu odayisa amajini kuphela esitolo sakhe, kunalowo odayisa zonke izinhlobo zezimpahla okuhlanganisa namajini. Yenza umkhiqizo Uphawu lwakho luyisithembiso sakho kukhasimende lakho, yilokho abalilindele enkampanini yakho uma licabanga ngawe. Kungase kuzwakale kusenesikhathi ukukhuluma ngophawo olumele ibhizinisi, kodwa uzovuna izinzuzo kusenesikhathi futhi. Ingabe ufuna ukuqonda ukuthi yini uphawu olumele ibhizinisi lakho? Hhayi-ke, cela amakhasimende akho ukuthi ashiye impendulo ngendlela engaziwa. Ngonyaka odlule ngibe nomhlangano nelinye lamakhasimende ethu e-B2B, u-Engineer Ken. Wathunyelwa kithi yikhasimende le-B2B futhi wayenze umsebenzi ongaphezu kwesigidi esingu-₦1. Ngasekupheleni konyaka ubehlabeke umxhwele ngendlela esidlale ngayo wacela ukuthi sibe nomhlangano. Sixoxile isikhathi esingangehora futhi ungacabanga ukuthi kwakuwukuhlangana kabusha kobungane nakuba bekungokokuqala sibonana.
Sixoxile ngemboni yezokwakha, isimo sengqondo sabahlinzeki futhi sahleka ngokuletha kwethu kokuqala. Kwenzekani ekuletheni kwethu kokuqala? Umphakeli uhlinzeke ngekhwalithi ephansi yesihlabathi esibukhali kodwa unjiniyela u-Ken ubengekho esizeni ngesikhathi sokulethwa. Ngokuvamile, sikhokhela abahlinzeki kuphela uma amakhasimende ebonisa ukwaneliseka, kodwa njengoba evumele ukulethwa, samkhokhela umphakeli. Lapho efika esizeni ezobona izinga lesihlabathi akazange ahlabeke umxhwele. Usibizile ukuze asho ukungenami kwakhe nokuthi ukunikezwa kuzomthinta kanjani njengosonkontileka. Sikhathazekile futhi sayalela umhlinzeki ukuthi abuyele esizeni. Umhlinzeki uvumile ukuthi ikhwalithi ayihlangabezani nezimfuneko azithembisile. Isihlabathi kuzodingeka sisetshenziselwe enye injongo yesayithi kunalokho ebesihlosile. Ngokushesha samkhokhela uNjiniyela u-Ken u-50% walokho akukhokhela.
Kamuva sasikhipha imali kumthengisi kwezinye izinto ayezilethile. Imali ayikwazanga ukuguqula isimo, kodwa okungenani yabonisa ukuthi sasikhathalela kakhulu iphrojekthi yakhe kunenzuzo yethu. Bekungokokugcina futhi ukuthi sibe nezinkinga ezifana nalezi njengoba kudingeke ukuthi siqinise amakhanda ethu. Phakathi nomhlangano, unjiniyela uKen wakhuluma ngendlela ahlabeke umxhwele ngayo ngendlela esisingathe ngayo lesi simo futhi waqinisekisa njalo ukuthi abahlinzeki benza okufanele. Ngamazwi akhe kanye namanye amakhasimende, sasibona ukuthi basibona njengenkampani ethembekile ebeka ikhasimende kuqala ngaphambi kwakho konke ukuthengisa. Amakhasimende awazona izimungulu, ayazi ukuthi uwabeke nini kuqala, aphinde abuye ngoba uwanikeze ulwazi hhayi umkhiqizo. Amaphutha anjalo angenzeka kanye emva kwesikhathi eside, kodwa ezimweni ezinjalo izithembiso zomkhiqizo ziqinisekisiwe. Bonisa ukuthi uyini umkhiqizo wakho, ungasho. Yebo silahlekelwe cishe u-₦ 20,000, kodwa akulutho uma kuqhathaniswa nesikuzuze kuye ekuthengisweni okuphindaphindwayo okungu-8. Hamba ibanga elingeziwe
Shayela i-Cribpark nganoma yisiphi isikhathi futhi sesilungile. Sithole izingcingo ngo-6am, 10pm, 11pm kanye kanye ngo-1am. Kuthe uma bexolisa ngokusifonela emva kwesikhathi, sasheshe sabazisa ukuthi akubanga nankinga nathi. Ngikhumbula ngempelasonto nginenombolo yokunakekela amakhasimende, bekuyimizuzu embalwa lidlule ihora lokuqala ekuseni ngeSonto ekuseni futhi ngathola ucingo. Ngabheka isikhathi, ngakhetha ucingo, futhi angenzanga njengokujwayelekile. Ikhasimende belisendaweni yethu lihlola zonke izinto elifuna ukuzithenga futhi ngibe nenjabulo yokuliqhuba ngomnikelo wethu wenani. Kwenzeka ukuthi ubefuna indawo eyodwa ayengathenga kuyo zonke izinto zakhe zenhlanzeko nezinye izinto zefenisha yendlu yakhe entsha. Saxoxa cishe isigamu sehora futhi sasayina isivumelwano esibiza izigidi ngaso. Njengesiqalo, alikho iphuzu lokwakha amahora ehhovisi ngaphandle kokuthi unesinye isiqinisekiso somholo ekupheleni kwenyanga. Amahora ethu okusebenza yinoma nini ikhasimende likwazi ukusithola, ngezingcingo, ama-imeyili, noma ngisho nasemaphusheni ethu.
Uma nje singatholakala, sesivulile. Ibanga elingeziwe liyisici esikhulu esihlukanisayo ukuze kuqalwe kabusha futhi kungafika ngezindlela ezahlukene. Sasineklayenti elaliphelelwa isihlabathi ngosuku lakha isitezi salo saseJalimane. Wasibiza ngo-12 emini wathi uyayidinga ngo-2 ntambama. Sake samletha ngosuku olufanayo, kodwa nalokhu kwaba inselele. Sishayele umhlinzeki oseduze kakhulu naye futhi sakwazi ukuthi alethe ngohlelo lwakhe olumatasa olukhona. Sishayele iklayenti lethu ukusho ukuthi ngeke silethe u-2pm kodwa kungenzeka ngo-3pm. Ubejabulile ukuthi singathembisa nokukuletha njengoba ngokuvamile ungakutholi kulula ukuthola izinto ezinjalo phakathi nosuku ngaphandle kokuthi uthenge ngosuku olwedlule. Silethe ngo-2.55pm futhi kuze kube namuhla usengomunye wamakhasimende ethu ahamba phambili. Amazwi athi singabahlinzeki bakhe abathembekile futhi.
