Yize ibhizinisi lisabheke ukuqhubeka nokufaka i-bootstrapping kanye nokwandisa ukuthengisa kuze kube yilapho selilungele ukutshalwa kwezimali okulandelayo, kuyajabulisa ukuqaphela ukuthi inkampani izuze isamba sokuthengiswayo samadola angama-$70,000 kusabelomali sokumaketha sika-$350 nje ezinyangeni zayo eziyisikhombisa zokuqala. Usimende, isihlabathi kanye negwadle kubalele ngaphezu kwama-70% okuthengiswayo. Izinselele Kule ngxenye yomhlaba, besingeke siyeke ukukhuluma ngodaba lokwethenjwa, futhi akuhlukanga neze ngeCribpark. Ngasohlangothini lomthengisi, u-Oludare uyachaza, "kunzima ukukholisa abathengisi ikakhulukazi ngoba babuza mayelana nezinzuzo ezisheshayo ." Inkampani ikuxazulule lokhu ngokudlula kubasabalalisi abakhulu kunokusebenzisa izinkampani. Ngakolunye uhlangothi amakhasimende afuna ukubona ukuhlukahluka endaweni yesikhulumi, ikakhulukazi mayelana nokusebenzisana komsebenzisi. Inkampani bekufanele ithathe inkokhelo ekuletheni ukuze kuthenjwe ikhasimende. I-Cribpark ngokuqhubekayo kwadingeka yethule inqubomgomo yokuvikela umthengi ehlinzeka ngezinsizakalo zokukhokha kumakhasimende; inkokhelo kufanele ithunyelwe kumthengisi kuphela ekuqinisekisweni okungu-100% komkhiqizo njengesimo esanelisayo emehlweni ekhasimende. Amathemba
