Inkampani i-DataTech, i-Melon Yethula olunye uhlobo lwe-Beta eyisixazululo Sokuphathwa Kwemininingo ehamba phambili, Inika Amandla Ama-Data Catalysts ase-Afrika I-Melon, inkampani yemininingo yezobuchwepheshe enomgomo wokuba i-Data catalyst ehamba phambili e-Afrika, ijabule kakhulu ukumemezela ukukhishwa kwe-beta kwesisombululo sayo esisha sokubikwa kweimininingo, i-MELON 1.0. Ngokugxila ekuthuthukiseni imiphumela nomthelela wokushayela, inkundla ye-Melon evelele ihlose ukuvala igebe phakathi kokuqoqwa kwemininingo, ukusetshenziswa, nokusabalalisa, ihlinzeka abenzi bezinqumo ngamathuluzi abawadingayo ukuze benze izinqumo ezinolwazi futhi bafeze izinjongo zabo. Ngokombiko wakamuva wocwaningo we-KPMG, imali engase isetshenziswe emakethe yaseNigeria kumini9ningo nezibalo kulindeleke ukuthi ifinyelele kuzigidi ezingama-500 e-naira eminyakeni emithathu ezayo. Lokhu kugqamisa ukubaluleka okukhulayo kokuthathwa kwezinqumo okuqhutshwa iimininingo esifundeni futhi kuqinisa isidingo sokusungula izinto ezintsha ezigxile kumininingo njenge-MELON 1.0. Imakethe yomhlaba wonke yeimininingo enkulu nezibalo zebhizinisi nayo ibhekene nokukhula okubalulekile, okulinganiselwa ku-$198.08 wezigidigidi ngo-2020 futhi kulindeleke ukuthi ifinyelele ku-$684.12 wezigidigidi ngo-2030. Ngesidingo esinencindezi semininingwane eqhutshwa yimininingo, uchungechunge olunamandla lwe-Melon lwamathuluzi namasevisi lufika ngesikhathi esibalulekile kumabhizinisi nezinhlangano ezifuna ukusebenzisa iimininingo ngempumelelo. "E-Melon, sizibophezele ekunikezeni abenzi bezinqumo amandla okwenza izinqumo ezinolwazi futhi bathuthukise umthelela," kusho u-Ayokunle Omoniyi, Umsunguli weMelon. "I-MELON 1.0 iklanywe ngokucophelela ukuze inikeze isithombe esiphelele kwamamethrikhi okusebenza nemiphumela, okwenza abasebenzisi bakwazi ukulandelela izinkomba zokusebenza ezibalulekile futhi balinganise impumelelo yezinhlelo zabo kalula." I-MELON 1.0 iziqhayisa ngezinhlobonhlobo zezici eziyibeka ihluke emakethe, okuhlanganisa ithuluzi lokubika elivumelana nezimo elivumela abasebenzisi ukuthi banikeze imininingwane ngenqubekelaphambili nomthelela wokutshalwa kwezimali noma izinhlelo.
Ideshibhodi yengxenyekazi ehlelwa ngendlela oyifisayo inikeza ukumelwa okuqondile kolwazi nemininingo, kuyilapho amasu ayo esayensi yemininingo ethuthukisiwe ekhiqiza imininingwane ephathekayo ukuze yazise ukuthatha izinqumo ngamasu nokuthuthukiswa kwenqubomgomo. Uhlaka lokubika lomhlaba wonke nolucwaningwe kahle lwe-melon luqinisekisa ukuthi amakhasimende angakwazi ukuqoqa ulwazi lwesikhathi sangempela esebenzisa izindlela ezihlukahlukene zokuqinisekisa kanye namathuluzi endawo anamaki we-geo, okuqinisekisa ukuqoqwa okuphumelelayo kwemininingo enembile nethembekile. “Iqembu lethu labasunguli abahlukahlukene badlala indima ebalulekile ekuqhubekiseni ukufinyelelwa kombono wethu wokuba ngabathuthukisi bemininingo abahamba phambili e-Afrika,” kwengeza u-Ayokunle Omoniyi. "Ngobungcweti nezizinda ezihlukene, ithimba lethu liletha ingcebo yolwazi nemibono etafuleni, okusivumela ukuthi sibhekane nezinselele eziyingqayizivele ezibhekene nezinhlangano ezisebenza e-Afrika ngempumelelo." Ukuzibophezela kukakhabe ukuhlala ngaphambi kwejika kwezobuchwepheshe kanye nezitayela zemboni kubeka inkampani njengomholi emakethe. Ukutshalwa kwezimali okuqhubekayo ocwaningweni nasekuthuthukisweni kwenza i-melon ikwazi ukuhambisana nobuchwepheshe obusafufusa nezindlela ezihamba phambili, iqinisekisa ukuthi amakhasimende ayazuza kuzixazululo ezithuthuke kakhulu ezitholakalayo. Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukuhlonishwa nokusekelwa kukaMelon ezinhlelweni ezifana neTony Elumelu Foundation Entrepreneurship Award ngo-2022, lapho akhethwa khona phakathi kweziqalo ezimbalwa ukuze athole imali yokuqala, kugqamisa amandla enkampani nokuzinikela ekuqhubekiseni izinguquko ezinhle ngemininingo yase-Afrika. Njengoba i-Afrika isondela onyakeni ohlosiwe we-Sustainable Development Goals (i-SDGs), ukuqapha imininingo kanye nokuziphendulela kudlala indima ebalulekile ekuhloleni inqubekelaphambili kanye nokufeza lezi zinhloso zomhlaba. Nge-MELON 1.0, i-melon ihlose ukuguqula izinqumo eziqhutshwa imininingo, ivumele amabhizinisi, izinhlangano, nabenzi bezinqubomgomo ukuthi basebenzise amandla emininingo futhi baqhube imiphumela enomthelela kuyo yonke imikhakha ehlukahlukene. Mayelana ne-melon:
I-Melon Data services LTD yinkampani yobuchwepheshe bemininingo ezinikele ekubeni i-Data catalyst ehamba phambili e-Afrika. Ngengosi yayo ephambili, i-MELON 1.0, i-melon inika abenzi bezinqumo amandla ngamathuluzi amasha nezinsizakalo zokuvala igebe phakathi kokuqoqwa kwemininingo, ukusetshenziswa, nokusabalalisa. Ngokusebenzisa amasu esayensi yemininingo asezingeni eliphezulu kanye nohlaka lokubika olucwaningwe kahle, i-melon ihlose ukuthuthukisa imiphumela futhi iqhube umthelela kuyo yonke i-Afrika. Ukuze uthole ulwazi olwengeziwe mayelana ne-melon nokukhishwa kwe-beta kwe-MELON 1.0, sicela uvakashele ku-https://melon.ng/ noma uxhumane nathi: solutions@melon.ng futhi ulandele imisebenzi yethu ku-LinkedIn naku-Twitter.
Ukuqala kwe-healtech yaseNigeria, I-Remedial Health, inyusa ama- $ 12 wezigidi ku-Series A uxhaso ukuze kwandiswe ukufinyeleleka kwezinsizakalo zayo Ukuqalwa kobuchwepheshe bezempilo eNigeria, Impilo Yokulungisa, kunyuse amaRandi ayizigidi ezingu-12 oxhaso lwe-Series A - amaRandi ayizigidi ezingu-8 ngokulingana kanye nezikweletu zamaRandi ayizigidi ezingu-4 - ukwandisa ukufinyelela kwezinsizakalo zakho ezweni. Le nkampani izophinde isebenzise izimali ukusekela ukulethwa kwezinsizakalo zezezimali ezihlosiwe ukuze kuqhutshekwe nokukhula kwebhizinisi kuwo wonke umkhakha wezokwelapha waseNigeria. I-QED Investors and Ventures Platform ihole ngokubambisana emzuliswaneni woxhaso lwezimali. Nakuba lokhu kuwutshalomali lwesibili lwangaphambili ekuqaliseni kwe-Afrika, lokhu kutshale kwezempilo Yokulungisa kusukela ekuqaleni kwesigaba sokuxhasa. Kuphinde kube yi-Ventures Platform yokuqala yokutshala imali yochungechunge A. U-Gaingels, u-Tencent, no-Ycombinator babambe iqhaza ngemuva kokubamba iqhaza emizuliswaneni yangaphambili. Umfelandawonye wezikhungo zezimali zasekhaya nezamazwe ngamazwe uhole ekuxhasweni kwezikweletu eziyizigidi ezine zamaRandi. Yethulwa ngo-2022 nguSamuel Okwuada (i-CEO) kanye no-Victor Benjamin (i-COO), I-Remedial Health iyisiqalo sobuchwepheshe esifaka idijithali uchungechunge lokuhlinzekwa kwemithi. Inkampani ye-B2B ihlinzeka ngohleloxhumano yamakhemisi nezibhedlela ukuphatha i-inventory yabo nokuthengisa.
Le nkampani isiza amakhemisi ukuthi athole imikhiqizo yemithi yamashalofu awo kubakhiqizi abakhulu nabasabalalisi, okuhlanganisa i-GSK, i-Pfizer, i-AstraZeneca, i-Emzor, ne-Fidson Healthcare. Iphinde inikeze uxhaso lwezimali emakhemisi noma ezibhedlela ezingenayo imali edingekayo yokuthenga izidakamizwa ezidingekayo. Kubakhiqizi bemithi, I-Remedial Health inikeza umzila osebenzayo oye emakethe wemikhiqizo yabo kanye nemininingwane eqhutshwa imininingo ezimakethe zasendaweni abangayisebenzisa ukuze bahlele ngempumelelo kakhudlwana nokwenza izinqumo. Ukuqala kobuchwepheshe bezempilo eNigeria, I-Remedial Health, ifaka idijithali uchungechunge lokuhlinzekwa kwemithi futhi inikezela ngezimali zokusungula emakhemisi. I-Remedial futhi inesitolo esiku-inthanethi esivumela abanikazi bamakhemisi abangasebenzisi uhleloxhumano layo ukufaka ama-oda ngohlelo lwayo lokusebenza lweselula. Abanikazi bezitolo bangasebenzisa uhlelo lokusebenza lweselula ukuthola imikhiqizo engaphezu kuka-8,000 ehloliwe, ngokudiliva kosuku olufanayo nokuxhaswa ngezimali kwe-inventory ukuze kuncishiswe ukungqubuzana kwemali etholakalayo kuma-oda avamile nokwandisa amathuba okuthengisa. Ngenkathi i-Remedial imemezela uxhaso lwayo loxhaso lwezigidi ezi--$4.4 ngoMandulo wezi- 2022, u-Okwuada wembula ukuthi ukuqalisa kwase kusebenza ezifundazweni ezingu-16 zaseNigeria futhi kunezinhlelo zokusabalala ezweni lonke. Manje, inkampani ithi isebenza nabakhiqizi abangaphezu kuka-300 futhi inikeza izibhedlela ezingaphezu kuka-5,000, amakhemisi, kanye nabathengisi bemithi ye-Proprietary Patent Medicine (PPMVs) kuzo zonke izifundazwe ezingama-34 kwezingu-36 zaseNigeria. Lapho ebuzwa ukuthi inkampani isikhule kanjani ezifundazweni eziningi eNigeria esikhathini esingaphansi konyaka, i-CEO ithe ibone izwe futhi manje iyaqonda ukuthi ibhizinisi lisebenza kanjani. Wengeze ngokuthi inkampani ifuna ukufinyelela kubantu abaningi.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, uthe ngenkathi inkampani isabalalisa kuzo zonke izifundazwe ezingama-36, ayikaze iqashe abasebenzi ezindaweni ezimbili. Khonamanjalo, ukufeza lokho kufike nezinselelo, futhi u-Okwuada wakuchaza “njengephupho elibi lokuhlela.” “Ukuhambisa into emgwaqeni kuyiphupho elibi, kusukela ekutholeni umaqondana — uma umdinga — kuya emigwaqweni engemihle kuya ekususweni kwezibonelelo zikaphethiloli, okuholela ekunyukeni kukaphethiloli kubathengi ongakwazi ukuwudlulisela ngo-100%. , kwabomthetho emgwaqeni abasuke befuna ukuqolwa." Kodwa-ke, uthi inkampani iyayiqonda inselele futhi iyazi ukuthi izwe lisebenza kanjani, nakuba kungenjalo ngokuphelele, kodwa ezingeni eliphezulu ngokwanele ukuthi lingasabalalisa ngempumelelo kuzo zonke izifundazwe. Selokhu yathola uxhaso lokuqala, inkampani ikhulise inani layo ngokuphindwe kabili, imali engenayo ngokuphindwe kahlanu, kanye nenani lamakhasimende ayo ngokuphindwe kathathu. Ngaphezu kwalokho, i-Remedial ihlela ukukhulisa ukunikezwa kwayo okukhona ngamasevisi amasha, okuhlanganisa izinkokhelo nezinsizakalo zokunakekelwa kwezempilo okuyisisekelo njengokuvakasha kodokotela noma ukuxilongwa umuntu ekude.
I-Healthlane inyuse u-$2.4m, yabe isisuka endaweni ekahle yokusebenzela yaya emiholweni eyikweletwayo, yadiliza abasebenzi, yaphinde yahlukaniswa nezimali. Manje kubikwa ukuthi iphakamisa uchungechunge A Ngenkathi ukuqaliswa kobuchwepheshe bezempilo baseCameroonia, HEALTHLANE BY GIFTEDMOM LIMITED (Healthlane), yethulwa ngokusemthethweni eNigeria zi-9, kuL;wezi wezi 2021, Umhleli wethu Ophethe, u-Emmanuel Paul, uhambele umcimbi ehhovisi le-Healthlane eLekki, eLagos, eNigeria. Emcimbini wokwethulwa, kwathiwa u-Alain Nteff (CEO) kanye no-Agbor Ashumanyi Ako (umsunguli kanye noMqondisi Wezokwelapha) baqale i-Heallane eCameroon ngo-2019 ukusiza abantu base-Afrika ukuthi bathole izinsizakalo zezempilo ezisezingeni eliphezulu nezithengekayo. Omunye wodokotela abangaphakathi kwaHealtlane uveze ukuthi ukuqalisa kunikeze izivivinyo ezifika kwezingama-78, imiphumela ivamise ukuphuma emizuzwini engama-45. Inkampani inikeze uhlelo lokuphakela, ukwengezela, noma lokuzivocavoca oluvela emiphumeleni yokuhlolwa. Ngakho, ngo-2022, abanye abasebenzi be-Techpoint Africa - uChimgozirim Nwokoma, u-Yinka Awosanya, u-Emmanuel Paul, no-Precious Mogoli- basebenzisa inkundla. Ngesikhathi uMogoli, uNwokoma, kanye no-Paul bebhalisela uhlelo lokuhlola umzimba wonke, u-Awosanya ubhalisele ukuthola umjovo wakhe we-Hepatitis B. Kodwa ngenkathi, ngoMandulo, u-Awosanya efuna ukuthatha umthamo wokugcina womgomo, wabona izimpawu ezikhathazayo eziphakamisa ukuthi i-Healthlane ingase ingasebenzi. “Ukusabela kokuqala kwaba ukuthi udokotela wayengekho,” kukhumbula u-Awosanya, “kamuva, ngatshelwa ukuthi ihhovisi labo lalilungiswa nokuthi babeza endlini yami noma ehhovisi ukuze bangiqondise. Kodwa abazange bakwenze lokho.
Ngemva kwalokho, uhlelo lwabo lwayeka ukusebenza.” Phakathi kuka-Ncwaba noMandulo, ngathola ukuxilonga okubili okuhlukene kodokotela ababili ngesevisi ye-HMO ye-Techpoint Africa. Bengizibuza ukuyikho kangakanani ukuxilonga kwabo. Ngaphandle kwalokho, nganikezwa imithi ethile, engayekisa ngenxa yomehluko ocacile wokuxilongwa. Ngifuna umbono wesibili, bengifuna ukuhlolwa ukuze ngiqinisekise ukuxilonga, ngakho ngilande uhlelo lokusebenza lwe-Heallane esitolo u-Google Play ukuze ngibone ukuthi belungasebenzi. Ibilahlekile futhi ku-Apple App Store. Ngaqala ukufinyelela kubasebenzi benkampani bamanje nabangaphambili, futhi engakuthola kwakukukhulu kunalokho engangikwesaba. Kodwa, ngaphambi kokuthi ngikudlulisele kulokhu kudalulwa, ake sibuyele ekuqaleni. Ekuqaleni Indaba esemthethweni ukuthi i-Healthlane yethulwe ngo-2019.
Kodwa-ke, ngokusho kwemithombo eminingi, ayizange yethulwe eCameroon noma eNigeria kuze kube ngu-2021, unyaka ngemuva kokukhuphula utshalomali oluyizigidi ezingama- $ 2.4 ngo-2020. Khonamanjalo, u-Alain Nteff uthe wasungula inkundla yezempilo ephathwayo, i-GiftedMom Limited (GiftedMom), ngo-2012, kamuva eyasebenzisa i-Healthlane ngoNdasa wezi-2019. Kodwa ngokomunye wemithombo yethu, i-Healtlane yahlanganiswa njengoGiftedMom ngo-2015, hhayi ngo-2012. I-athikili ye-GSMA, ebala u-GiftedMom njengesiqalo sephothifoliyo, ibonakala iqinisekisa lesi simangalo. Ngokusho komthombo, ukuqala kwashintsha abanikazi bamasheya futhi kwavala igatsha layo laseYaoundé ngosuku olungaziwa. Ngo-2021, yaqasha abasebenzi abathile ukuthi basebenze eDouala. Ngenxa yalokho, imisebenzi yaseDouala yaqala phakathi kukaNtulikazi noNcwaba ngawo lowo nyaka. Imithombo eminingi ithi i-Healtlane yayinesiko elihle lomsebenzi ngenkathi yethulwa okokuqala ngo-2021 eNigeria naseCameroon. Kangangoba abaningi bebezimisele ukusebenza ngaphezu kwamashifu abebewahlelile ukuze baqinisekise ukuthi ukusebenza kwenkampani kuhamba kahle. “Sisanda kuba nendawo enhle yokusebenza lapho sonke singabangane.
Besithemba, futhi wonke umuntu wayelokhu ephusha ukukhipha imkhiqizo ngoba besazi ukuthi sizozuza uma sidayise kakhulu,umthombo olwaziyo lolu daba esho. Abasebenzi baseNigeria babefinyelela kuzindawo zokuzivocavoca zenkampani. Kwakukhona nezithelo zesihe, amasaladi,nesidlo sasemini, inkampani izokhokha uhhafu wezindleko zesidlo sasemini. Inkampani yaphinde yathembisa abasebenzi ukuthi bazoyozivuselela ekupheleni kuka-2022. Kodwa azikho kulezizinzuzo, nokho, ezilungiselwe bona "ukuqedwa" "nezindawo zokusebenza ezingathokozisi" lokho kwakusazolandela. Futhi ukuzivuselela akuzange kwenzeke. Ngokomthombo eCameroon, injongo yasekuqaleni yenkampani kwakuwukusebenzisa imithi yokuvikela ukusiza abantu ukuthi baphile isikhathi eside futhi baphile kangcono. Kodwa imodeli yebhizinisi labo yayingenayo indlela yokuhwebelana namasu okudayisa babencike ethembeni. Ushintsho esikweni lokusebenza Umthombo uthi njengamanje isiko lokusebenza aliyilutho kodwa alixhumani namuntu, lithule, liqamba amanga, lenza izinto ngaphandle ngaphandle kokuxhumana nemibono efanele,nemihlangano engenasidingo nokuphathwa yikhanda
Kodwa kwenzeke kanjani ukuthi inkampani enesiko lokusebenza elihle kangaka ivele ishintshe nje? Ngaphezu kwalokho imithombo eminingi iyasho ukuthi inkampani ayinaso isakhiwo noma indlela ephathelene nendlela yeHealthlane, izinjongo noma isu. Isibonelo umthombo uthi,"Inkampani eCameroon yayididekile ngendlela yokuthi baqala balingisa okwakwenziwa emazweni anezinkampani,behluleka ukubona ukuthi izimakethe zethu zazihlukile. Ngesikhathi bebona ukuthi bekungekho okudayisayo, baze bacabanga ukuguqula lendawo bayenze umtholampilo Kodwa lokho kusolwa kokungabibikho kwesakhiwo nokuqonda kwakuyisiqalo. Ngama akhawunti amaningi, imiholo yayijwayele ukukhokhwa ingakapheli inyanga, kwaze kwaba uZibandlela ngonyaka wezi-2021, Ngesikhathi abaphathi bazisa abasebenzi ukuthi bazosheshe bavale ngamaholidi kaKhisimusi. Bonke abasebenzi baphinde bacelwa ukuthi bathathe izinsuku ezinhlanu zokusebenza kube yilivu ngempoqo ngesikhathi sekhefu. Inkampani yaphoqa ukwenza ilivu yezinsuku ezinhlanu zokusebenza kuwona wonke umuntu, owayengumsebenzi azisa iTechpoint Africa. NgoZibandlela mhlaka 16 ngonyaka wezi-2021, iHealthlane yenza umcimbi wokuphela konyaka endaweni yayo nabasebenzi kanye nabadayisi bayo. Imithombo eminingi yaveza ukuthi ngemva kwalokho akekho umsebenzi owathola iholo lakhe ngokuphela kukaZibandlela.
Imiholo yabambezeleka futhi yakweletwa ngoba yinkampani esanda kuqala ngoMfumfu kunyaka wezi-2021, bekukuningi obekwenzeka, kusho umthombo. Kubikwa ukuthi uNteff waqinisekisa ithimu ukuthi inkampani yayinayo imali eyibeke eceleni ukubhekelela ukusebenza kuze kube ukuqala kukaMasingana ngonyaka wezi-2022. Ngakho babehlezi befisa ukwazi incazelo yangempela yokuthi kungani inkampani yayihluleka ukukhokhela abasebenzi nabadayisi nokweqa intela nempesheni ukuthi ithathwe emiholweni yabasebenzi. Imithombo eminingi iyaqinisekisa ukuthi ekuqaleni kukaMasingana ngonyaka wezi-2022, kwakungekho ukuxhumana okuqhamuka kubaphathi ukuthi kungani imiholo yayibambezelekile. Ngasekupheleleni kwenyanga, abasebenzi baqala bakhombisa ukuthi kukhona abakusolayo. Kwakungenzeki kwaze kwashaya isikhathi ngoMasingana lapho lasatshelwa ukuthi inkampani inezinkinga ezincane ngokungena nokuphuma kwemali, kukhumbula umthombo. ngesikhathi abanye abasebenzi bethola imiholo yaZibandlela sekuyophela uMasingana , abanye bayithola ngoNhlolanja ngonyaka wezi-2022. Kubikwa ukuthi iHealthlane yaphinda yaqala phansi uhlelo lwemiholo yangoMasingana, futhi ngoNhlaba, eNigeria yayisiqalile ukubambezela izinkokhelo zemiholo futhi. Ngesikhathi sokushicilelwa, kubikwa ukuthi inkampani ikweleta abasebenzi babo baseNigeria imoholo yezinyanga ezine kusekela ngoNtulikazi.
Ngokomthombo omunye wabasebenzi eCameroon wazisa abaphathi ukuthi bazomisa imisebenzi yabo baze bathole okungenani imiholo yezinganga ezimbili kule yezinyanga ezinhlanu abakweletwa yona. “Abaphathi” baphendula ngokuthi “bayalele onogada ukuthi bangabavumeli ukuthi bangene emahhovisi ngesikhathi bebasusa ezindaweni zokusebenza. Yaphinde yazisa ehhovisis lezabasebenzi eCameroon ukuthi umsebenzi useyeke ukwenza imisebenzi yakhe ngaphandle kwesexwayiso.” Ngokomthombo waseNigeria, "Kuke kwafika isikhathi ngonyaka wezi-2022, sasingezwa lutho oluvela ehhovisi. Njengoba kubonakala ukuthi abaphathi benza izinqumo bebodwa, sayeka ukuzwa ngabo. Abakuthwali. Abaphenduli. Abalandeleli." Ngokomunye umthombo, abasebenzi babelokhu benezikhalo ngokuthi kungani ulwazi lungaphumi ngesikhathi semihlangano. Babefisa ukwazi ukuthi yini eyenza kube nzima ukutshela abasebenzi ukuthi kwenzakalani.
Babefuna ukwazi nje ukuthi kungani “abantu abaqala umsebenzi bengasebenzi ngendlela elindelekile, kodwa abasunguli babengabatsheli iqiniso.” Imithombo eminingi yayikhononda ngokuthi ayijwayele ukuthola izimpendulo “kubaphathi” noma yinini uma bezama ukuxhumana nabo. Omunye wabasunguli uAshu wayehlezi ebadlulisela kuCEO uNteff ngaso sonke isikhathi uma bezama ukuxhumana naye, ekhombisa ukuthi akukho angakusho ngaloludaba. Ukumiswa emsebenzini nokusula emsebenzini Ngesikhathi inkampani inesiko lokusenza elihle ngaphambi kukaZibandlela ngonyaka wezi-2021, imithombo ithi yayizibona izinkomba eziyizexwayiso kodwa ayinakanga. Ukwenza isibonelo ngoMandulo ngonyaka wezi-2021 kwabikwa ukuthi iCEO yaxosha umsebenzi, owabuye wabuyiselwa emsebenzini kodwa sekwehliswe umholo futhi esehlisiwe esikhundleni, nokuqashwa kwakhe kwanqanyulwa inyanga ingaphelile. "Ukungazinzi kwenzawo yokusebenza kungenye yezikhali ezibalulekile zenkampani,” kuveza umthombo, “Isimo sesikhulile kusukela ukuqala konyaka ngenxa yezizathu eziningi okuhlanganisa ukubambezeleka, ukufika kamuva kokungakhokhelwa kusukela ngoZibandlela wezi-2021." Kusuka ngonyaka wezi-2021 iHealthlane yayinezinto eziqinisa iqembu labawu-12 nabawu-10 eNigeria naseCameroon. Yayiphinde ibe nabayitoho abayisishagalombili kuwona womabili amazwe. Kodwa ke imithombo yaseCameroon naseNigeria yathi ukumiswa emsebenzini kwaba yinto ejwayelekile eHealthlane ngesikhathi kuqala unyaka wezi-2022.
ECameroon umsebenzi waxoshwa abanye ababili basula ngenxa "yezimo zokusebenza ezimbi." Okusempeleni izimo ezifanayo ezenza abantu abayisikhombisa basule emsebenzini emva kokuthi abathathu babemisiwe emsebenzini. ngesikhathi sokubhala, imithombo yakhombisa ukuthi kubandakanya abasunguli, njangamanje inkampani inabasebenzi abathathu eNigeria nabane eCameroon. "Labo abasula emsebenzini babephoqelekile ukwenza njalo. Icebo labaphathi ukukwenza ungabi umsebenzi walutho uze usule emsebenzini, futhi bayaxolelwa kunoma yimaphi amacala," kusho umsebenzi. Iphepha elabonwa yiTechpoint Africa liveza ukuthi inkampani yaxosha bonke abasebenzi abayisishagalombili abayitoho. Ukulungiswa kabusha kwebhilidi nohlelokusetshenzwa olubuyekeziwe lokusetshenziswa Ekuqaleni ngike ngakusho ukuthi isisetshenziswa seHealthlane sasingasebenzi kanjani kuAndriod futhi singatholakali kusigcinazisetshenzisa. Uma ngibuza abasebenzi bamanje nababesebenza kulenkampani ukuthi kungani isisetshenziswa singasebenzi, abaningi babobathi abanalo ulwazi. Omunye wabo wabeka ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi u-Alaina ukweleta uApple
Yize noma uHealthlane uthi okwamanje basenza izinguquko kusisetshenziswa, imithombo eminingi yaqinisekisa ukuthi isissetshenziswa besingasebenzi kusuka ngoMandulo wezi-2022. Ngomhlaka-9 kuLwezi ngonyaka wezi-2022, kuqhudelwano ngentengo ukwenza umqondo wakho konke lokhu, ngikhethe ukukhuluma nabanye abatshalizimali baseHealthlane. Okujabulisayo, ngosuku olulandelayo ukusebenza kwezisetshenziswa kumadivayisi akaAndriod kwasukuvele kwavuseleleka. Kwaphinde kwabakhona futhi nakusigcinasisentshenzisa. Kodwa ke ukusebenza kokubhukha kwakungakabi khona. "U-Alian akanyena umakhi womahambanaye. Kungenzeka ukuthi wenza inkontileka nabathuthukisi bangaphandle ukuthi basebenze isisetshenziswa," kusho owayengumsebenzi, "Okwamanje usaqhubeka nokukweleta onjiniyela bangaphakathi kanye nabasebenzi bakhe." Baphinde basho ukuthi iHealthlane inkampani ngokwephepha kuphela ngoba awukho umkhiqizo, "ingwaba yamanga nje kuphela." Ihhovisi leHealthlane laseNigeria laliku-16 Adewale Kolawole Crescent, Lekki, eLagos State, eNigeria "kwaze kwaba NguNcwaba ngonyaka wezi-2022 ngesikhathi inkampani ishiya kuleli bhilidi. Irenti yaphelelwa yisikhathi ngoNhlangulana 30 ngonyaka wezi-2022
Ngenxa yalokho, owayengumsebenzi uyakugcizelela ukuthi "akukho okulungiswayo okwenzekayo kwenziwa yinkampani. Ngokusemthethweni iHealthlane eNigeria ayinahhovisis. Izinto zenkampani zapakishwa emzini womsebenzi, abasebenzi bazithola besebenzela emakhaya ngesikhathi besalinde umbono olandelayo Omunye uyengeza ukuthi "Ikhasimende labo lamanje bagcine ukulibona ngoNtulikazi, ngakho okunye emva kwalokho kwakungukwenza nje." Ngavakashela indawo yenkampani eLekki ngoLwesibili ukuqinisekisa lokhu. Ukungabibikho kwezinkombandlela eHealthlane kwaba yinto yokuqala engayiqaphela uma ngifika lapha. Ukubuka kanye nje kusakhiwo empeleni kwakungekho lutho. Ukulandela uphenyo olwaluqhubeka ngebhilidi, imithombo emibili yaqinisekisa ukuthi kwakungekhomuntu owayehlala kuleli bhilidi. Baphinde basho ukuthi inkampani yahamba ezinyangeni ezimbili ngaphambilini. Ngokomunye wabo umasitende uyena osengumnikazi webhilidi.
Ngaxhumana nomxhasi wethu weHMO ukuthola ukuthi bayazi yini ngokwenzekayo nokuthi babesabambisene neHealthlane. Ngesikhathi beqinisekisa ukubambisana kwabo, babengenaso isisqiniseko sendawo lakutholakala iHealthlane. Umthombo uyaqinisekisa ukuthi, "Akukho ukulungiswa kabusha owenzekayo eCameroon. Angiboni ukuthi yini ekhona ukuze kwenziwe kabusha ukuze ukusebenza kungenzeki. Bakweleta ngisho abadayisayo abaningi futhi kunzima ngisho ukukhokhela izikwelethu zikagesi." Omunye umsebenzi uyengeza ukuthi indawo yaseNigeria kwakumele ivalwe nhoNtulikazi ngenxa yokuthi kwakubiza ukuyinakekela, okufaka irenti, ukulungisa okufile, ijeneretha kanye nokunakekela indawo yokubhukuda. Emva kokuvalwa, abasebenzi batshelwa ukuthi kuzoqashwa indawo encane okwesikhashana. Kodwa ke ekuhambeni kwesikhathi batshelwa ukuthi ngeke kube nehhovisi nokuthi iHealthlane okungcono izogxila kuemisebenzini yezelebhu yangaphandle ngesikhathi benza ukulandelela kwamasu okunakekela kwezifo zezempilo zamahlalakhona. Kodwa kwakungenjalo eCameroon. Ngesikhathi ihhovisi lingakavalwa,isu laguquka kusukwa ekuhlolweni nohlelo lokunakekela lwaya ekuphindiseleni emuva uhlelo, futhi kamuva nje awukho umsebenzi.
Ngakho ke abekho abasebenzi benkontileka ababeqashiwe kusuka ngoMfumfu ngoba ayikho imiholo esikhokhiwe kusuka ngoMbasa ngonyaka wezi-2022 eCameroon. Umbuzo wesigidi esiwu-1.4 zamadola Ngokubona ukuthi iHealthlane ibikade inesiko lokusebenza elihle, yaba yinkathazo ngokuhluleka ukuxhumana nabasebenzi babo, ukubambezeleka nokukweletwa kwemiholo nokuxoshwa kwabasebenzi omunye angayiqagela imbangela yalokhu. IHealthlane yenza izigidi ezingu-$2.4 wembewu ngonyaka wezi-2020 base baqala ukusebenza ngoNcwaba wezi-2021. Kodwa kusukela ngoNhlaba kunyaka wezi-2021, kulandela uhlelo lokuqasha olwaqala ngoNdasa, inkampani yayinemali engaphansi kwesigidi esisodwa samadola eyayisele. Umbuzo wezigidi ezingu-$1.4 uthi, "Kwenzakalani kuzigidi ezingu-$1.4 mande kuqale ukusebenza kweHealthlane?" Ngokomthombo ososndelene naloludaba, iHealthlane ayinalo ibhodi labaqondisi. UNteff iCEO "umphathi" futhi okunguyena osayindela ama akhawunti enkampani. "Ngaphambi kokuba kuqale ukusetshenzwa enkampanini, uNteff wayesevele eqalile ukukhipha izamba zemali. Kunokukhishwa nokufakwa kwemali okusolisayo okukhombisa ukuthi inkampani ibiyisa kwenye indawo uxhasozimali."
Imithombo eminingi iyakuqinisekisa ukuthi iCEO yathenga impahlakusebenza ingazange ixhumane nabasebenzi. Lokho kwaholela ukuthi kusetshenziswe imali kumpahlakusebenza okwakungenasidingo noma okwakungadingwa yinkampani. Isibonelo wathenga abahlaziyi bezegazi ngesikhathi inkampani isivele inababili abasebenzayo. "Ngesikhathi lokhu kuthenga kunesidingo, kwenziwa ngaphandle kokuxhumana namalunga eqembu afanele, ngakho awubanga namsebenzi ngesikhathi ufika," kusho umthombo. Baphinde baveza ukuthi uNteff wazifihla kanjani ezinyangeni ezintathu eHhotela i-Eko nakumaSuthi aseLagos ngesikhathi abakweletisimali bakhe bemkhiphile eCameroon naseNigeria. Yize noma bengeke babuthole ubufakazi obuqanda ikhanda kusho umthombo "Ama-ejenti okubuyisa izikweletu iPayhippo ayizange iphumelele ukumthola ehhovisi izikhathi ezingingi." Amadokhumenti amaningi akhombisa ukuthi uNteff wasebenzisa izimali zenkampani ezindlekweni zakhe, kumshiya enezikweletu kubadayisi abaningi kubandakanya isisetshenziswa saka-Fintech esibolekisa ngemali. Uzokhumbula ukuthi iHealthlane kwakungenye yeziqalo zaseAfrika ezingu-60 ezazikhethiwe ukuhlanganyela okwesibili kuGoogle kuStartups Black Founders Fund (BFF) ngoMandulo ngonyaka wezi-2022. Kwenzakaleni ezimalini? Yini okumele yenzeke manje? Ngokomthombo uNteff wayeka ukuza ehhovisis eCameroon esontweni lesibili kuLwezi nhgonyaka wezi-2022.
Lokho kwaba amasonto ambalwa emfa kokuthi uAgbor eyekile ukuza ehhovisi. uAlian wapakisha yonke into ehhovisi lakhe. Wayalela umuntu onakekela amahhovisi ukuthi adlulisele isikhiye sakhe sehhovisi kuReevy Ngokwesimo, iReevy inkampani yaseCameroon yayibambisene ngezinto zezempilo neHealthlane ezweni. Ngokomthombo, "kunamahemuhemui athi u-Alian wayehlela ukudayisela uReevy ihhovisi." Kusho ukuthi njengamanje uReevy wayeselithathile ihhovisi futhi esesebenza ukuthi kuqalwe futhi ukusebenza, kodwa ke uAlian wayesaphethe umunxa wezobuchwepheshe benkampani Ukuqhubeka, umthombo uthi uReevy wayezosebenza njengeHealthlane eCameroon ezinyengeni eziyisithupha ezilandelayo ngaphambi kokuba ashintshe igama. Ngokwabo, "izinyanga eziyisisthupha kwakuyisikhathi esanele ku-Alian ukuthi aqhubeke enze abatshalizimali izilima ukuthi inkampani iyasebenza ukuze ezokwazi ukwenza iSeries A." Imithombo eminingi ibika ukuthi uNteff ubheke ukukhulisa iSeries A ngonyaka wezi-2023. Ukwenza lokhu ngoba efuna ukukhokhela izikweleti zakhe eziningi kusho umthombo, Yingakho ezokuphika ukuthi uzovala iHealthlane
Omunye umthombo uthi bezwa ukuthi uAlan ufuna umlimngani abazothenga naye ingxenye yezempilo yeHealthlane ngesikhathi eqhubeka nombono wakhe wemithi yezingcingo awuphakamisa kubatshalizimali. Okunye futhi umthombo ngesikhathi sokubhala, washo ukuthi iCEO yathumela izithombe kubasebenzi abangaphezu kwababili eNigeria esho ukuthi usethumele nge inthanethi imiholo yezinyanga ezintathu kubona kumele baqinisekise. Baphinde basho ukuthi uNteff wathi uzohlakaza iqembu laseNigeria. Kodwa ke inkampani yaxosha abasebenzi ababili eNigeria emva kokuthi beqinisekise imiholo yabo Ngesikhathi sokubhalaakekho kubasebenzi baseCameroon owayethole imiholo ababeyikweletwa. ITechpoint Africa yaxhumana neCEO uNteff ukuqinisekisa lokhu kanye neminye imininingwane. Unteff waphendula ngokuthi izitatimende eziningi azisho iqiniso. Kepha ke ngenxa yophenyo oluqhubekayo lokufinyelela okungekho emthethweni kumafayela aseHealthlane yizintatheli, ngeke sikwazi ukukunikeza impendulo ngaphambi komqamulajuqu wakho. Ekupheleni kwakolu phenyo,siyojabula ukukhipha isitatimende esigcwele
Ukwethula iCircue: isisetshenziswa sokuhamba esisha esibekelwe ukwenza uguquko ukuthi uwubona kanjani umhlaba Kusuka kulokhu kuqala iCircue ibinenjongo eyodwa - ukwenza ukuhamba kube lula, ngokuhlanganisa ezobuchwepheshe nobuntu ukuletha ukufinyeleleka, ulwazi okuyilo nomuzwa wokuhamba njengomphakathi. Isisetshenziswa sokuhamba iCircue sichazwa nguMsunguli uTaiwo Gbadegesin "njengoguquko olukhulu ukufeza injongo yebhrendi", ukuthulwa kabusha bukhoma ngoMbasa eyayisingathwe ngowezokuhamba - udokotela wewakawaka kugadwe ngu-Enech Dominica. Kwakungumcimbi owawugcwele izihambeli kanye nezikhulumi njengo Dkt Chinoso Egbemba owaziwa ngengo dokotela Aproko, uMsunguli weCyclebreeze, uFaith Olayini noLabby uMsunguli weZokuxhumana, u-Omolabake Ogundero obaboleke izwi ukudingida ezokuhamba nezinkinga zokushintsha indawo. Abasebenzi bezinkundla zokuxhumana uAsiwaju Lerry noMaleek bebekhona. Emcimbini cishe abantu abangamashumi amathathu abebethamele abathole imiklomelo econsisa amathe, emzwamweni wokubuyisela emuva umsunguli akubiza ngokuthi "abamukeli bayo bokuqala". Imiklomelo ibandakanya: Uhambo olukhokhelwe zonke izindleko oluya entabeni iObudu (zifakiwe izithombe zaseObudu) lapho abawinile abanenhlanhla bezobona izintaba zesimanga zifihlekile edolobheni elipholile laseObudu, endaweni iCross River eNigeria. amakhompuyutha abafundi, abanini bamabhizinisi nabafisa ukwazi ngobuchwepheshe. Imali yokufaka isicelo sevisa kubantu abafisa ukuthutha bayohlala phesheya.
Imali yokufaka isicelo kwabafuna iziqu kanye nesikole sabaphothulile, phakathi kwezinye izinto. Uma ucabanga ukuthi lokhu kuyajabulisa, izinto ezifakwe kusisetshenziswa sokuhamba uzohlabeka umxhwele. Kucabange lokhu, inkundla yaku-inthanethi lapho ungakwazi ukwabelana ngezinto ozithakaselayo, ukuxhumana, ukuhlola ulwazi olungabiza izigidi ngezifunda ezahlukene ngesikhathi ubheka ngebalazwe, uhumushele kulimi lwebele kuya olimini oluncamelayo, ukuguqula izimali,isikhathi nokunye okuningi. Okuseqinisweni yiphupho lawo wonke umuntu ohamba izindawo. Sasungula isisetshenziswa iCircue ngoba besifuna ukwenza umehluko ngendlela abantu abahamba ngayo futhi bafunde amanye amasiko. Sibonile ukuthi ukubheka izindawo ezintsha namasiko kungaba ngaphezu kwamandlafuthi besifuna ukwakha inkundla ezokwenza kube lula kubantu ukuthi bathole ulwazi olufanelekile, baxhumane nabendawo kanye nabahambi nokwakha umqondo womphakathi kusho uMsunguli. Umbono wethu ukwakha umphakathi wabahambi emhlabeni, abokufika nabendawo bangaxhumana, babelane ngolwazi basekane ohambweni labo Isisetshenziswa iCircue ivele ku-Apple noGooglePlay stores futhi ikhona uma ufuna ukuyilanda noma yikuphi emhlabeni. Ngesikhathi sibakhona bukhoma ngomhlaka-14 kuNtulikazi 2023, sesithole ukunakwa kakhulu ikakhulukazi kwabahambayo belanda okuqoshiwe nsukuzonke nokusayinela ukuba yingxenye ngezinkulungwane eziyishumi. "Isisetshenziswa iCircue umoya wokuhlola womhlaba," kusho omunye wabasebenzisi.
