Ngabe umusha kwezobuchwepheshe,uyafisa ukungena kodwa awunaso isiqiniseko ukuthi uzoqala kuphi? Mhlampe ufuna ushintsho kwezomsebenzi ezithokozisayo khona uzokhulisa intshisekelo yakho yezokuhlela? Noma ungena ngezikhathi ezithile kwezobuchwepheshe usukulungele ukunyusa ikhono nokwamukela izingqinamba ezintsha. Kodwa, noma ngabe ume kuphi, lokhu kubambisana kwenziwelwe WENA. Emphakathini waseHM sifuna ukwenza indawo efana nomndeni lapho siseka siluleke kahle. Cabanga uzungezwe ongoti abathanda ezobuchwepheshe abazokukhuthaza, bakhe kanye nawe, futhi bakweluleke ohambweni lokubhala ngobumfihlo. Icamaraderie emphakathini wethu iyajabulisa! Kodwa ke akukhona lokho kuphela. I-NewDev.io inkundla ongaya kuyona ukuvula izimfihlakalo zokubhala amakhodi. Ngomcebo ophezulu kakhulu yezinto zokufunda nokulawulwa ongoti, uzoba yisazi sokubhala ngobumfihlo esikhathini esingesingakanani.
