Uhlobo lweTECNO CAMON 20 Doodle oluneAnti-Shake luzokwethulwa maduzane Ekujabuleni emhlabeni wezobuchwepheshe, lapho ukucabanga kuhlangane nokwenza kabusha, uhlobo lweTECNO CAMON 20 iyagqama. Ekujuleni kwezobuchwepheshe kukhona imfihlo-ubungcwele bangemuva buhambisana nobunjalo bezobuciko beDoodle ngokubambisana noMnu Doodle. Asicubungule kuzimanga zaledivayisi ehluke kakhulu ngesikhathi silindile ukuvezwa kwayo. Ubuciko beDoodle isebuMnyameni: Zilungiselele ukujabuliswa ikhava yangemuva yohlobo lweCAMON 20 Doodle, eveza ubuhle bobuciko beDoodle elibenyezelayo ebumnyameni. Zicabange usendaweni ezikhanyiswe ngodimu, buka imidwebo ikusanganisa ikhanda, kwengeza into ekwenza uzibuze ngolwazi lwefoni yesimanje. Ngalokhu okuhlukile iCAMON 20 izoba ukuqala kwengxoxo ngisho noma uya kuphi! Ikhamera Yakudala ene-Anti-Shake noMlingo Wokukhanya- okuphansi: Uhlobo lweCAMON 20 Doodle ibuya nekhamera eyiclassic ethatha izikhathi ngokucaca okungeke kuqhathaniswa nokunemba.
Valelisa kumavidiyo anyakazayo futhi angabonakali kahle enento yamavidiyo anganyakazi aqoshiwe, iqinisekisa zonke izivalelo zigxilile zinganyakazi. Ngisho nasezimweni ezingqinamba zokukhanyisa, ikhamera enokukhanya okuncane izinto ezikhuphukela kupuleti, ukudiliva imiphumela ejabulisayo ezokushiya umangele. Ivisual Delight esebenza ngokushesha okukhulu! Uhlobo lweTECNO CAMON 20 Doodle iveza ngobuqiniso ukubhala komdwebo kuhlangana nobuchwepheshe. Ubuhle bayo obushelelekayo nobesimanje buveza ubuhle, ngesikhathi isibonisi se-AMOLED esingu-6.9 intshi sinikeza injabulo ebonakalayo enesilinganiso sokuvuselela esingu-120Hz esibushelelezi sabezindaba, abadlalayo, nabathanda ukuphequlula. Amandla iwanikwa yiMediaTek Dimensity 8050 SoC uhlobo lweCAMON 20 Doodle ekunikeza ukusebenza okuyisimangaliso futhi okusheshayo okusekwe kwafika ku-16GB weRAM no-256/512GB wendawo yokugcina. Yizwa ingxube yokwakhiwa namandla okugcina idivayisi, umsebenzi wobuciko ongaphezu kokulindelekile, ikulungelelokuphila kwakho kwesimanje. Amandla osuku lonke nokushaja okusheshayo: Ukhathazekile ngokuthi ibhurethi ithatha isikhathi esingakanani? Ngobukhulu buka 5000mAh bebhurethi yeCAMON 20, ungahlala usuku lonke ngokukhululeka ngisho uyisebenzisa kakhulu.
Futhi uma sekuyisikhathi sokurishaja, i45W ishaja ngokushesha ikuqinisekisa ukuthi uzobe usunamandla agcwele esikhathini esingesingakanani, ikugcina uxhumekile ube uhamba. Uhlobo lweTECNO CAMON 20 Doodle luhlelelwe ukuchaza kabusha indlela oyazi ngayo ngobuciko nezobuchwepheshe. Ngakho zilungiselele ukuqala uhambo olufaka makhono nokwenza kabusha kudivayisi eyenziwelwe ukuthathekisa. Hlala uqaphile ukukhishwa okusemthethweni futhi uzilungiselele ukusebenzisa izinzwa zakho ngomlingani wokugcina wendlela yokuphila.! Thola eminye imininingwane uma ulandela uTECNO kuFacebook, Instagram noTwitter.
Siyakubingelela siqalo sezobuchwepheshe bezempilo, uJumia uzokudla isinkwa sakho! NgoLwesibili ziwu-17 kuNhlaba ngo 2022, iNigerian eCommerce enkulu, uJumia yakhipha umbiko wezezimali wekota yokuqala yango-2022. I-Co-CEO uJeremy Horada no Sacha Poignonnec babelana ngamaoda,ingenisonzuzo, nenani lokudayisile kukonke (GMV) babona ukukhula okukhulu uma uqhathanisa namakota ayisishagalolunye adlule. Uma uqhathanisa uQ1 ngo-2021 no Q1 wango-2022, amaoda akhula kusuka ezigidini ezingu 6.6 kuya ezigidini ezingu 9.3, uGMV wakhula usuka ku $198.9 izigidi uya ku$252.7 izigidi, ngesikhathi ingenisonzuzo isuka ku$33 izigidi iya ku$4.6 izigidi. Ngisho lokhu kukhula, akukona okuhle kodwa enkampanini njengemiholo ngaphambi kwenzalo,intela, ukwehla nokukhokha izikweletu (EBITDA) ukulahlekelwa kwaba izigidi ezingu-$53. Ocingweni neTechCrunch, iPiognonnec yabelana ngezinhlelo zenkampani ukugcina ukulahlekelwa kwe-EBITDA kungaphansi kwezigidi ezingu-$70 kuqoshiwe naku-Q1 wango 2021. Manje okuhle nentuthuko ejabulisayo engenzeka. IJumiaPay, umkhiqizo wayo we-fintech, isithole ukunikezwa isixazululo sokusebenza kwenkokhelo (PSSP), okuzovumela uhlelo lwenkokhelo lomuntu wesithathu emabhizinisini eNigeria. Lentuthuko iyibeka ekuncintisaneni ngqo nePaystack, Flutterwave, eTranzact kanye neRemita. Ibuye inikezele omunye umnyombo wengenisonzuzo uma isidinga ukunyusa izingenisonzuzo.
IPSSP ijwayele ukwenza imali yayo ngokubiza imali yokuthengiselana ekutheniselaneni ngakunye abakwenzayo, lezi zimali zijwayele ukwahluka kuncike kunani lokuhwebiselana. Ngombiko ngamunye u34% wamaoda afakiwe kuJumia aqediwe ngokusebenzisa uJuminaPay ngemvume yawo,izinamba zikaJumiaPay zinganyuka kumakota azolandela. Ukunakekelwa kwezempilo kuhamba phambili Mhlampe into ejabulisayo ngezinguquko okwabelwane ngazo embikweni yisinqumo sikaJumia sokwehluka endaweni yokunakekela kwezempilo. Ngokubambisana neQembu leConsultative ukuSiza abahlwemou, inkampani ihlola ukusebenza okuzovumela abasebenzisi ukuthi bangene kodokotela ngokukhokha njalo ngenyanga imali engango $1. Ngokubhekwa ngokwahlukana, umnyakazo omuhle kakhulu ukuthsibone iJumia ingena esizindeni samakhasimende ayo akhona kanye nengqalasizinda. Kuphinde kumele kubancintisani abasabekayo kuziqalo zokunakekelwa kwezempilo ezikhona. Inhlangano yezempilo emhlabeni (WHO) iphakamisa udokotela oyedwa kubantu abangu 600 ezweni, kodwa eNigeria kunodokotela oyedwa kubantu abangu 5000. Okungaphezu kwalokho Inhlangano yezeMpilo eNigeria ibika ukuthi abantu abangu 35000 kwabangu 72000 ababhalisele ukuba ngodokotela futhi abasebenzayo eNigeria, ngesikhathi imboni yezokunakekelwa kwezempilo eAfrika ihlose ukuba nemali engango $259 amabhiliyoni ngonyaka wezi-2030. Yize noma imininingwane emincane yanikezwa ngalomnyakazo, ukuhlaselwa kwayo kusendaweni enzima engathandeki eAfrika futhi ayihlobene nebhizinisi ngqo okuvumela imibuzo.
Ezempilozocingo ezikhona eziyisiqalo ezweni okubandakanya iCribMD, iWello neWellaHealth. Njengezinkampani ezizimele, imibiko yabo ayijwayeleukuba sendaweni yomphakathi, kodwa ngo 2021 ingxoxo neTechpoint Afrika, iWello yabika ukuthi isibe namakhasimende angu 140, ngeCribMD kubikwa ukuthi isiza iziguli ezingu 2800 kusuka ngonyaka wezi2021. I-CEO yaseWellaHealth iphinde yabelana ngokuthi ngokuthi inkampani ifike ku-10,000 wabasebenzisi abehlukile ngo-2017, nezinkulungwane zabantu abalindile. Lezi zinkampani kancane ukuneJumia, ngomkhakha wezokunakekelwa kwempilo waseAfrika esikhulise izigidi ezingu-$392 ngonyaka wezi-2021. Kepha ke lezi zinkampani kumele zilwele ukungena ku inthanethi okuncane, ukunciphisa imali engenayo emakhaya, izimiso zamasiko ukuze bathole amakhasimende akhokhayo. Ukwengeza uJumia akanabo ongoti abasebenza emkhakheni wezokunakekelwa kwezempilo abangadlula ekushintsheni kokufunda ukuze abakwenzayo kuphumelele. Ngisho nombono wokuqasha izifundiswa ezinesipiliyoni, izinto mhlampe ngeke zihambe ngendlela yabo zisuka nje. Indalo yeziqephu yendawo ezokunakekelwa kwempilo enye ingqinamba abadlali abakhona ababhekana nayo. Isibonelo kukhona izibhendlela ezinomsebenzi omningi namarekhodi angedijithali futhi ngisho nezimbalwa zisabelana ngalolulwazi. Lokhu kwenza kuphoqe ukuthi iziqalo zokunakekelwa kwezempilo zakhe izixazululo zalenjongo.
Ukwakha ukubambisana okuzosebenza kahle kwezokunakekelwa kwezempilo Ngesikhathi lokhu kungaveza inkingaezinhlelweni zikaJumia kwezokunakekelwa kwezempilo, uYomi Kazeem, uMeluleki oMkhulu, iSeleleko esibalulekile, ukholelwa ukuthi iJumia inawo amandla okuphumelela, ikakhulukazi uma ihamba ngomgudu wokubambisana. Ngesikhathi sikhuluma neTechpoint Africa, uthe, iJumia inawo amandla okwakha ezobuchwepheshebezempilo kwayo ngokuba nababambisani abaningi abazobheka ukuthi konke kuhamba kahle. Ingabambisana futhi namakhemisi, ibambise ngelojistikhi yohlelokuxhumana,futhi ihalnganise ukuhanjiswa kwemithi ngokusebenza kwemithi yocingo,ngakho iziguli azikhulumi nodokotela kuphela kodwa futhi bathola imithi yabo ngendlela elula. Le ndlela ibalulekile ngoba, ekugcineni ukunikeza ukukwazi ukungena ekuxhumaneni iyona kuphela indlela yokunakekelwa kwezempilo. Ngalezizinkampani eziningi ezivelayo, ukuzuza kwabasebenzisi kuba umncintiswano. Ngalokhu, ukubambisana nabantu besithathu okubheka ukungena ezigulini ngezinga eliphezulu kubalulekile Akufani nabadlali abakhona bezobuchwepheshebezempilo,uJumia usakhe umsebenzi onengqondo ongasiza ukuhambisa imithi ngokushesha ukuneziqalo okumele zincike kubanikezeli bosizo besithathu. Ngesikhathi lokhu kusho ukuthi uJumia angakwazi ukungena emakethe, kuphinde kuveze nethuba lokwandisa umsebenzi wezobuchwepheshe bezempilo ezweni ngesikhathi kuvulwa omunye umnyombo wengenisonzuzo kuJumia. Iziqalo zokunakekelwa kwezempilo, isibonelo zinganikezela ngokushesha futhi zenze kahle umsebenzi ngokubambisana neJumia.
Ukubambisana okunjena kungabaveza kuJumia mhlampe esizindeni esikhulu samakhasimende. Isibonelo sokubambisana okunjalo ukubambisana kwe AirtelKenya neMydawa, ikhemesi le inthanethi eKenya elivumela amakhasimende aka Airtel ukuthi angene kuwebusayithi yeMyDawa ngaphandle kokulahleka kokubiza kwemininingo ngesikhathi iMyDawa ikukhethisa ukukhokhela imikhiqizo ngeAirtel Money. Ngaphandle kokunyuswa yiCOVID 19 iziqalo zezobuchwepheshe bezempilo zisenendlela ende yokuhlangabezana nezidingo zezokunakekelwa kwezempilo eAfrika. Kepha ukubambisana okunjengalokhu kungaba okubalulekile ukuqhubekela phambili.
ISeamlessHR, iGates Foundation yethula isombululo i-Earned Wage Access yabasebenzi baseNigeria Uhla lokuholela oluhamba phambili eAfrika nenkampani yezobuchwepheshe beHR, iSeamlessHR ngokubambisana neBill and Melinda Gates Foundation isanda kusingatha umcimbi ophezulu wabasebenzi babasebenzi bekhola eluhlaza eNigeria emcimbini okhethekile ukuxoxa ngezindaba zabasebenzi bokhola oluhlaza nomkhiqizo ngezobuchwepheshe ezintsha zezixazululo, iBreeze Payer. Abaphathi be-7up Bottling Company, eGuiness Nigeria, Lafarge Cement, Julius Berger, Bua Cement, UACN nabanye bakhuluma kuseshini okwakukhuluma bonke futhi babamba iqhaza engxoxweni eyayivutha eyayiholwa ngabameli beGates Foundation neqembu lobuholi beSeamlessHR bebheka izixazululo ezintsha kulezizingqinamba eziyinkinga ezibhekene nabasebenzayo eAfrika, okukhethekile ukuveza izindaba zokuthuthuka zomsebenzi nokwengeza kumkhiqizo wesixazululo esiholwa ezobuchwepheshe. Esivumelwaneni iSeamlessHR iveze iBreeze Payer, isisetshenziswa esihamba phambili kubasebenzi esizokwazi ukuqhubeka nogqozi lwethalente phakathi kwabasebenzi ngezixazululo ezinjengo Earned Wage Access. Le nkundla ivumela abasebenzi babasebenzi bakhola oluhlaza ukuthi baphathe kahle uhlankokhelo lwabo, babheke umholo nezinkokhelo zemiholo, nokuxhumanisa umsebenzi wabo nezimakethe zemisebenzi yokkwengeza inani lwezezimali. Phezu kwetafula kukhona isixazululo esivumela abasebenzi bangene emiholweni yabo ngaphambi kosuku lokuhola nokuthi bengamele izimoeziphuthumayo zezezimali, ngaphandle kwamaphepha futhi kubiza kancane. Ukwengeza le nkundla isiza abaholi bakhe umlando wezezikweletu zabo, okungasiza ekutholeni izikweletu ezinkulu ngaphandle kwamathena nokwenza kangcono konke okwezezimali kwabo. Ulynn Eisenhart, uSekela Mqondisi weBill and Melinda Gates Foundation, ophinde wakhuluma ngokuthi izindaba zomsebenzi ziwuphazamisa kanjani umsebenzi, uthe, Abasebenzi bayimpahla ebaluleke kakhulu. Abantu bahlala ngoba kungukuthi izinhlangano zibaphatha kanjani kanye nabakuzuzayo futhi bakuthokozele ngesikhathi besahleli. Abasebenzi bakhola oluhlaza bafanele ukusizwa ngemisebenzi yezezimali nokusizwa yinhlangano yabo ukuze benze ngcono umsebenzi wabo.
Sifuna ukubanikeza izinsizakusebenza zezezimali ezandleni zabo ngenkundla yeEarned Wage Access. Yingakho sibambisene neSeamlessHR nabasebenzi, ukubambisa ngemininingo yomsebenzi nokwenza izixazululo ezihlalayo Emazwini akhe okuvala Iceo yaka SeamlesHR uEmmanuel Okeleji, ukhulume ngezixazululo zezobuchwepgeshe okumele inkampani izakhe ukwenza kangcono ukusebenza kwenhlangano,ikakhulukazi komqashi nomqashwa. "Ngokuhambisana nokwenzakabusha inkundla ye-Earned Wage Access uhlelo lokwenza uhla lwenkokhelo olusiza ukuphatha abasebenzi kanye nohla lwenkokhelo lukamqashi kanye nokubheka ukungena ezikweletini ezinanzalo encane siphinde sakha ezobuchwepheshe ezinkulu okuyithuluzi lokubheka isikhathi nokwethamela. Lesi sixazululo esihlanganisiwe silanda ugqozi ekwenzekeni okuyimpumelelo emhlabeni wonke, kuqinisekisa ukuthi abasebenzi bakhola oluhlaza bayaqhakaza endaweni enokweseka emsebenzini. Ngokubambisana neGates Foundation nabasebenzi abaphezulu babasebenzi bakhola oluhlaza, singakha umthelela wesikhathi eside kulesisiqephu sekhono leAfrika." Ungoti wezokuthuthukiswa kwengqalabhizinisi yabantu-uSolwazi Dapo Adeleye,uFaculty Director of Human Resources Management eNyuvesi yaseGeorgetown,isikhulumi esiqavile,wethula inkulumo emangalisayo ngokubaluleka kwezindaba zomsebenzi namandla okuguquka kwezobuchwepheshe endaweni yokusebenza namhlanje. "Sidinga ukushintsha indlela yethu nokuphinda sihlole isiphakamiso somsebenzi. Esikhundleni sokugxila kuphela ekhonweni eliphezulu, kumele sibone ukuthi ingxenye ebalulekile yokusebenza inabasebenzi bakhola oluhlaza ekugcineni kwesitebhisi. Ucwaningo olunzulu seluveze umthelela oncomekayo wokungena kwemali yomholo nokufakwa kwezezimali ekusebenzeni kwabasebenzi.
Ngokuqhakambisa ukuphila kahle kwabo nokubanikeza amathuluzi afanele,singavula amandla angempela ekusebenzeni kwethu, sihole nokukhula okuzogcineka enhlanganweni yethu, usho njalo". Isigaba sesibili saloluhlelo sihlelelwe ukuthi senzeke eKenya njengoba iSeamlessHR iqhubeka yanda ekufinyeleleni nasemtheleleni, iyaqhubeka nokushesha ekuzinikeleni kwayo ukusiza amabhizinisi aseAfrika ngoguquko lwezedijithali. NgeSeamlessHR ISeamlessHR iyona ehamba phambili ohlweni lokuholela nenkampani yobuchwepheshe beHR, egxile ekusizeni amabhizinisi akwazi ukuphatha iHR nohla lokuholela kusuka ekuqasheni kuya kumhlalaphansi ngezixazululo ezihamba phambili zobuchwepheshe. Ngokucishe kufike ku-1,000 imisebenzi ephakathi nendawo kuya kwemikhulu emazweni angu-20, inkampani inamahhofisi eNigeria, eGhana, eKenya futhi isanda kuqala ukusebenza eBotswana. Inkampani isanda kuqongelela izigidi ezingu-$10 kuChungechunge A lomzuliswano woxhasomali ukuphinda kabili ekukhuleni okujabulisayo kwepan-African nokwakha imikhiqizo emisha efake nezezimali, eminye ezokwethulwa kulomcimbi. ISeamlessHR obambisene ngobuchwepheshe kuBill noMelinda Gates Foundation kwakhola oluhlaza wephrojekthi eAfrika.
Veza amandla onawo okudlala imidlalo ngeInfinix NOTE 30 Innovative Bypass Charging Function Kubadlali abanogqozi , ukuhlangana nabangani kumaseshini okudlala ezihlokweni ezidumile njengo "Free Fire" noma "Arena of Valor" isebenza ngendlela yokuphumula futhi wehlise ingcindezi yosuku. Kepha, izingqinamba ezijwayelekile ziyavela ngesikhathi amafoni ephelelwa yibhurethi ngesikhathi somdlalo futhi ifuna ukushajwa ukuze ukwazi ukuqhubeka. Lokhu kujwayele ukuholela ezinkingeni zokushisa ngokweqile emabhurethini amafoni ajwayelekile, okudala ukuthi ukusebenza komdlalo kube nenkinga ngenxa yokukhiyeka kwesivalo seSoC. Ngenhlanhla iInfinix NOTE 30 ibhekana nalenkinga ngokudlula kokusebenza kokushaja,okuvumela abadlali ukuthi bashaje ngesikhathi bedlala ngaphandle kokushisa okweqile. Nge NOTE 30 abadlali bajabulela ukungaphazamiseki nesipiliyoni sokudlala kahle. iInfinix NOTE 30 yethula i45W emangalisayo kawaya enento yokushaja ngokushesha, enikeza amahora angu 1.95 okudlala ngebhurethi eshajwe amanithi angu 5. Ukwengeza, ingashaja kuze kufike ku-75% we-5000mAh ibhurethi ngemizuzu engu-30. Into egqamile efonini okusha kwayo kokudlula kwezobuchwepheshe kwezokushaja okunika amandla ngqo imotherboard ngesikhathi ushaja futhi udlala imidlalo. Yengeza impilo yebhurethi, yehlisa ukuguga kwebhurethi yengeze ukuphepha ngesikhathi ushaja futhi udlala imidlalo.
Okuseqinisweni, umsebenzi wokudlula kokushaja indlela ephambili yeNOTE 30. Uma izinga lebhurethi lifika noma lidlulaumbundu wokushaja (iphutha ku-30%) manje ukushaja kudlula kubhurethi besekuya ngqo kumathabhodi. Ngokwenza ukudlulisa kokushaja, ifoni ivele yehlise izinkinga zokushisa ngokweqile ezijwayele ukwenzeka ngesikhathi ukwenza kanye kanye ukushaja nokudlala. Kuzivivinyo ezenziwe yiInfinix Lebhu, ukudlulisa ukushaja kwehlusa izinga lokushisa kweNOTE 30 ngo-2-7°C uma uqhathanisa nalezi ezinye izindlela zokushaja. Lokhu kunyusa kakhulu ukunethezeka komsebenzisi, ikakhulukazi ngamaseshini engeziwe okudlala noma ezimweni zokushisa kakhulu kwelanga. Ukuvumela ukudlulisa ukushaja kulula futhi ungakwazi ukungena kukhona nge-X-Arena ingaphambili lokudlala. Abasebenzisi bangadlulisa kubha eseceleni kusuka esinxeleni kuya esayidini lwesokudla lesikrini bese becofa ukudlulisa ukushaja. Infinix izimisele ukunikeza abasebenzisi inkululeko eningi kanye nokuza nokusha njalo. Ngemodeli entsha, abadlali bangashintsha ukudlulisa kokushaja umbundu ngokuhlela kuX-Arena ngezindlela ezintathu:20%,30% noma 40%. Loku kusiza abasebenzisi ukuthi bakhethe ukuthi ngabe abathengisi bamanje basaplaya ngqo amandla kumathabhodi ukunokuthi kudlule kubhurethi uma ibhurethi ifika embundwini akade bewufisa.
Ngesipiliyoni sokudlala ngokuhambisana uchungechunge lweNOTE 30 lwethula uhlelokusebenza lokudlala olukhethekile lweX-Arena. Ngokuhanjiswa yinjini ephambili iDar-Link 2.0, ngobuchule ilinganisa isivinini seCPU neGPU kwiHelio G99 isivalelokuhlela, iqinisekisa ukudlala kahle nemibonakaliso egqamile emdlalweni ngamunye. I-XArena inikezela ngezinto ezibalulekile nengokungenelela kwezingcingo nemiyalezo kanye noRespawn Countdown, egcina abadlali benolwazi ngesikhathi somdlalo, oubavumealyo ukuthi benze kahle imisebenzi yabo. Ngaphezu kwalokho, iNOTE 30 PRO yenza umdlalo ube kwelinye izinga ngeVC okuwukethsezi kokupholisa, umsindo weJBL ohamba phambili, kanye nesikrini esigxilile esingu-120Hz, umsindo omkhulu oqinisekisiwe, ukuthinta, kanye nesipiliyoni sokubonakalayo kwabanogqozi lokudlala. Njengoba ehlobo kushisa, i-Infinix NOTE 30 iba yisinama kubadlali, ivumela amaseshini angaphazamiseki emidlalo ngaphandle kokukhathazeka ukuthi izishisa kakhulu. Ngena emdlalweni ojabulisayo kanye nozodlala nabo osukwini bese uzizwisa injabulo yesibiliyoni sokudlala lonke ihlobo! Infinix NOTE 30 uchungechunge lungathengwa ezitolo zokdayisa ezinemvume eNigeria yonke. Landela uInfinix Nigerai ezinkundleni zokuxhumana uma ufuna ulwazi olwengeziwe ngeNote 30 uschungechunge nezinto zayo ezimangalisayo.
Isibambiso samandla entsha,isikonekhono lezomnotho; isikhiye sekusasa leAfrika- Afrika Soft power IWheatbaker, iVictoria Island, iLagos ibone umfutho wokuhlangana kwabaholi baziwayo bamabhizinisi, abanomthelela kumakhono eAfrika, abenzi bezinqubomgomo, abanqobi bedijithali nosomabhizinisi abaholayo ezimbonini ezahlukene ngoLwesihlanu olwedlule. Behlangene ngombono ofanayo, labantu abehlukile abanemiqondo ehlakaniphile abahlanganisiwe ukuhlola ukuthi iAfrika ingavikela kanjani ikusasa ngokuvula mandla entsha yayo, isiko nekhono lomnotho. Ihlelwe yi-Afruca Soft Power ibambisene neFord Foundation, Open Society Foundation neAfrican Women on Board, umcimbi ugxile kubudlelwano phakathi kwezinkundla zedijithali ukuthathwa kwezobuchwepheshe nokwakhiwa kosomabhizinisi. “Njengezwe nezwekazi, kubalulekile ukubandakanya abantu abasha nabesifazane kubona bonke ubuholi. Kusuka ku-#endsars# kuya ku-#iCongoisbleeding neminye iminyakazo yezenhlalo embalwa izwe eseliyibonile eminyakeni edlule, sesibonile ukuthi kwenzakaleni uma singanikezeli ngokudingekayo nokuphepha kabesifazane nabantu abasha,'' kuveza uNkiru Balonwu, Umsunguli noMqondi wamakhono weAfrika Soft Power. “Sizoqhubeka sibe nalezizingxoxo, sikhanyisa amathuba amandla eAfrika, egxile kakhulu esikweni layo nesibalo sabantu basha, enikezela ngokukhula. Ngesikhathi adiventi yezindaba zedijithali nokuya phambili kwezobuchepheshe kunikeza intsha yaseAfrika ngezinkundla zokuveza amathalente,kwakhe izindaba zabo nokwakha ezokusebenza ezipyimpumelelo ezimbinini ezahlukene sizohlala sizimisele ukuqhubeka izingxoxo ezizosiza izwekazilibambise ngamandla okukhula kwalo,” kusho uNkiru. Ngisho nekhono nolwazi ezimbonini kuletha amathuba amaningi entsheni yaseAfrika, kukhona okubi la ngaphandle - okuphezulu kulolo luhla ukungazithembi. Ukuphepha yindaba embaxaningi enomthelela kuyona yonke into kusukela esisekelweni samalungelo abantu, amazinga okuphila, ukuhwebelana, ukuphumelela, ukuhamba ngenkululeko, ukuthola imfundo, ukungalingani ngobulili, njll.
Ukungabi khona kokuphepha ngenye yezinto enqanda ukwenza kabusha nokukhula kwezomnotho ezindaweni eziningi zewekazi. Emcimbini owawuneseshini yephaneli, igadwe nguFolashade Anozie, Umsunguli neCEO, yeNonconform Productions. Iphanela ngongoti abakuseshini kufaka: uNjideka Agbo, Umsunguli neCEO Glann Media Consult nowayenguUMhleli weGuardian Life Magazine; uHon. Akintude Oyebode, UKhomishana Wezezimali Nokuthuthukiswa Komnotho, wase-Ekiti State; uDKT Seun Fakorede, UKhomishana Wentsha Nezemidlalo, wase-Oyo State no-Adaora Ikenze, uMqondisi, Inqubomgomo Yomphakathi, i-Anglophone West Africa kwa-Meta “Ngeke ukwazi ukuxazulula inkinga yokuphepha lapho kungekho ubuqotho nobulungiswa,” kusho uHon Akintude Oyebode, uKhomishina wezokuthuthukiswa kweZezimali neZomnotho, u-Ekiti State. “Into enkulu eholela ebugebengwini ukungabi khona komphumela, yingakho uzothola ukthi emphakathini lapho kungekho khona umphumela, abantu bajwayele ukungena ebugebengwini. “Ingqinamba yokuphepha eNigeria inkinga okubhekenwe nayo,ezinye izingxenye zezwe,kunokuthuntwa okukhulu okuqhubekayo,kwezinye izingxenye,kunenkinga yezidakamizwa,kodwa okjule ukunakho konke kungukuvuma okucacile ukuthi amandla okukwazi esizwe ayehla sekunesikhathi eside sekufike lapho singasakwazi ukubhendula ezinkingeni zenhlalo,” kuphetha uAkintunde. Cishe ngo-60% wesibalo sabantu eAfrika abangaphansi kwemiyaka engu-25, izwekazi liyaziqhenya njengabantu abancane emhlabeni. Ngo-2050, isibalo sabantu kuqagulwa ukuthi siyobe siphindeke kabili, uma ubheka lentsha vezwa yizibalo njengethuba elikhulu lokukhula, ukwenza kabusha nokugcineka kokuthuthuka. Unjindeka Agbo, uMsunguli neCEO weGlannMedia Consult & Fmr, Editor waseGuardian Life Magazine,uyasho ukuthi ukushoda kokuphepha nokufakwa yikona imbangela yokumomwa kwengqondo eNigeria kanye nezinye izingxenye zase-Afrika. "Ngesinye isikhathi abantu bebejabulile ukubuyela eNigeria, kodwa konke lokhu sekushintshile.
Ngo-2018 sasiyiqoqo elikhulu labadingisiwe eEuropean Union, ngoba abantu babelokhu befuduka bebheka amadlelo aluhlaza, amathubaamaningi nokuphepha okungcono. Izinga lokuthanda izwe elivezwa yintsha ezweninlayo yenziwa izinga lokuthakaselwa abalithola kuhulumeni, kuhambisana nokuphepha nokufakwa abakunikezwa izwe labo, Engeza lokho. Ukuvikela Ikusasa: Amandla entsha, Amasiko kanye noMnotho Wokudala kwakuyinkundla ebalulekile kubona bobabili ababambisani bahulumeni namazwi entsha ezimbonini ezahlukene ukuthib baxoxisane. Ababambisani bomhlaba bayayeseka intshisekelo yeAfrika,ukubaluleka kokubona indima ebalulekile yamandla entsha nekhono lezomnotho ekwakheni izwekazi lwempumelelo.
