Kubandakanya ifomula ezokwenza ukuhlaziya emakethe,ibheka okusematheni nokwenza ukuhweba kwakho kusebenze kahle okwezinzuzo ezisheshayo. Imakethe ihamba ngokushesha okukhulu kodwa amabhothi aphucuzekile ayamelana nesivinini futhi ibambe okuvamile okungavela kuphinde kunyamalale ngesekhondi. Ngenxa yamathuluzi ezobuchwepheshe aphambili kakhulu iHFT isidumile njengesu losuku lokuhweba. HFT iyazenzela ukuhweba njengoba iqeda ukuhweba uma ihlangana nezimo ezisethwa ngabahwebi. HFT ibambisa okungenasisekelo ukwenza inzuzo esikhathini esincane. Ukuthenga nokudayisa ngesikhathi esisodwa ukuthenga impahla yobumfihlobezezimali enkundleni eyodwa futhi udayise kwesinye isibambiso ngokwahluka okuncane kwenani ukuze uzuze okwengeziwe. High-frequency Trading iyathandwa ngoba yenza kuhambe kahle emakethe futhi ixhumanise abathengi nabadayisi ngokushesha ngakho iqinisekisa ukuzinza. I-Algorithm okwakhiwe ngayo iHFT iphinde ivumeleabahwebi ukukhulisa izinzuzo zabo njengoba ukuthengiselana kwenzeka ngokuncike ekuhlelweni kuqala kwenani kwabahwebi. I-Scalping I-Scalping isetshenziswa uma abahwebi belahla izimpahla eziningi emakethe kodwa bathathe ithuba kumanani amancane emakethe ukunokugxuma okukhulu.
Inhloso ukuhlanganisa izinzuzo ezincane osukwini ukuze kube nezimbuyiselo ezinkulu ekupheleni kosuku. KuScalping ikhoyini yenzuzo ijwayele ukuba nesisindo esiphezulu sasemakethe nokukwazi ukushintsha imali njengoBitcoin ngenxa yokuma ndawonye kokushintsha kwenani. Ukwenza inzuzo eningi abenzi bemali benza ezabo izimfuno nosaplayi ngokuthenga ngenani lokubhida kodwa badayise ngenani elibuziwe. I-Scalping ithanda ukuhlaziya ngezobuchwepheshe ngaphezu kwamaqhinga abalulekile, ngakho abahwebi bathembela kulendlela abayaziyo ukusebenza kwangaphakathi kwe-ekhosistimu yobumfihlobezezimali futhi bungabekezela ngaphansi kwengcindezi. I-Scalping ingaphinde ingazenzekela isebenzisa amabhothi okuhweba ukuthola okusematheni nokuhweba okunenzuzo. Ukwengeza ngenxa youkwazi ukushintsha imali okubalulekile,umyalelo wokumisaukulahlekelwa akuxoxiswana ngawo. Ngakho, akukhuthazwa kwabaqalayo. Ukwahluka kokuthengiselana Ngokujwayelekileamanani ezobumfihlo bezezimali ahlezi etholakala ngokwahluka. Kusuka ekuzinzeni okuphezulu kuye ekuzinzeni okuphansi kuveziwe ekwesekweni nasemilayinini yokuvimba.
Noma yinini iya ngaphezulu noma ngaphansi kokwehluka kukhombisa ushintsho olungajwayelekile. Abahwebi abehlukile basebenzisa le ndlela ukubheka isikhathi esifanele sokuthenga noma sokudayisa impahla. Emazingeni okweseka inani lobumfihlo bezezimali ngeke likwazi ukudlula ukuze lehle. Ngesikhathi kusezingeni lokuvimba inani lezobumfihlo bezezimali lizohlangana nesivimbo esizovimba ukuthi linyuke. Ngakho uma inani lisondle nezinga lokwesekwa,mhlambe isikhathi esihle ukungena emakethe uphume futhi uma inani lisondela kumazinga okuvimba. Ubungcuphe bosuku lokuhweba ngobumfihlo bezezimali Usuku lokuhweba ngobumfihlo bezezimali kungaba nenzuzo. Kepha, kuza nokuqaphela kwakho,futhi imiphumela ingaba mibi uma ungakubheki lokhu okuyizingcuphe okunamathele osukwini lokuhweba ubumfihlobezezimali. Ukunyamalala Imakethe yobumfihlobezezimali ayidumile ngenhla yokungazinzi nokungaqaguleki kokushintsha kwenani.
Ikhoyini eyodwa ingaba phezulu ngolunye usuku bese iwa pansi ngosuku olulandelayo. Ngakho uma uqala emakethe yobumfihlobezezimali ungaba nobunzima bokubhekana nalokhu. Kodwa abahwebi bayazi ukuthi kunjani futhi bangasebenzisa namasu ehlukile ukudlala ngendlela ezobavuna. Ukuhlolwa okungacacile Ukwenza kwesikhathi eside kobumfihlo bezezimali akuchaziwe. Akufani nesitoko sasemakethe esinezinhlelo zebhizinisi nokuqhubeka kwezezimali okuchaziweokuncike ekwenzeni emakethe,ubumfihlo bezezimali abunakho lokho. Ngisho uhlweza olusetshenziswayo emhlabeni wedijithali lusanika inselelo yokuhlaziya isikhathi eside sezimpokophelo zezimali-kwenza kube nzima ukuqagula inani labo. Ngemakethe yobumfihlo bezezimali,okubonayo yikona okutholayo. Ayikho imigomo echaziwe Abanye bangayitusa ubumfihlo bezezimali, ngesikhathi abanye benkhathazeka ngobumfihlobezezimali ngenxa yalokhu.
Ngokucacile,lolu udaba lwendlela obona ngayo. Ukushoda kwegunya akunikezi abantu amandla phezu kwemali yabo nokubavumela ukuthi benze ibhizinisi kepha bacabanga ukuthi bakulungele. Ngokufanayo kungaba yindawo yokudlalela abantu abagangile abangaphunyula kungekho nomthetho ophoqa ukugwetshwa kwabo. Kodwa sesibone ukwenza ngokwahlukile emazweni ahlukene bebhekisissa ukuthi bangayilawula kanjani ubumfihlo bezezimali. Isibonelo U.S iyakuzama lokhu ngezinqobomgomo ezahlukene ngesikhathi amazwe afana noEl Aslvador esekwamukele ngokuphelele iBitcoin njengethenda elisemthethweni. Ngakho - okwehlukene kwabantu abehlukene. Kodwa ngisho siqhubeka sibona ukulawulwa endaweni yobumfihlo bezezimali,ekugcineni uwena ophethe ezokuphepha kwakho nokuphatha impahla. Isiphetho. Usuku lokuhweba kubumfihlobezezimali kuzuzisa imali kakhulu futhi kulula,futhi ngokufunda okufanele kulamasu: iHigh Frequency Trading, iScalping noma iRange Trading, uzorekhoda ukuhweba ngempumelelo. Kubeke emqondweni ukuthi imakethe yobumfihlo bezezimali ihamba ngokushesha,ngakho kumele usheshe njengoba yenza nayo.
