I-Grooming Endowment Trust ibambisana neKickoff Afrika Iqala uHlobo lwesibili leGETAccelerated, Ukuya phambili kunikeza ukungena kokuqala kweZiqalo kuN10 000 000 kuxhasomali olumahhala. I-Grooming Endowment Trust (GET)- ibambisene neKickoff Africa imoto yotshalomali olwaziwayo olusezingeni lokuqala kosomabhizinisi baseAfrika-lucela kufakwe izicelo kuhlobo lwesibili lohlelo lweGETAccelerated, umzamo woguquko owakhelwe ukusiza abasunguli abasezingeni lokuqala eNigeria. IGETAccelera inikeza iziqalo ezikhethiwe ithuba lokuthola Un10 000 000 kutshalozimali olunobu ekhiwthi obumahhala,kuhambisana nokuthola abeluleki abangongoti namathuba abalulekile asemakethe. I-Grooming Endowment Trust GET inhlangano engenanzuzo esengulwe ukugqugquzela imizamo ezinzile yenhlalonhle,kwezemfundo ezempilo amabhizinisi nokuthuthukiswa komphakathi. Ngokugxila kwawo ekunikezeleni ngokuseka notshalomali olune ekhwithi yamahhala kumabhizinisi enhlalonhle,Thola izinhloso ukwenza umthelela omuhle futhi usize abantu nemiphakathi eNigeria. I-GET ibambisana neKickoffAfrika benza uhlobo lokuqala lohlelo lweGETAccelerated ngo 2022 futhi baseka abasungulu abawu 10 abasaqala ngotshalomali lweikhwithi yamahhala lwa N10 000 000 futhi sebeqalile ngohlobo lwesibili lohlelo lwa 2023. I-GETAccelerated ihlose ukweseka iziqalo emikhakheni ebalulekile njengezinsiza zezimali, ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, ezemfundo, ezokulima, idijithali (ezomnotho) ingqalasizinda,umethelela kwezenhlalo, ukuhamba/logistikhi, ezokudayisa (ezokudayisa noma ezokudayisa kunhlalo). Ngemva kokuhlisiswa okukhulu nohlelo lokukhetha izizqalo eziyishumi zizothola isamba sezigidi ezingu-₦55 zoxhasomali olune ekhwithi yamahhala, ukuthola ongoti abazokweluleka, namathuba amaningi asemakethe ukukala amabhizinisi abo. Ukuba nemvume,iziqalo kumele zibhalise futhi zihlanganise neCorporate Affairs Commission (CAC), babe nomkhiqizo obalulekile omncane (MVP) nengxenye noma abasebenzisi abakhokhayo futhi asebesebenze isikhathi esingangezinyanga eziyisithupha kuya eminyakeni emibili. Ukwengeza, imodeli yebhizinisi ehlukile kumele iqonde noma ingaqondi ukwenza olunye uhlobo lomthelela (ezenhlalonhle, ezomnothi, ezomnotho, wenhlalonhle, ezepolitiki) emphakathini.
Iziqalo ku-angel imbewu yasekuqaleni noma izinga lembewu liyagqugquzelwa ukuthi lifake isicelo. "Siyajabula ukubamba uhlobo lwesibili lweGETAccelerated nokunikeza abasunguli abasanda kuqala izinsizakusebenza abazidingayo ukukhuphula isikali sabakuzamayo. Ngoxhasomali olune-ekhithi yamahhala, ukwelulekwa, namathuba asemakethe siyakholwa ukuthi loluhlelo lizosiza ekukhuleni lokwenza okusha kweziqalo zaseNigeria" -uMichael Adoghe, Umphathi weZokusebenza eGrooming Endowment Trust. "Sithole isipiliyoni sokuqala sokuthi ukweseka osomabhizinisi kungawenza kanjani amathuba amanye nomthelela ongatholakali kahle nasemuphakathini ogcindezelekile ngohlobo olusha lohlelo lweGETAccelerated. Sijahile ukweseka okunye ukwenziwa okusha eNigeria, ngokuvumela izinkampani zezinga lokuqala zithole ingqalabhizinisi, ukwelulekwa nezinsiza kusebenza ezidingekayo ukuhambisa umsebenzi wokuxazulula ingqinamba ebelesele yaseNigeria" - uFola Olatunji-David; umbambisani onguMsunguli weKickoff Afrika. IKickoff Afrika ibambisana neGET njengoba ihlobo lokugcotshwa lweGETAccelerated lugcinwa lusebenza njengoba iKickoff Africa yaziwa ngokweseka kwayo ukwenza okusha eAfrika yonke nokutshala kwayo izimali kuziqalo ezisezingeni lokuqala futhi isendaweni enhle ukunikeza ukweluleka okubalulekile nobuchule kosomabhizinisi ababambe iqhaza. I-GETAccelerated iyaqhubeka ikhipha izimemo kungelosi ukutshala abasunguli esiteji kuseshini yewebinar ezobukwa ngoLwesihlanu, ngoNtulikazi 21, kusuka ngo-4 ntambama kuya ku-5 ntambama,kuzobe kunongoti bemboni ongoti uToyin Bamidele (Umphathi weHlelo, Kickoff Afrika) noAdaeze Sokan (Program Led - Digital Eonomy; neMastercard Foundation). Iwebinar ithembisa ukuba neseshini enolwazi kubasebenzisi nabafake izicelo baqonde ukuthi bazifaka kanjani zicelo ukuze bagqame, ukubeka isiqalo sabo kuxhasomali lweikhwithi emahhala kumasu namaqhinga okubhekana nezingqinamba zeziqalo ezisezingeni lokuqala eNigeria. Ukubhalisa kulewebhina vakashela http://bit.ly/GET2023Webinar. Ukufakwa kwezicelo kuGETaccelerated kuvuliwe kuze kube uMgqibelo mhlaka-29 kuNtulikazi 2023, iziqalo ezinomdlandla zingafaka izicelo kubit.ly/GETAccelerated2 noma www.groomingendowement.org.
Uma ufuna ulwazi olwengeziwe nge GETAccelerated sicela uvakashele ku-www.grommingendowement.org.
