ITech1M yethulwa kuFounders Connect,ukusiza okungenankinga kokuqasha emhlabeni kwamabhizinisi ITech1M uhlelokusebenza lwebhizinisi Al yokubhekisisa amathalente emhlabeni futhi omunye wabaxhasi ohamba phambili emcimbi obonwa kakhulu weFounders Connect Live, yethule umkhiqizo woguquko lokuqasha emhlabeni. Ngokukhishwa komkhiqizo wayo omusha,iTech1M isthwe ukuthi iiphinde ichaze amazinga okuqasha,ukunikeza amabhizinisi esixazululo esihambisanayo sokubhekisisa,ukuqasha,nokukhokhela amathalente emhlabeni. ITech1M isanda kusekwa yiTechstars yaJ.P. Morgan isibambiso emcimbini njengoba kunikwe inkundla efanele ukuthi yethule umkhiqizo wayo omusha emakethe yaseAfrika. ITech1M yenze umkhiqizo Al ubhekane nokubhekisisa nezingqinamba zokuqasha ezibhekene nezigidi ezingaphezu kuka-400 zamaSME emhlabeni. Ukubhekisisa okungenankinga nokuqasha amathalente emhlabeni, ITech1M isiza amabhizinisi ukuthi aqashe okuyisithupha ngokushesha, okubiza kahle futhi okusebenza kahle konke enkundleni eyodwa. Ekwethuleni kwakhe okubonakalayo ngesikhathi somcimbi,uMsunguli weTech1M uTommie Edwards,ucacisele abasunguli namathalente kuTech1M ukukwazi ukubhekisisa kahle nokuphatha kahle izinkokhelo zamathalente omhlaba. Ngokuka Tommy Edwards iTech1M ayikho ngokuxhumanisa amabhizinisi ethalenteni,ingokukwazi kwamabhizinisi ukubhekisisa kahle ithalente,ukuqinisekisa ukuthi llifanele isidingo sabo esikhethekile. Enhliziyweni yenjongo yeTech1M ukuzinikela ukunikeza ukubhekisiswa kwethalente okukhulu okudlulela ekungachemini komuntu futhi okuletha ngesivinini,ukwenza kahle nangobulungiswa. "Njengenkundla ehamba phambili ukwakha amaqembu afakiwe ngokushesha, shibhu futhi ngendlela efanele, sihlose ukulinganisa indawo yokudlala, siqinisekise ukutho ithalente lonke, ngaphandle kwendawo yabo, inethuba elilinganayo ukuthola amathuba abafanele," kusho uTommie Edwards.
Ngaphandlekokungena okusha emakethe, iTech1M isinesipiliyoni esincomekayo sezinga lokukhula njalo ngesonto ngo-30% kusuke ijoyine iTechstars ngabasebenzisi abangaphezu kuka-12000 abavele basenkundleni nababambisani kumabhizinisi abangaphezu kuka-28. Ukwengeza okuthokozisayo kokwethulwa komkhiqizo,amathalente namabhizinisi afanayo anikezwa ithuba lokuwina izipho zemali namagajethi aphezulu, ukwenyusa ukujabula emcimbini. IFounders Connect Live benza izihlokoezahlukene namaseshini enkulumo ebalulekile kubasunguli abaziwayo eNigeria, ukulima indawo efanele ukufunda, ukubambisana kanye nokusizana. NgeTech1M ITech1M uhlelokusetshenizswa kwebhizinisi oluholayo olusiza ukuqasha amamenenja kubhekisiswe ukuqasha kanye nokukhokhela amathalente emhlabeni. Ngokuqondanisa kweAl, ukuqasha amavidiyo nezinye izinto ezintsha,kwenza kubelula ukubhekisisa ithalente futhi kwenza kube lula ukwenza izinkokhelo ezeqa imingcele emazweni angu 120. ITech1M yenza izinguquko endaweni yokuqasha ngokwenza i-ekhosistimu ebheka ukwenza kahle ukuqasha,ukuqeqesha kabusha nokulawula amaqembu akhishiwe. Ukwazi kangcono ngeTech1M,sicela uvakashele www,tech1m.com.
Ukusebenza okungaqhathaniswa nalutho enanini layo-Uchungechunge lweNOTE 30 lweInfinix luthole ukubhekisiswa yiRave kwamanye amaTech Media Worldwild Umkhiqizo wohlobo oluphakathi nendawo oluncomekayo lweINFINIX seluthole ukunakwa okukhulu ngaphezu kwemingcele yasemakethe ejwayelekile. Uhlobo lusanda kuveza uchungechunge obelulindelwe kakhulu lweNOTE 30 ukunikeza abasebenzisi abasha ngokukhetha okunye kokusebenza okuncomekayo. Izindaba zobuchwepheshe ezidumile zamaphepha sezenze ukubhekisisa okunzulu kwaloluchungechunge,bencoma okuhle kwe-68W wokushaja ngokushesha, ukwakhiwa okuhehayo, izinto zeqophelo eliphezulu, nokubiza okukhonekayo. Manje akwesihlole ukucabanga kongoti bezezindaba besesigubha ekubanjweni komhlaba yilona lonke uchungechunge lweNOTE 30. Ukubhekisisa kweRave Umazi wezobuchwepheshe iRenowned British,iSuperSaf ibhekisise kahle amamodeli amathathu ochungechunge lweNOTE 30: Inote 30,NOTE 30 5G neNOTE 30 Pro. Ngesikhathi kuhlolwa Inote 30 Pro, echoma ngakho kokubili i-68W ukushaja okusheshayo kukawaya no-15W wokukwazi ukushaja ngokushesha okungena waya, iSuperSaf ayikwazanga ukuzibamba kodwa yaveza ukuncoma kwayo. Ukubalulile ukuthi "I-NOTE 30 Pro iyinto engajwayelekile emakethe yamanje yamafoni esimanje,inikeza ukushaja okusheshayo okungena waya ngenani lokuncintisana." Akubizi lutho ukuthi iNOTE 30 Pro ifoni yesimanje yokuqala enanini layo ukuba nokushaja okusheshayo okungena waya.
Ingcono kakhulu ngohlelomali olukahle iNOTE 30 idonse amehlo eSuperSaf ngokuhle kwayo okwehlukile. Ukucacisile ukuthi, Ï-NOTE 30 iyaqhama kuhlelomali lwamafoni." Lolu chungechunge lunikeza izinto ezincomekayo njenge 45W wokushaja ngokushesha isikrini esihle sa120 Hz nendawo enkulu yokugcina efika ku 16GB+256GB konke lokhu ngenani elihle labancintisani. Ukwengeza, iNOTE 30 5G yandisa uchungechunge ngokukwazi kwayo kwe-5G nokuncomeka okungu-180MP kwekhamera. USuperSaf wabelane ngemicabango yakhe,ethi "Inote 30 5G inikeza ukusebenza okuhamba phambili kwanoma iyiphi ifoni ye5G kunani layo Inconywe Kakhulu yiZindaba Uchungechunge lweNOTE 30 llunikeza ukukhetha phakathi kwegilasi ngemuva noma kufakwe isikhumba ukwengeza isitayela esihle. Izindaba zobuchwepheshe ezihloniphekile iGSMArena iyatuswa ngentshisekelo, ukusho Infinix ngokucacile inentshisekelo futhi ifuna ukungena ngaphezu kwekilasi layo, esikujabulelayo Uma kuza empilweni yebhurethi, iNOTE 30 yedlula obekulindelekile, ithola okujabulisayo amahora angu-119 esivivinyo sokubekezela. IGSMArena ithe, "Kungcono kakhulu ukunobesikulindele kuleshiphusethi nebhurethi inhlanganisela enamandla.
INOTE 30 yenza kahle ekubekezeleni kokulinda." INOTE 30 ayijabulisi abantu kuphela ngempilo yebhurethi kodwa ne-45W wokukwazi ukushaja ngokushesha futhi ihlala isikhathi eside. Ifoni inezinto okusha isibonelo sakho konke ukushaja ngokushesha isixazululo sokudlula, ukuhlehla nokusebenza okuphusile. Lokhu kwandisa isipiliyoni sokushaja ezimweni ezahlukene. Ukudlula ukusebenza kokushaja,isibonelo, kunika ngqo amandla imathabhodi yefoni, yehlisa ingcindezi kubhurethi nokwenza kangcono ukusebenza kokudlala-into ebalulekile kubadlali abasha bamafoni. GSMArena iveze,Yinto enhle le,ikakhulukazi uma ufuna ukudlala futhi unganyusa kakhulu ubude bebhurethi Ubhloga wezobuchwepheshe odumile waseAmerica uSomeGadgetGuy wenze isivivinyo sokubheka ubuhle bomsindo omkhulu kuNOTE 30 Pro ngeJBL yokushintsha egumbini lokulala elincane. Imiphumela ibincomeka,nokuzwakalayo okucacile,nokulahla umkhondo okuncane. ISomeGadgetGuy iphethe, "ngichaza ukuthi loyo umsindo ozwakala kahle." Ibhloga izwakalise ukwaneliseka ngesikrini, esikunikeza ukushintsheka phakathi kuka60Hz,90Hz no120Hz,sikholelwa ukuthi inamandla okuhambisa isipiliyoni esihle esingalindelekile kubasebenzisi.
Ithandwa Abanomthelela Amawebhusayithi ezobuchwepheshe anomthelela emhlabeni, 9to5Google kanye neGizChina, income kakhulu ukusebenza kokubiza kochungechunge lweNOTE 30. I-9to5Google iveze ukuthi iNOTE 30 5G idlula okunye ukukhetha ezingeni lenani layo, ukunikeza ngesipiliyoni esikhulu somsebenzisi eStates. IGizChina iklomelise INOTE 30 Pro isiko esiphezulu samaphuzu angu 4.4,isho ukuthi INGUMNQOBI WANGEMPELA WEVFM Kokubili ukubhekwa kuncome ukwakhiwa okwahlukile,ukusebenza okunamandla kwehadiwe,ungqo wesikhrini esihle nezobuchwepheshe bokushaja ngokushesha kuNOTE 30Pro. Kukhona konke izindaba zobuchwepheshe zinconywe kakhulu kuchungechunge lweInfinix NOTE 30, ngokuvumelana bebonga ukusebenza kahle nesipiliyoni ngenani elikhonekayo. Uchungechunge lushayelwa izandla ngenani lalo elehlukile. Lokhu kugcizelela ukukholelwa kwethu ukuthi lonke uchungechunge lweNOTE 30 olusha luzogcwala imakethe yamafoni abiza kancane kuhhafu wonyaka. Infinix ihlose ukuletha injabulo yezobuchwepheshe kubantu abaningi emhlabeni wonkenge NOTE 30 namadivayisi ekusasa eInfinix bakulungele ukusiza intsha yanamhlanje nakusasa.
I-i-Academy isiza iTech Talent futhi ibungaza ukuphumelela kweHackathon I-i-Academy ehola kwezokufundwa kwezobuchwepheshe iqale ukusizwa yiAfrika Prudential PLc,iyaqhubeka yenza umehluko obalulekile ekwakheni amathuba okukhula nokuya phambili kumbini yezobuchwepheshe. Ngokuzibophezela kwayo ukunciphisa umethelela kuthalente lezobuchwepheshe, i-i-Academy, inikele ngohlelo olukhulu lokuqeqeshwa kwezinyanga eziyisishagalolunye eyakhelwe ukuqeqesha intsha enentshisekelo kwezobuchwepheshe enamakhono adingekayo nolwazi lokulungela umsebenzi,nokwenza kahle endaweni yokulokhu kushintsha ezobuchwepheshe. Uhlelo lokuqeqeshwa lwe-i-Academy lubandakanya ukuthuthuka kohlelokusebenza lwangaphambili nangemuva,kwengezwa nokuqeqeshwaa kumakhono athambile futhi abalulekile. Indlela eyinhlanganisela yokufunda abavundi bathola isipiliyoni sokuzibambela nokubona amaphrojekthi empilo yangempela,ukuqinisekisa ukuthi bazilungiselele kahle ezimfunweni zemboni uma sebezogogoga. Njengengxenye yokuzibophezela ukuze kulondolozwe ukwenza okusha nokubambisana, i-i-Academy isanda kubamba ihackathon eyimpumelelo enkulu,ihambisana nesamba samaqoqo ayisishagalolunye abambe iqhaza. Lo mcimbi unikeze inkundla amaqoqo abantu ukuthi aveze ukusebenza kokwenza kolwazi abalutholil,bakhombise amathalente abo,futhi babukise ngokukwazi kwabo ukuxazulula izinkinga okwehlukile. Kumaqembu abambe iqhaza bekuyiqembu 3, elinabantu abane abanethalente elimangazayo,ilona eliqele njengeqembu elinqobile, bethola inani lemali abalifisayo elingu-150,000 NGN. Indlela yokunquma kuhackathon ifaka izinto ezahlukene, okufaka ukwenza kabusha nekhono, ubungcweti kwezobuchwepheshe, ukuxazulula inkinga, ukubambisana nokusebenza ndawonye, ikhodi yokuhle, nesiiliyoni sokusebenzisa nokudweba, umthyelela nesikalo, ukwethulwa nokuxhumana, nokubhekwa kwenkambiso. Iqembu ngalinye bekudingeka balethe imininingwane ephelele yephrojekthi yabo, beveza isitatimende senkinga,baphakamise isixazululo,izinto ezibalulekile nokusebenza,nezobuchwepheshe namathuluzi asebenzile.
Iphaneli yamajaji ahloniphekile, ehlanganisa u-Antoinette Edodo; iHead of Business Afrika Prudentail Plc, u-Osahon Elaiho; iHead of Product Engineering Afrika Prudential Plc, u-Olusegun Adesina; i-IT Audit Analyst Africa Prudential Plc, uRoy Anaedobe; iLead Business Analyist Africa Prudential Plc, kanye noPhillip Nkwam Analytics & ML Leader, eThe Bulb Africa, bajabula ngampela ngokusebenza okuhle kuwona wonke amaqembu abambe iqhaza. Banike iziphakamiso ezibalulekile iqembu ngalinye, benikeza ngemicabango neziphakamiso ukwengeza kuMinimum Viable Products (MVP) futhi baphakamise amaphrojekthi abo. Bheka okunye okuningi ngemikhiqizo yabo,esizokwabelana ngakho neqembu elikhethiwe. "Siyaziqhenya kakhulu ngokuzuzwe iQembu 3 kanye nabo bonke ababambe iqhaza kuhackathon,kusho u-Ivy Ikpeme-Mbakwem,uMqondisi weziNhlelo ze-i-Academy. "Ukuzinikela kwabo, ukwenza kabusha,umoya wokubambisana ukhombisa okuhle esifuna ukufaka kwabaqeqeshwayo. I-i-Academy izohlala izimisele ukunakekela nokusiza isizukulwane esizayo ukuba ngabaholi bezobuchwepheshe abazi B2602 umthelela omuhle ku ekhositimu yezobuchwepheshe baseNigeria Nezinhlelo zayo ezinamandla zokuqeqesha, nokukhuluma ngokuzanywayo njengehackathon, i-i-Academy iyaqhubeka yakha ikusasa eliqhakazile kulemboni yezobuchwepheshe, inikeza amakhono afanele nokwesekwa kwabafufusayo abanentshisekelo yezobuchwepheshe. Ngolwazi olwengeziwe nge-i-Academy nezinhlelo zayo, sicela uvakashele http://t.me/eacademy23. Nge-i-Academy: I-i-Academy isizwa yiAfrika Prudential Plc, eyezemfundo nezomnotho zenhlalo,umzamo obhekele ukubhekana nokuntuleka kwamakhono ethalente lezobuchwepheshe eNigeria nangale kwayo.
Ngohlelo lwayo olunamandl alokuqeqeshwa kwezinyanga eziyisishagalolunye, i-i-Academy iqeqesha abanetshisekelo kwezobuchwepheshe abasha ngamakhono abalulekile nolwazi oludingekayo ukuphumelela kumboni yezobuchwepheshe. Lo mzamo uhlose ukwenza amathuba okukhula nokuyisa phambili ngesikhathi ilondoloza isiko lokwenza kabusha nokubambisana.
I-InDrive imemezele ukwelulwa kweModeli ethi Name-Your-Price kumadolobha engeziwe angu-15 aseNigeria futhi yethule ukusebenza okusha kwentuthuko IBolsters Operations neZero-Commission inikeza abashayeli kumadolobha angu-15 NgoLwesihlanu, ngomhlaka-14 kuNtulikazi, i-inDrive okuhambayo okubonwa umhlaba wonke nenkundla yokusiza emadolobheni, iveze izinhlelo zokwelula izinsiza zokugibela umuntu nomuntu kuya emadolobheni angu-15 eNigeria nokwethula intuthuko yento yomkhiqizo ebizwa nge-inDrive.Freight. Isimemezelo senziwa Kusonto lesiqalo eLagos 2023,eyayibungaza ububhizinisi nokwenza okusha kweAfrika. UTimothy OlAdimeji, uMmeli weZokuthuthukiswa kaMabhizinisi inDrive Nigeria, uchaza ukuhamba njengesidingo ngqangi okumele wonke umuntu abe naso, ugcizelele ukuthi ukwelulwa kwamadolobha angu-15 kwe InDrive kuzokwenza lokhu kubelula kanjani kuwona wonke umuntu emphakathini wasendaweni ngemodeli yokubiza imoto yokukuhambisa kube nokuthembeka nobulungiswa. Ngokuqhubeka ngikhulume ekwethulweni kokusekwa kwelojistikhi yomkhiqizo omncane, ophakathi nendawo kanye namabhizinisi amakhulu, u-Oladimeji uthe, "Kusuka ekuhlaziyweni kwemininingo, sibonile ukuthi abantu bafuna izinsiza zokuhambisa nokulanda ipahla lokho kungabasiza ukuthutha amaphekhi asinda ngaphezu kuka-20kg. Ngakho ke, sethule savuselela indlela yezinsiza zokuhambisa impahla- i-inDrive.Freight - efunekayo, izinsiza zokuhambisa ngosuku olulodwa okuvumela amakhasimende kanye nabanikazi bamabhizinisi ukuthi bathuthe izimpahla ezisinda phakathi kuka-20kg kuya ku-20tn, ngaphandle kwenkinga." Ummeli wokuThuthukiswa kwamaBhizinisi waqhubeka wachaza ukuthi i-in Drive.Freight izibuko zemojuli yomuntu nomuntu ukugibela-izinto zesisetshenziswa,evumela amakhasimende ahlele amanani abawancamelayo,ukukhetha izimoto nokukhetha abashayeli. Iphinde ikhombise izinto zayo ezahlukile ezivumela amakhasimende athathe izithombe zezimpahla abahlose ukuzithumela. Kubanikazi bamabhizinisi lokhu kunomthelela woguquko njengoba abanikazi bamabhizinisi singasekho isidingo sokuthi batshale imali yengqalabhizinisi ukuhlela izinsiza zabo zokuhambisa impahla noma amabhizinisi elojistikhi, ngezinye izindlela zokonga ukubiza ezinikezwa ngokusebenzisa i-inDrive.Freight.
Kuzobukwa ukwethulwa kuyona yonke iNigeria, ngoMsombuluko ngomhlaka-18 kuNtulikazi, ukwelulwa kwe-inDrive emadolobheni amasha awu-15 eNigeria sekuqalile ngokusemthethweni.
